Product Short Description: Being Fast Acting Oral THC QuickStrip™ is a smoke-free cannabis alternative that delivers more cannabinoids per equivalent dose, faster, than other non-combustible formats.
Product Long Description:
Being Fast Acting Oral THC QuickStrip™ is a smoke-free cannabis alternative that delivers more cannabinoids per equivalent dose, faster, than other non-combustible formats.

Each QuickStrip delivers cannabinoids rapidly by micronizing cannabis oils and suspending them evenly in a thin film. And when dissolved under the tongue each THC QuickStrip delivers its cannabinoids with greater impact than edibles, oils or capsules containing similar amounts of THC because it bypasses the digestive system.

Being strips can easily be torn into smaller segments for micro-dosing. Sold in pouches of 10 strips (10 mg THC ea), with each strip hermetically sealed in individual wrappers for perfect portability.

Being strips are nut-free, and contain no animal products. Naturally flavoured with peppermint oil.

Product Short Description: A 0.5 g Blue Dream 510 thread cartridge from Good Supply filled with a smooth, berry-flavoured distillate.
Product Long Description:
The distillate in this 0.5 g cartridge from Good Supply comes from a hybrid extract. 

This product’s smooth, berry flavour comes from a terpene profile that contains beta-caryophyllene, also in black pepper, cloves and balsam; myrcene, which is present in mangoes, lemon grass, hops and thyme; humulene, which it shares with hops and coriander; and linalool, found in lavender and many flowers, mint and cinnamon. 

This cartridge should be stored upright in a dark, room-temperature environment. This cartridge requires a 510 thread vape battery for use.

Good Supply produced by Aphria, from Leamington, Ont., which grows all of its cannabis in state-of-the-art greenhouses and controls quality with a 509-step process.
Ingredients: THC Distillate, flavouring agents

Product Short Description: Ultra-thin (14g/m²) pre-rolled cones made from100% eco-conscious bamboo fibre.  Size: 1 1/4 (84mm).  10 cones per pack.
Product Long Description:
Rolling papers and pre-rolled cones made from 100% eco-conscious bamboo fibre,  OCB® BAMBOO utilizes the world’s most renewable fibre – bamboo – and does so in a way designed to respect and preserve the environment. 

The bamboo is grown without chemical fertilizers or pesticides, eco-consciously harvested (roots left intact to regrow for continual harvesting), and minimally processed (i.e., no chemical pulping or bleaching) to minimize impact on local ecosystems. The papers are left unbleached, dye-free and finished with all-natural acacia gum adhesive. 

The result is an ultra-thin (14g/m²) all-natural paper that’s great for the planet. Bamboo’s long fibres make it remarkably tear-resistant and easy to roll with, and its natural resistance to humidity means it won’t get gummy in humid conditions.  The burn is ultra-slow and even, and the taste is clean and neutral, with zero aftertaste.

King Palm rolls and filters contain no additives, chemicals and tobacco; flavoured with only all-natural essential oils.

Product Short Description: This pen brings supreme functionality to the palm of your hand in a powerful, ultra-discreet, lightweight and affordable device.

The newest addition to Grenco Science’s portfolio of dried herb vaporizers, the G Pen Dash brings supreme functionality to the palm of your hand in a powerful, ultra-discreet, lightweight and affordable device.  Featuring a glass glazed stainless steel heating chamber with three temperature settings (375F/190C, 401F/205C, and 428F/220C), the G Pen Dash fits in any sized pocket.  

Combined with a clean air source and integrated air path, experience unsurpassed flavour and vapour production from your favourite strains.  Other key elements include an ergonomically designed chamber opening for convenient loading and a magnetically attached mouthpiece that can be taken apart for easy cleaning and maintenance.   

The G Pen Dash also features haptic feedback and a smart button with three LEDs to indicate heat level and battery life.  With pass-through charging capability via Micro-USB and automatic shut-off, the G Pen Dash maximizes battery life and usability.

Product Short Description: The world's first line of ultra-thin (14g/m²) rolling papers and pre-rolled cones made from 100% eco-conscious bamboo fibre.
Product Long Description:
The world’s first line of rolling papers and pre-rolled cones made from 100% eco-conscious bamboo fibre,  OCB® BAMBOO utilizes a renewable fibre – bamboo – and does so in a way designed to respect and preserve the environment. 

The bamboo is grown without chemical fertilizers or pesticides, eco-consciously harvested (roots left intact to regrow for continual harvesting), and minimally processed (i.e., no chemical pulping or bleaching) to minimize impact on local ecosystems. The papers are left unbleached, dye-free and finished with all-natural acacia gum adhesive. 

The result is an ultra-thin (14g/m²) all-natural paper that’s great for the planet. Bamboo’s long fibres make it remarkably tear-resistant and easy to roll with, and its natural resistance to humidity means it won’t get gummy in humid conditions. The burn is ultra-slow and even, and the taste is clean and neutral, with zero aftertaste.

Terpee Slerpee represents the next generation of infamous West Coast genetics. It's a cross of GMO and Orange Zktlz. Notable terpenes limonene, linaool and pinene bring serious flavour and a robust citrus profile bolstered by a dank undercurrent and skunky aroma. Light, fluffy and frosted, Terpee Slerpee is the potent and flavourful product you can expect from the Qwest family.​

Truro Wedding Mint is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our state-of-the-art production facilities, where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang-dried, hand-trimmed, slow-cured and hand-packaged for a best-in-class craft cannabis experience. Wedding Mint Pre-Rolls are produced from the whole flower of our best-in-class batches and we have refined our mixing and milling processes to mirror the quality and THC levels of our popular whole flower products. All Truro Pre-Rolls are hand-weighed and hand-packaged.

Product Name: Tweed Quickies Kush Mints Joint Pre-Roll
Product Short Description: Tweed Quickies pre-rolls are evenly milled and machine rolled for a consistent burn. Made with Kush Mints, an indica-leaning hybrid, high THC strain.
Product Long Description: Tweed Quickies pre-rolls are evenly milled and machine rolled for a consistent burn. These Quickies are made with Kush Mints, a high THC indica-dominant hybrid strain known for its unique minty and earthy flavour and aroma profile. Kush Mints comes from a cross of Animal Mints and Bubba Kush. Tweed Quickies come in a convenient, recyclable case, keeping them sealed, protected and ready when you are.

Product Short Description: Masterfully pre-rolled joints containing Doja Ultra Sour, a sativa-dominant strain with a East Coast Sour Diesel and MK Ultra lineage.
Product Long Description: Masterfully pre-rolled joints containing Doja Ultra Sour, a high THC, sativa-dominant strain. Doja Ultra Sour is bred from OG strains East Coast Sour Diesel and MK Ultra. Together this lineage creates a strain that emits a pungent citrus aroma and flavour profile. Ultra Sour's pungent aroma is complemented by its unique buds covered in trichomes and lots of dark orange pistils.

Product Short Description: With sweet and citrusy flavours, Gelato #33 is an indica hybrid cross of Sunset Sherbet and Thin Mint GSC that is now available in a pre-roll format.
Product Long Description: With sweet and citrusy flavours, Gelato #33 is an indica hybrid that crosses Sunset Sherbet and Thin Mint GSC. LOT420 is a licensed cannabis producer located southeast of Montreal in Quebec's Eastern Townships, focused on producing hand-crafted, select batch and high-grade flower. Using proven methods developed in-house, every batch is thoughtfully cultivated, hang-dried, cured and hand-trimmed to give consumers a high grade product.

Product Long Description: The Citizen Stash Discovery Pack features a rotating set of our favourite strain finds of the moment. Currently featuring Banana Berry Kush, Lemon Pound Cake, Grease Monkey and Ape Tape. Each pre-roll has a soft grind and tight pack for a steady and smooth smoke.

Product Long Description: Bred from Grandaddy Purp and Bay Platinum Cookies it has a sweet start with a pine finish.

Product Long Description: Presenting Weed Me's strain specific 0.35g pre-rolls! This sativa dominant strain boasts a very strong THC potency potential, is milled and then filled into light-weight paper cones with a paper mouth piece.

Product Short Description: Enjoy the sweet grape aroma of this hybrid strain.
Product Long Description: Scotti's Cake est une variété hybride à fort potentiel de puissance en THC. Il est obtenu en croisant Biscotti, Gelato 41 et Animal Mints BX1. Son arôme est de raisin doux avec des notes de pétrole. La saveur est également douce avec des nuances de vanille. Le cannabis est broyé et ensuite rempli en cônes de papier léger avec une bouche à papier.

Product Short Description: Cherry Cookies gives you a dank, cakey and all-around earthy rich quality with a kick of fruit and sweetness and a dial-up in the potency department.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Frosted, berry and very bright, meet Frosted Cherry Cookies. Cherry Cookies, an offshoot of the GSC genetic dynasty, gives you that dank, cakey and all-around earthy rich quality with a kick of fruit and sweetness and a dial-up in the potency department thanks to its cross with The White. This defies its GSC undertones with a brighter profile and distinct punch in flavour that mirrors a sour cultivar.

Product Short Description: Sour tart berries, a bit of chemical fumes and elements of diesel and pine, White Sherbet crossed with Jet Fuel Gelato will do that.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Sour tart berries, a bit of chemical fumes and elements of diesel and pine, White Sherbet crossed with Jet Fuel Gelato will do that. A cone dipped in petrol and sprinkled with whiffs of grape is what Icicle entails. Frosted buds to match the icy quality of its trichomes against colours of emerald and hues of purple.

Product Short Description: Dialling up the apple rind, sweet flesh and juicy elements of the Mac with the potent, dank and citrus rich diesel of Trophy Wife.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Embrace the ripe side of the Mac. Dialling up the apple rind, sweet flesh and juicy elements of the Mac with the potent, dank and citrus rich diesel of Trophy Wife gives you more than your Red Delicious. Not fit for a pie and definitely not found at any orchard, Apple Mac is worth bobbing for.

Product Short Description: Our very first sampler multi-pack pre-rolls, with four cultivar varietals packaged in individual 0.5g pre-rolls.?
Product Long Description: Qwest is excited to introduce its very first sampler multi-pack pre-rolls, with four cultivar varietals packaged in individual 0.5g pre-rolls.​ Discover two core Qwest genetics currently in market with the special bonus of a reserve cultivar and a fourth sample of our newest harvest.​ ​Each package is a testament to our dedication to authentic, unique and interesting cultivars, abiding by the same craft process and providing a convenient format to partake in Qwest family genetics.

Product Short Description: Craft Golden Berry 3 x 0.5g Pre-Roll. Indica dominant hybrid with a sweet-spicy berry taste which is delicate and natural without being overpowering.
Product Long Description: We’ve taken everything we love about the Craft Golden Berry and put it in a pre-roll. Craft Golden Berry is an indica dominant hybrid with a sweet-spicy berry taste which is delicate and natural without being overpowering. The flavour profile includes undertones of red berries, slight skunk and pine aftertaste. Using only premium whole flower and organic hemp paper. Packaged in fully compostable pop-tube. 3 x 0.5g Pre-Rolls per package.

Product Name: ON (Jack Herer) + OFF (Afghan Skunk) Variety Pack (12pk)
Product Short Description: THINKER's ON + OFF multi-pack brings together two craft cultivars with 6 sativa-dominant "ON” and 6 indica-dominant “OFF” pre-rolls in each pack.
Product Long Description: THINKER's ON + OFF multi-pack features 12x0.25g pre-rolls with two different cultivars and terpene profiles chosen for thinkers looking to turn their thoughts ON (sativa) and OFF (indica). Crafted with premium whole flower, these pre-rolls are hand packaged with hang-dried and hand-trimmed buds. The unique 0.25g pre-roll size offers the right amount of flower to enjoy a fresh experience every time.

Product Short Description: A sativa-dominant cultivar with a refreshingly spicy scent, subtle hints of lemon grass, freshly cut pine and Thai basil.
Product Long Description:
A sativa-dominant cultivar consisting of Stardog and Arise, has an unmistakable bouquet with a refreshingly spicy scent and subtle hints of lemon grass, freshly cut pine and Thai basil.
Pheno hunted and selected by MSIKU.  Pre-rolls are made with 100% milled flower.

Product Short Description: A highly sought after genetic from the Swamp Boys with notes of gas and earthy undertones. Be sure to check this one off your bucket list!
Product Long Description: This powerful cultivar from the acclaimed Swamp Boys is a modern take on a classic genetic consisting of Chem 91, Star Fighter and White 91. This award-winning strain produces a flavourful smoke with warming gassy notes and earthy undertones. Be sure to check this one off your bucket list!

Product Short Description: Electric Lettuce features a rotating single strain, premium milled flower offered at a value price expertly rolled for a clean, consistent burn.
Product Long Description: Electric Lettuce features a rotating single strain, premium flower offered at a value price. Milled from flower, not trim, expertly rolled for a clean, consistent burn and gently packed into multi-packs. Grown fully indoors, in precision-controlled laboratory conditions. All Natural History flower is thoughtfully hung to dry, hand trimmed and cured for a minimum of 21-30 days.

Product Short Description: Ghost Drops offers each of its first drops in a convenient pre-roll multipack. Featuring First Class Funk, Z-Splitter, and Khalifa Mints.
Product Long Description: Ghost Drops offers each of its first drops in a convenient pre-roll multipack. Featuring First Class Funk and Z-Splitter hunted by Cultivating Happiness at Mother Labs and Khalifa Mints hunted by Headwater Cannabis at Imperial Micro Gro in Ontario. This unique sku gives consumers the opportunity to try the Ghost’s first drops with a single convenient purchase. Each perfectly rolled pre roll is hand crafted with whole flower, All bud, no bull.

Product Short Description: Reminiscent of classic Pineapple OG strains, these buds are sticky and dense with heavy trich coverage.
Product Long Description: This mouthwatering hybrid has a super sweet flavour and vanilla exhale. Reminiscent of classic Pineapple OG strains, these buds are sticky, resinous and dense with heavy trich coverage.

Product Short Description: The one and only Bacio Gelato. If you know, you know.
Product Long Description: The one and only Bacio Gelato. If you know, you know.

Product Short Description: Imagine sweet apple, with a subtle hints of mint and pine.
Product Long Description: This unique cross has gas! Dark hued buds with hints of olive green, caked sugar leaves, contrasting orange pistils, and frosted with a healthy coat of trichomes. Imagine sweet apple, with a subtle hints of mint and pine.

Product Short Description: A loud cultivar offering a diverse terpene profile and delicious aroma.
Product Long Description: This cultivar brings a diverse terpene profile that delivers a loud aroma which is delicious and unique. Dripping with creamy trichomes, this indica hybrid packs a flavour punch from start to finish.

Product Short Description: This renowned OG strain packs a serious flavour punch and is not one to take lightly. Sweet, skunky and straight gas.
Product Long Description: Sweet, skunky and straight gas. This renowned OG strain packs a serious flavour punch and is not one to take lightly. Chunky and dense buds, with fiery red pistils that offer serious bag appeal.

Product Short Description: Pink Kush Pre-rolls are ready-to-go. Each pack contains three 0.5 g pre-rolls packed with finely milled whole bud from potent indica flower.
Product Long Description: Pink Kush Pre-rolls are ready-to-go. Containing finely milled whole bud from potent, indica flower traditionally derived from OG Kush, a popular West Coast cannabis strain. Pink Kush is known for its fresh lemony aroma with notes of spice and lavender derived from its limonene, caryophyllene, and linalool terpenes.

Product Short Description: Sister plant to Oreo Mint Kush, this indica provides a sweet limonene smell with a smooth smoke. Hand trimmed, hang dried and cured for 11 days.
Product Long Description: Sister plant to Oreo Mint Kush. HHH presents large, beautifully frosted buds with incredibly strong odours of pine, lemon, menthol, and skunk. This indica is a smooth smoke thanks to it being hand trimmed, hang dried and cured for 11 days.

Product Short Description: Bahama Blizzard #11 “Buddies” is a complex cultivar from the Sugarbud genetic library created through the cross of Caribbean Cooler x Jet Fuel Gelato.
Product Long Description: Caring is sharing responsibly with our pre-roll Bahama Blizzard #11 “Buddies” in a convenient 10 x 0.35g format. This unique and delightfully complex cultivar from the Sugarbud genetic library is created through the cross of Caribbean Cooler x Jet Fuel Gelato. Bahama Blizzard #11 has well defined aromas of sweet confectionary, pine, lemon citrus, floral and fuel. We use 100% bud and no trim in our expertly crafted pre rolls.

Product Short Description: Khalifa Mints is an indica hybrid with sweet and earthy aromas. Rolled in unbleached hemp paper and packaged in a fully compostable/recyclable tube.
Product Long Description: Bred by Compound Genetics, Khalifa Mints is a name we gave this strain, due to the fact that its legacy name is heavily copyrighted in a galaxy far far away. Its genetic lineage is Khalifa Kush x The Menthol — an indica hybrid with sweet and earthy aromas. Small batch, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Grown without the use of pesticides or chemicals, and non-irradiated. Rolled in an unbleached hemp paper and packaged in fully compostable/recyclable tube.

Product Short Description: Bred by Ethos Genetics - Purple Sunset is known for sweet fruity notes, but also slight floral and sour aromas.
Product Long Description: Bred by Ethos Genetics - Purple Sunset is known for sweet fruity notes, but also slight floral and sour aromas. Minty green buds with deep purple undertones provide the  backdrop for beautiful trichome coverage. Our product is grown without the use of any form of pesticides, and is non-irradiated. Small batch (under 700 sqft rooms), hang dried, hand trimmed, and hand packaged. Non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Lilac Diesel is a sativa hybrid with a unique terpene profile featuring notes of berries, pine, spice, and citrus fruits.
Product Long Description:
Redees by Redecan are an unparalleled pre-roll experience that just got even more convenient. The Redecan King Pack offers 1 oz of your favourite Redecan strains, pre-rolled in our signature packaging, and sealed in packs of 10 to guarantee freshness. Thoughtfully designed for personal use at 0.40g, Redees by Redecan are rolled with all bud, no shake. Lilac Diesel is a sativa hybrid strain, named for its beautiful appearance and especially unique flavour profile. With a terpene profile featuring notes of berries, pine, spice, and citrus fruits, this bud is dense with lilac undertones and light-purple crystal trichomes.

Each Redecan King Pack contains 70 Lilac Diesel Redees.

Product Name: Cold Creek Kush Redees King Pack
Product Short Description: The Redecan King Pack offers 1 oz of your favourite Redecan strains, pre-rolled in our signature packaging and sealed in packs of 10.
Product Long Description:
Redees by Redecan are an unparalleled pre-roll experience that just got even more convenient. The Redecan King Pack offers 1 oz of your favourite Redecan strains, pre-rolled in our signature packaging and sealed in packs of 10 to guarantee freshness. Thoughtfully designed for personal use at 0.40g, Redees by Redecan are rolled with all bud, no shake. A sativa dominant hybrid between the ever-popular MK Ultra and Chemdawg 91, Cold Creek Kush, or CCK, is a globally recognized strain, known for its light green hues, amber hairs, and trichrome-frosted flowers. Cold Creek Kush is recognized for its dank smell, resembling a damp rainforest with notes of earth, wood, sour, and pine, giving a strong but fresh aroma and a dank, spicy, herbal flavour. 

Each Redecan King Pack contains 70 Cold Creek Kush Redees.

Product Short Description: Masterfully pre-rolled 2x0.5g joints containing DNA Genetics Kosher Kush: an indica-dominant strain.
Product Long Description: Masterfully pre-rolled joints containing DNA Genetics Kosher Kush: an indica-dominant strain. Available in a 2x0.5g format, DNA's award-winning Kosher Kush's emerald green buds produce an intriguing combination of woody and diesel aromas thanks to terpenes like myrcene, ꞵ-caryophyllene & limonene.

Product Short Description: Kootenay Fruit Pre-Rolls offer several 0.5g joints that pack a robust terpene profile of strong sweet fruit with hints of chocolate and Kush.
Product Long Description: General Admission is taking its jam-packed vape flavours to compact new heights with our line-up of multi-pack pre-rolls. Don't let these sleek and discreet pinners fool you, this Kootenay Fruit pack offers several 0.5g joints that will pack the perfect flavour boost you need. Kootenay Fruit Pre-Rolls is an indica straight from interior BC, and boasting a robust terpene profile of strong sweet fruit with hints of chocolate and Kush.

Product Short Description: The scent of lemon zest and spice make for a refreshing combination in these 100% milled flower pre-rolls.
Product Long Description: Upon opening the jar, you will be hit with a decadent wave of lemon zest. After that initial wave, the complexity of the bouquet sets in with some spicy and sweet undertones. The bright green coloured flowers are dense and coated in trichomes. Vibrant orange hairs and faint purple accents make this cultivar look as good as it tastes. We are extremely excited to round out our list with this latest addition to the line-up. Pre-rolls are made with 100 % milled flower.

Product Short Description: Sweet with hints of vanilla, this cultivar presents dark green flowers with purple hues in these 100% milled flower pre-rolls.
Product Long Description: The aromatics on this wonderful cultivar are true to its Gelato #33 and Tropicana Cookies lineage. Extremely sweet and almost candy like, with a hint of vanilla. The aesthetic presents dark green flowers with purple hues, with the structure leaning more towards Tropicana Cookies. Between the aromatics and the colours, this may be the most beautiful genetic we have grown. Pre-rolls are made with 100% milled flower.

Product Short Description: Ghost Drops Khalifa Mints is an indica dominant hybrid cross between Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. Its nose is fruity, followed by pungent peppermint.
Product Long Description: Ghost Drops Khalifa Mints is an indica dominant hybrid cross between Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. Its hunted by Rockstar Canadian cultivators Headwater Cannabis and grown locally in a micro craft facility. Khalifa Mints is noticeable upon appearance due to its dense, light dark green buds, caked with trichomes, and highlighted by bright hairs. Its nose is heavy and fruity, followed by notes of pungent peppermint, and its flavour is dominated by menthol with hints of citrus followed by a gassy aftertaste. Ghost Drops is thrilled to continue our relationship with Headwater Cannabis in the legal market, holding true to our promise: “No Ghost left behind."

Product Short Description: Thug Pug’s Meat Breath cut is stunning to behold, with an odor contrasting from spicy pepperoni to savory meat with layers of gas on top.
Product Long Description: Bred by the legendary Michigan breeder Thug Pug, Meat Breath is a combination of a cultivar called Meatloaf of an unknown lineage and Gage Green Genetics Mendo Breath. This Meat Breath cut is stunning to behold, and hosts some of the most alluring visual appeal you will see. It presents a tight, dense bud structure dripping with an almost unnaturally thick blanket of trichomes across the flower, which hide colours ranging from dark forest green to indigo and purple. The odour is unique and very pungent, contrasting from spicy pepperoni to savory meat with layers of gas on top. Meat Breath is fully cultivated indoors, in precision-controlled laboratory conditions. All Natural History flower is thoughtfully hang drief, hand trimmed and cured for a minimum of 10 days.

Product Short Description: Drew’s pheno features a rotation of limited drops grown by our partner craft growers and hand selected by our Master Grower.
Product Long Description: Top-shelf flower always start with a pheno hunt, where untold hours are spent popping seeds in the pursuit of finding a unicorn. Drew’s pheno features a rotation of limited drops grown by our partner craft growers and hand selected by our Master Grower.

Product Short Description: Sorbetto is an award-winning strain that features dense purple shaded buds with mouth-watering flavours that live up to its legendary lineage.
Product Long Description: Because it’s just the right thing to do, all our flower is hang-dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch that features a perfect airtight seal. Non-irradiated, obviously.

Product Short Description: Tiger Cake is a home run for all of the gas lovers out there. The aroma of menthol and gas tickle your senses.
Product Long Description: Tiger Cake is a home run for all of the gas lovers out there. Large, frosty buds feature a deep green colour with bright orange hairs, and the aroma of menthol and gas tickle your senses.

Product Short Description: A taste of the tropics, now in a twelve-pack. A cross between Pineapple Haze and Nuken, this hybrid has a sweet fruity aroma with earthy undertones.
Product Long Description: A taste of the tropics, now in a twelve-pack. A cross between Pineapple Haze and Nuken, this hybrid offers a sweet fruity aroma with earthy undertones thanks to its exotic terpene profile that’s high in ocimene, farnesene, and caryophyllene.

Product Short Description: BC Zaza is a sativa-dominant hybrid that crosses Animal Face x Sherb Crasher. Strong tropical fruit and vanilla flavours offer a sweet and sour aroma.
Product Long Description: BC Zaza is a sativa-dominant hybrid that crosses Animal Face x Sherb Crasher. Strong tropical fruit and vanilla flavours offer a sweet and sour aroma.

Product Short Description: From Canada's first 100% Indigenous Licensed Producer, Island Cherry is a hybrid strain with sweet cherry flavour and strong THC and terpenes levels.
Product Long Description: When the first Licensed Producer from Indigenous land on Cornwall Island teams up with one of the best cultivators on Prince Edward Island, you're bound to create sparks. Island cherry is an indica-dominant hybrid with strong cannabinoid and terpene levels. This dessert strain has a loud flavour profile full of mouthwatering sweet cherries and floral undertones.

Product Short Description: Brought to you by the first Licensed Producer on indigenous land, a limited run of our debut house bred & selected cultivar - Milk & Cookiez.
Product Long Description: Brought to you by the first Licensed Producer on indigenous land, a limited run of our debut house bred & selected cultivar - Milk & Cookiez. Just in time for the holiday season, this strain has a creamy flavour profile with sweet hints of vanilla and sour dough.

Product Short Description: Guava Ghoul is an indica-dominant guava-forward tropical island strain from GOOD BUDS. Grown in Living Organic Soils on Salt Spring Island, BC.
Product Long Description: A GOOD BUDS exclusive strain, Guava Ghoul is a chill tropical island monster. This organic indica was created when strains Zombie Stomp and Snow Monster crept through our Salt Spring Island farm to feast on a Hawaiian, creating a complex, tropical-punch strain. Guava Ghoul basks in warm ocean breezes, giving it a special sticky-greasy quality that's rich in CBG. With dominant β-caryophyllene, α-bisabolol, and β-myrcene terpenes, Guava Ghoul tastes of guava, honeydew, Tahiti lime, cinnamon and Candeia wood.  GOOD BUDS is a family-owned and operated LP from Salt Spring Island, BC. We believe in connecting good people with good cannabis, and we accomplish this using only living, organic soils rich in bioavailable microorganisms and nutrients for enhanced flavour, sustainability and quality. All our buds are harvested by hand, and hang dried in small batches using artisanal slow-cure methods.

Product Short Description: Durban P is a sativa-dominant strain with dark, luscious aromas of licorice and subtle piney notes.
Product Long Description:
Featuring sought-after strains, OS.ONE is a large, one-ounce bag of great quality weed from Original Stash. All OS.ONE flower is grown with care in our hybrid greenhouse, preferring natural controls and sunlight.

Durban P is a famed landrace cultivar, said to date back centuries to the modern-day port city of Durban. Brought to and refined by breeders in North America, this sativa-dominant strain has fat buds with frosty trichomes all over and is accompanied by dark, luscious aromas of licorice and subtle piney notes.

Product Short Description: Garlic Jelly, aka JMO, is a modern indica-dominant cross with a sticky sweet and sharp spicy aroma.
Product Long Description:
Featuring sought-after strains, OS.ONE is a large, one-ounce bag of great quality weed from Original Stash. All OS.ONE strains are grown with care in our hybrid greenhouse, preferring natural controls and sunlight. 

Garlic Jelly, aka JMO, is a modern indica-dominant cross, containing impressive lineage from its parents Jelly Breath (OG Kush Breath, thought to be a descendent from GSC) and GMO (another GSC line crossed with Chemdog). For those not in the know, those respected genetics inspire a sticky sweet and sharp spicy aroma.

Product Short Description: Pucker up, because Ultra Sour is an ultra potent sativa-dominant hybrid with light green buds, dense trichome coverage and fiery orange pistils.
Product Long Description: Pucker up, because Ultra Sour is an ultra potent sativa-dominant hybrid with light green buds, dense trichome coverage and fiery orange pistils. Upon opening the bag, your nose will be greeted by a complex dank diesel and zesty citrus aroma thanks to its dominant terpenes: terpinolene, limonene and caryophyllene.

Product Short Description: Marley Black Master Kush 3 x 0.5g Pre Rolls

Crossed in Amsterdam between two landrace strains from the Hindu Kush regions, this heavy indica strain provides a subtle earthy flavour with hints of citrus to deliver a classic kush experience.

Product Short Description: The Lobo blunts are made from natural hemp with glass tip, and are packed with Golden Pineapple.
Product Long Description: The Lobo blunts are made from natural hemp with glass tip, to make sure you have a clean and unimpeded blunt experience. This blunt is packed with Golden Pineapple which is a hybrid cross between Golden Goat and Pineapple Kush. The dominant terpenes are ocimene, farnesene-2 and limonene.

If it’s mainstream, it’s not for us. That's why this unique strain is one of our favourites that we turn to when we're looking to kickback. Kalifornia genetics root back to Nepali OG and 88 G-13 Hashplant. This pre-roll has a  total of up to 1.8% terpenes, which brings forward spicy, woody, and earthy tones. Every pack of Kolab Project pre-rolls is packaged in a biodegradable carton with post-consumer waste recyclable tray. To ensure the highest quality smoke, each pack has a resealable freshness peel-back seal that can be resealed after opening.

Product Short Description: This 60% indica-dominant hybrid strain boasts a perfume and flavour of flowery citrus notes, cookie dough and a hoppy, peppery tartness.
Product Long Description:
Harts pre-rolls are made entirely of Biscotti Gushers flower and do not contain any shake or trim. This 60% indica dominant strain is a true hybrid that expresses traits of both the sativa and indica flower. The terpene profile provides a flavour of flowery citrus notes, cookie dough and a hoppy, peppery tartness. Biscotti Gusher is an extremely popular smoke and ideal for hybrid connoisseurs.

Using state of the art technology Harts pre-rolls are machine-rolled and hand-packed to ensure consistency for customer satisfaction. Harts utilises a slow burning rod paper and a hollow acetate mouthpiece to allow for a full-flavoured experience.

Product Short Description: This 80% indica-dominant strain boasts a perfume of pungent gas, sweet vanilla and flowery caramel. Perfect for connoisseurs that enjoy heavy indicas.
Product Long Description:

The terpene profile: caryophyllene, myrcene, and humulene, provides a flavour of pungent gas, sweet vanilla, and flowery caramel. Pink Gas is perfect for connoisseurs looking for that gas-like heavy indicas.

Using state of the art technology Harts pre-rolls are machine-rolled and hand packed to ensure consistency for customer satisfaction. Harts utilises a slow burning rod paper and a hollow acetate mouthpiece to allow for a full-flavoured experience.

Product Short Description: Organic Rockstar Tuna is a high-THC, high-terpene cultivar with an intense aroma, gorgeous buds, and unique flavour profile  in a reusable green tin.
Product Long Description: Organic Rockstar Tuna Pre-Rolled 3-pack is a high-THC, high-terpene 3-pack of 0.5 g pre rolls in a reusable green tin. Grown in living soil, this adored indica strain was originally created by crossing the classic strains Tuna Kush and Rockstar. It has made a name for itself thanks to its intense aroma, gorgeous buds, and unique flavour profile that combines fruity-skunk, and spicy herbs. Our Organic Rockstar Tuna cultivar delivers high THC with a unique and high potency terpene profile that brings alpha-humulene, alpha-bisabolol, and beta-caryophyllene to the forefront.

Product Short Description: Organic Sugar Bush is a high-THC, high-terpene sativa that’s full-bodied, and full of fruity, skunk aroma reminiscent of ripe melon and passion fruit.
Product Long Description: Organic Sugar Bush Pre-Rolled 3-pack is a high-THC, high-terpene sativa 3-pack of 0.5 g pre rolls in a reusable green tin. Grown in living soil, this trichome-covered high-THC sativa gets its Sugar Bush name from the maple tree forests in Quebec — the source of maple syrup that is used to nurture the soil it grows in. The end result, a strain that is full-bodied, and full of aroma — bringing with it a fruity, skunk scent that is reminiscent of ripe melon and passion fruit.

Product Short Description: Everything a true sativa should be. Uplifting lemon and citrus notes with energetic spice, earth and zesty aromas from its distinct terpene profile.
Product Long Description: Amnesia Haze is everything a true sativa should be. Uplifting lemon and citrus notes accompanied by energetic spice, earth and zesty aromas from its distinct terpene profile that stays true to her landrace sativa origins. This sativa marvel should satisfy even the most discerning with its lime green buds and delicate texture that is thickly covered in oily trichomes. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang-cured and hand-trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Product Short Description: Kush Mints buds are exceptionally shaped with bright green and purple colouration, hidden under the thick covering of crystals with notes of mint.
Product Long Description: Kush Mints is one of the most densely trichome covered buds the growers at Broken Coast have ever seen. The buds are exceptionally shaped with bright green and purple colouration, hidden under the thick covering of crystals. Expect a thick dusting of kief to form on everything that touches these buds. Rife with notes of mint, hash and a subtly fruity scent, you’ll want to experience this quality hybrid again and again. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang-cured and hand-trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Product Short Description: A dense indica flower with deep purple and silver colouration, the large swollen calyxes are covered so thickly in  trichomes they're almost white.
Product Long Description: Sunset Sherbet is one of the more coveted cultivars ever grown by Broken Coast. Exhibiting dense indica flowers with deep purple and silver colouration, the large swollen calyxes are covered so thickly in glandular trichomes they're almost white. With the most abundant terpenes being caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene, Sunset Sherbet may be our most fruit-forward strain yet, evoking the truly unique smell and taste of a basket of strawberries and guava. But don’t let those rich aromas fool you, there’s prominent dank and pungent undertones that any great cannabis cultivar should have. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang cured and hand trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Our Pink Bubba joints are just that, Well Made.

Product Short Description: Subtle notes of sweet melon and under-ripe banana, and the classic sweet earth and dank hash flavour comes through, courtesy of its OG Kush heritage.
Product Long Description: A lineage of giants - a bit Kush, part Haze and traces of Skunk - Banana OG is not your average loaf. Subtle notes of sweet melon and under-ripe banana on the nose, but upon taste the classic sweet earth and dank hash flavour comes through, courtesy of its OG Kush heritage. Banana OG is as pungent as it is potent, and like its lineage suggests, is a cultivar for lovers of legacy genetics.

Product Short Description: One of the most complex terp profiles and as striking on the nose as it is visually, with purple patches and green shades under a heavy coat of resin.
Product Long Description: Taking our deep roots in cultivation to the next level, Qwest reserve is a testament to our grower's seed bank and the treasure trove we've gathered in hard-to-find, but sought-after genetics. Here you'll find limited lots, selective releases of only the most high-caliber but seldom listed cultivars. These are genetics with a groundswell elsewhere, but not yet discovered on Canadian soil. Discover something different, but altogether special, with our Qwest Reserve. A clash of red fruits: Grape Stomper collides with Cherry Pie - how can you not love this combination? Grape Pie while purple and fruity in name, offers one of the most complex terp profiles to date. Concord grape jelly with a bit of white grape juice is present on the nose, but the flavour is all sweet, diesel-rich earth with a bit of spice - maybe cinnamon raisin? You be the judge. Regardless, Grape Pie is as striking on the nose as it is visually with mauve purple patches and shades of green in a heavy resin undercoats.

Product Short Description: While notes of cherry are present, the unique, pungent and altogether musky aroma of GMO plays through when first taking whiff of Redneck Wedding.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest, and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Make no mistake, this is neither a cake nor a cookies varietal. Redneck Wedding comes from crossing Trophy Wife with GMO. While notes of cherry are present, the unique, pungent and altogether musky aroma of GMO plays through when first taking whiff of Redneck Wedding. Once ground you'll find the musk from a vintage store fades away and gives rise to a lovely nuttiness, coffee ground and spice, with fuel upon exhale. Dark green dense buds are completely frosted, making this trichome rich bud as white as a wedding.

Product Short Description:
This cultivar smells like a freshly-iced blackberry strudel - fruit-forward, with undertones
of fuel, Canadian maple, and mulled spice.
Product Long Description: Our Blackberry Gelato pre-roll smells like a freshly-iced blackberry strudel - fruit-forward, with undertones of fuel, Canadian maple, and mulled spices. Limonene, farnesene, and linalool exaggerate the light-but-fruity overall flavour, rounded out with myrcene. The ripe flowers are round, very dense, and sticky - especially once cured. Visually, they're a West Coast Rainforest-green, with hints of dark purple throughout, contributing to the cultivar's name. Product Long Description: Platinum Cookies are nothing like your sorta weird relative’s cookie recipe. Sure, it’s a sativa that’s a whole lot of sweet and a little bit spicy, with just a hint of berry. Yes, it’s smoke is rich and silky smooth (you’d expect that from a recipe handed down from OG Kush and Durban Poison). Platinum Cookies aren’t soft and chewy, but they are sure to steal the show. Ready to share, find 10 x .5g pre-rolls packed in a resealable pop top box with an air-tight freshness seal and humidity pack included. Product Short Description: Rolled Jean Guy is a ready to enjoy pre-roll for a no fuss, portable experience.
Product Long Description: Rolled Jean Guy is a ready to enjoy pre-roll for a no fuss, portable experience. This hybrid strain is a unique balance of a sweet citrusy and woody aroma with bold and sweet notes characteristic of this French-Canadian legend, it has a distinct pungent aroma.

Product Short Description: Chocolate Marshmallows is an exotic, limited edition 50/50 hybrid of the well known and potent GG#4 crossed with Mint Chocolate Chip.
Product Long Description: Our Jenn's OG pre-rolls are single strain consisting of nothing but our Chocolate Marshmallows flower. We have put utmost focus on maintaining the pure taste of the bud in its pre-rolled form and to keep it an exclusively cannabis product across all of its components. Pre-rolls are rolled in ultra-thin hemp paper allowing for a slow and even burn. We further treat them to food grade filter tips made of pure hemp and featuring bio-cooling technology to cool down the smoke without foregoing any of the flavour. The combination of passionately cultivated strains, a gentle processing and their elegant, fully bio-degradable filters made of pure hemp material makes Jenn's OG pre-rolls a true connoisseur piece prone to become the next benchmark.

Product Short Description: Amherst Sour Diesel has a gassy aroma and delivers a complex flavour profile of ripe fruit, incense, and exotic wood.
Product Long Description: Amherst Sour Diesel is a Chemdog and Amherst Super Skunk, Sativa-forward cross that features elongated, bright green, compact buds. In addition to a gassy aroma, it also delivers a complex flavour profile with a powerful punch of ripe fruit, incense, and exotic wood. Our single-strain pre-rolls are made from all bud – not shake – and rolled with a lightweight, organic hemp paper and mouthpiece for a smooth, even burn. We hang-dry and hand trim pre-rolls and then package them inside FSC-certified cardboard boxes, fresh-sealed inside a 100% recyclable, child-resistant pouch for optimal moisture content and shelf-life.

Product Short Description: Billy's Pheno features the latest drop that was selected by our Flower Manager for its unique terpene profile, bag appeal, and cannabinoid profile.
Product Long Description: At Carmel, incredible flower all starts with a pheno hunt, where we work through hundreds of seeds to find our unicorn. Billy's Pheno features the latest drop that was selected by our Flower Manager for its unique terpene profile, bag appeal, and cannabinoid profile.

Product Short Description: Sativa-dominant strain with a limonene, myrcene, linalool terpene profile. Diesel, citrus and cake notes.
Product Long Description: Say hello to Rosy AF - the first-ever pre-roll experience from SuperFlower! Filled with the coveted Animal Face strain, you get an undeniable diesel aroma complemented with notes of cake and citrus in this convenient multi-pack. This sativa is crafted with care in collaboration with our friends at Carmel. Is it irradiated? Nope. Is it full of flavour? You bet!

Product Short Description: The pinnacle of GreenSeal’s genetic selection program, this indica-heavy phenotype blends ultra-high THC with the comforting aroma of blueberry pie.
Product Long Description: After testing hundreds of Gorilla Berry seedlings for terpenes, bud structure, and potency, GreenSeal’s genetic selection program discovered this true unicorn combining the sweet, fruity flavours of blueberries and citrus with high THC potential. Upon opening a container, the sensation is the unforgettable smell of a freshly baked blueberry pie cooling on the windowsill. The rich mix of terpenes (headlined by tart pinene and balanced with peppery caryophyllene and musky myrcene) mingle to impart more subtle earthy/spicy flavours beneath the sweet berry overtones. GreenSeal’s pre-rolls use unbleached Dutch paper cones designed with a slim profile for a longer, smoother, consistent burn. Each pre-roll contains top shelf flower and is packaged and sealed by hand to ensure freshness and quality.

Product Short Description: A no-holds-barred strain that leaves its mark with a heady citrus and woody aroma. On the first draw a subtle garlic, spice and diesel flavour.
Product Long Description:
Halcyon selected Garlic Z as its first cultivar BECAUSE ‘garlic’ is not for everybody. The name will challenge some, others will be fully attracted to its promise. This is a heady citrus and woody cultivar that has some subtle hints of garlic with an undertone of spice and diesel. There are as many cultivars as people with different taste preferences. Halcyon salutes you all but first introduces Garlic Z - a strain for the more refined palette.

Lineage: GMO Cookies x OZ Kush
Of course, terps vary by lot but this sun-grown cultivar achieves consistently high terpenes with an average of 4.4%
Main terpenes: caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, limonene, linalool

TOP NOTES: Heady Citrus & Woody
HEART NOTES: Subtle Garlic
BASE NOTES: Spice & Diesel

Made only from our finest flower and rolled in paper made without animal products from mills that use sustainable forestry practices. 1 x 0.5g pre-roll so you can easily discover Garlic Z. 

Make it a Halcyon Day.

Product Short Description: High potency, single-strain pre-rolls made with whole bud from UP20™ Ghost Train Haze flower that is served up in a convenient three-pack.
Product Long Description: High potency, single-strain pre-rolls. Made with whole bud from UP20™ Ghost Train Haze flower that is served up in a convenient three-pack. We take special care to preserve freshness and ensure a great burn. Sun grown in hybrid greenhouses, Ghost Train Haze is a highly potent sativa known for its fluffy, bright green buds and dense, frosty trichome coverage. Expect to be hit by this runaway train of sour citrus and floral aromas, derived from the dominant terpinolene and complimentary ocimene and caryophyllene and hazy pinene.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid pre-roll with very strong THC potency potential and sweet tropical fruit and sour earth flavour.
Product Long Description: Acai Berry Gelato pre-rolls from Dunn Cannabis are indica-dominant with very strong THC potency potential. They offer a fruity flavour profile with notes of citrus, sweet tropical fruit and sour earth from limonene, farnesene and caryophyllene. Rolled with care inside each pre-roll is a deep purple and green cultivar covered in trichome crystals. A fruity, limited-edition concoction not to be passed up, but most definitely around.

Product Short Description: Includes our sweet and sour indica dominant Zktlz Glue, our sugary sativa dominant Blck Cndylnd and our zingy sativa dominant Electric Punch.
Product Long Description: Sample the best of bold with our Craft Sampler pack! Includes our famous Gelato (Sunset Sherbet x Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies), our sweet and sour Zktlz Glue (Zktlz x GG#4), and our newest addition, Blck Cndylnd (Candyland x Animal Cookies x Blackberry Kush). The best things always come in threes! Whole flower and hand finished, just the way your pre-rolls should be.

Product Short Description: Ghost Drops First Class Funk Blunt has a pungent, funky, creamy, fragrance compounded by a dense scent of jet fuel.
Product Long Description:
Ghost Drops First Class Funk Blunt was bred by Compound Genetics, hunted by Cultivating Happiness and grown by several ultra-premium, hand selected, and vetted craft micro-producers.  The genetic make-up of this strain contributes to what it’s best known for, its funk.
 
Its heavy nose smacks you in the face as you open the package, with a pungent funky, creamy, fragrance compounded by a dense scent of jet fuel, making for an undeniably dank aroma. The funk tastes as funky as it smells with notes of fermented anise and fennel coupled by gassy aftertaste as it rolls off the palate.

Product Short Description: Ghost Drops Z-Splitter Blunt was bred by Uprising Seed Co, hunted by Cultivating Happiness at Mother Labs and grown by Natural Earth Craft Cannabis.
Product Long Description: Ghost Drops Z-Splitter Blunt was bred by Uprising Seed Co, hunted by Cultivating Happiness at Mother Labs and grown by ultra-premium craft micro-producer, Natural Earth Craft Cannabis.

Product Short Description: Ghost Drops Khalifa Mints is an indica-dominant cross between Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. A heavy and fruity nose, followed by pungent peppermint.
Product Long Description:
Ghost Drops Khalifa Mints is an indica-dominant hybrid cross between Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. It’s hunted by Rockstar Canadian cultivators Headwater Cannabis and grown locally in a micro craft facility. 

Khalifa Mints is noticeable upon appearance due to its dense, light dark green buds, caked with trichomes, and highlighted by bright hairs. Its nose is heavy, fruity at first scent followed by notes of pungent peppermint and its flavor is dominated by menthol with hints of citrus followed by a gassy aftertaste.  

Ghost Drops is thrilled to continue our relationship with Headwater Cannabis in the legal market, holding true to our promise: “No Ghost left behind.”

Product Short Description: Drift’s Cyber Fuel OG Pre-Rolls includes 7 x 0.5-gram pre-rolls of Cyber Fuel OG, a cultivar with unique notes of orange cream soda and gas.
Product Long Description: Drift’s Cyber Fuel OG Pre-Rolls is a convenient way to experience the latest cannabis cultivars on the go. Every pack includes 2 x 0.5-gram pre-rolls of Cyber Fuel OG — a hybrid strain bred from OG Kush and Wedding Cake genetics. The taste and aroma profile of Cyber Fuel OG features unique and rare notes of orange cream soda and savoury garlic, followed by a pungent gas finish — from its primary terpenes, limonene, beta-myrcene, and trans-caryophyllene. Every Cyber Fuel OG Pre-Roll contains whole milled flower, and never shake. Expertly rolled for a smooth burning experience every time.

Product Short Description: Drift’s Alien Cake 3030 Pre-Rolls includes 7 x 0.5-gram pre-rolls of Alien Cake 3030, a strain with citrus, cake, and cream cheese notes.
Product Long Description: Drift’s “Alien Cake 3030 Pre-Rolls” is a convenient way to experience the latest cannabis cultivars on the go. Every pack includes 2 x 0.5-gram pre-rolls of Alien Cake 3030 – a sativa hybrid bred from Miracle Alien Cookies. The taste and aroma profile of Alien Cake 3030 contains unique notes of orange cream soda and savoury garlic, followed by a pungent gas finish – from its primary terpenes, trans-caryophyllene, terpinolene and limonene. Every Alien Cake 3030 Pre-Roll contains whole milled flower, and never shake. Expertly rolled for a smooth burning experience each time.

Product Name: Go Steady Sunshine Bubble Kush Pre-Rolls
Product Short Description: A cross of Sunshine State’s Triangle Kush and the dank, bubble hash-esque ‘88 G13 Hashplant. A sugary, earthy flavour with a gentle, spicy aroma.
Product Long Description: Go Steady Sunshine Bubble Kush is a balanced hybrid created by crossing the Sunshine State’s Triangle Kush with the dank, bubble hash-esque ‘88 G13 Hashplant. The strain has a sugary, earthy flavour with a gentle, spicy aroma of cloves and pine, followed by a citrusy perfume. The bud is compact and quite dense, with deep purple, almost black sugar leaves. It’s known for producing extremely potent flowers. FIGR dried flower products are hand selected to ensure dense, high-quality buds are in every package.

Tommy's Grape Galena is a high THC and CBG strain grown in the west, known for its silvery dense buds that resemble moon rocks. This glistening indica brings with it notes of cherry, sour berries and grape candy, derived from myrcene, caryophyllene, humulene and limonene. All our pre-rolls are hand-packed only with flower. What's more, our reusable and recyclable container will keep each pre-roll fresh from the first to the last, maintaining terpenes and locking in moisture. Enjoy this cross between OGKB, Lost Sailor and Platinum Kush.

Product Short Description: Temple Kush has herbal aromas that complement mixed flavours of earth, liquorice and a touch of diesel.
Product Long Description:
Temple Kush, a popular child of Nepalese Hashplant and Hindu Kush, has herbal aromas that complement mixed flavours of earth, liquorice and a touch of diesel. 

Delicately rolled by highly trained staff, our pre-rolls are hand finished via our industry-leading seven-points of contact — ensuring every joint, looks, feels, and burns consistent. Finally, our pre-rolls are hand-packaged in recyclable containers.

Rosetta Stone, a sativa-dominant child strain of Jack Herer, celebrates light, sweet, citrus flavours with a slightly sour citrus exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a peppery herbal overtone that sweetens as it burns, unlocking a slew of rich trichomes.

Delicately rolled by highly trained staff, our pre-rolls are hand finished via our industry-leading seven-points of contact – ensuring every joint, looks, feels, and burns consistent. Finally, our pre-rolls are hand-packaged in recyclable containers.

Product Long Description: RAD Pink Haze Blunts offer a sativa strain with flavours of sweet vanilla and candy, expertly rolled with premium hemp wraps.

The effects of this product can be felt within seconds to minutes, and can last for up to 6 hours or more. Some effects could last as long as 24 hours.

Product Short Description: Ace Valley pre-rolls made using Wappa, an indica strain that delivers a deep tropical fruity flavour and aroma.

Product Short Description: A cross of Blueberry x Cherry Pie Kush, this cultivar reinterprets the fresh fruit, dank kush elements of its parents into a spiced, potent berry jam.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest, and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. If berry terps are what you seek then look no further. Qwest Blueberry Syrup brings you notes of sweet, fermented black currents. A cross of Blueberry and Cherry Pie Kush, this cultivar reinterprets the fresh fruit and dank kush elements of its parents into a spiced and potent berry jam. It's a compote for those who prefer an indica lean.

Product Short Description: There’s a savoury quality that dials up the elements of GMO from its Redneck Wedding parent intermixed with the potent, unmistakable Animal Mints.
Product Long Description: Taking our deep roots in cultivation to the next level, Qwest Reserve is a testament to our grower's seed bank and the treasure trove we've gathered in hard-to-find, but sought-after genetics. Here you'll find limited lots, selective releases of only the most high-caliber but seldom listed cultivars. These are genetics with a groundswell elsewhere, but not yet discovered on Canadian soil. Discover something different, but altogether special, with our Qwest Reserve. Under a bed, in a closet, or in a study covered in rich leather and mahogany lies Grandpa's Tool Shed. Bits of sawdust, aged cedar and musk are the first to hit your nose. Breaking apart these dense buds will make you think perhaps they were covered in sap with each resin rich bit giving way to lilac and wet earth mixed with a pile of autumn leaves. There's a savoury quality that dials up the rank elements of GMO from its Redneck Wedding parent intermixed with the heavy, unmistakable Animal Mints.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant strain from it's lineage of GMO and Orange Zktlz.
Product Long Description: This pheno of Turpy Slurpy is a strong indica. The flavour and aroma profiles are fascinating, stemming from its lineage of GMO and Orange Zktlz. Sweet, citrus and earthy notes abound and come partnered with very high THC levels.

The sweet candy aromas are complemented with earthy, citrus undertones. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non irradiated. This is single strain, whole bud, milled to perfection and rolled with 100% organic hemp papers and finished by hand.

Product Short Description: Island Gold is a cross between Triangle Kush 88 & G13 Hashplant. Notes are citrusy pine and roasted coffee. 2 convenient pre-rolls per pack.

This flower expresses a citrusy pine and roasted coffee aroma and a sweet & spicy citrus flavour in a convenient 2-pack of ready-to-spark half gram pre-rolls. We give back to the First Nations community by donating a portion of proceeds to the Strong Roots North Charitable Foundation.

Product Short Description: Citrus Orchard pre-rolls are full of bright citrus flavour, complemented by notes of spice and earth.

Product Long Description: Sweet name with a skunk lineage carefully chosen for its distinct traits. Lemon Pound Cake is known for the juicy aromas of sugary lemon, skunk and sharp gas. With buds that are bright green and caked in trichomes with curly orange hairs. Who knew skunk could be so sweet?

Jungle Cake has a sweet, fruity berry flavour with hints of marshmallow and nuttiness. The aroma is piney with a fresh fruity overtone that's both sweet and spicy. Jungle Cake is an extremely popular smoke and ideal for hybrid connoisseurs. Nepali OG, aka Nepali Kush, is a long-lineage classic close to Tahoe OG that brings conical-shaped buds and earthy notes of an OG aroma, while Snow Lotus lays an undercurrent of black cherry and subtle hints of liquorice. The colas of Pacific OG are caked, hand-harvested, and cured, providing a full flavour due in part to dominant terpenes of pinene and nerolidol.

Dominant terpenes include Caryophyllene, Limonene, and Terpineol. This strain is a true quad that tests higher on THC levels. This strain, like all Broken Coast strains, is grown indoors in strain specific rooms, slow cured and hand trimmed preserving the quality and large dense buds Broken Coast is known for. (80% Indica / 20% Sativa)

Beautifully coloured fox tailed buds with purples, blues and gold tints have such dense calyxes, so thickly coated with resin, the growers at Broken Coast aptly named this one Frost Monster. Dominant terpenes include caryophyllene, limonene and linalool which help create the sweet, sour and spicy aromas along with peppery, earthy, spicy flavours. Gabriola, like all Broken Coast strains, is grown indoors in small batches in strain specific rooms then slow cured and hand trimmed. (80% Indica / 20% Sativa)

This sativa dominant strain is grounded by fresh and fruity notes, exhibiting subtle, natural sweetness with spice and almost tropical flavours on the exhale. Like all Broken Coast strains, is one is grown indoors in small batches in strain specific rooms then slow cured and hand trimmed to ensure the integrity of the flower. (10% Indica / 90% Sativa)

This bright green sativa dominant strain is rounded and well-balanced and retains the best qualities of its infamous parents. Just like every Broken Coast product, Ruxton is grown in strain specific room in small batches and is slow cured and hand trimmed by passionate and dedicated staff. (30% Indica / 70% Sativa)

Product Long Description: Cherry Bomb from JC Green is an exceptionally high THC potency sativa-dominant hybrid strain that produces dense, light green buds with golden-orange pistils and a thick frosting of trichomes. Cherry Bomb delivers a refreshing earthy aroma of sweet flowers derived from a diverse terpene palette of beta-caryophyllene, beta-pinene, d-limonene, nerolidol and linalool. Cherry Bomb’s lineage is complex and features popular parents like OG Kush, Tangerine Dream, Head Hunter and a Hawaiian Sativa Landrace strain. Cherry Bomb plants are grown with the utmost care in small batches before they are hang-dried, slow-cured, and delicately hand-trimmed and then packaged fresh to preserve their true elegance.

Product Short Description: Our product has significant levels of myrcene which give off spicy, woody, and ripe flavours.
Product Long Description: This indica flower has a consistently high potential of THC potency. This narrow-leafed, full of flower plant has an overabundance of trichomes from its flowery center carrying on throughout its trim and leaves. The amount of snow-like substance found on the flower is reminiscent of a winter wonderland. Our product has significant levels of myrcene which give off spicy, woody, and ripe flavours. Lemon Pepper Spice gives off the aroma of cantaloupe and melon which are accented by the spiciness (ocimene). Overall, the flower has a sweet and herb like flavour (guaiol). Our product as identified in its name, is home grown and hand nurtured at our greenhouse facility, steps from the Niagara Escarpment. The Niagara Region is one of the oldest parts of Canada so it links well with the older of the terpenes guaiol, which can be traced back to the 16th century.

Product Short Description: Sweet, creamy notes of vanilla, dough, and after dinner mints, this is a strain for the modern cannabis connoisseur. Made with 100% milled flower.
Product Long Description: With a thick, sticky layer of sugar-like resin like and sweet, creamy notes of vanilla, dough, and after dinner mints, ICC x Kush Mints 11 is a strain for the modern cannabis connoisseur. Pre-rolls are made with 100% milled flower.

Product Short Description: California Dreaming contains our highest grown level of THC. This flower is hand groomed from seed-to-sale.
Product Long Description: California Dreaming contains our highest grown level of THC. This flower is hand groomed, from seed-to-sale, and grown under natural sunlight with the assistance of LED lights. This indica-dominant flower is derived from flowers known as Hash Plant and Northern Lights. The earthy combination of alpha pinene and beta pinene brings you the sweet smell of pine trees. While pinene is the most widely encountered terpene in nature, underneath the earthy aroma is a hint of spice brought on by beta caryophyllene. California Dreaming is grown in the heart of Niagara's world renown grape and wine country. At Dykstra Greenhouses we take great care in hand grooming our flower to bring you our best product.

Dank Rainbow’s buds are covered with frosty crystals, orange hairs with dark green and ultraviolet undertones. The smell of D. Bubba’s sour aroma is balanced with the sweetness of the Rainbow Punch. The terpene profile is dominated by myrcene followed by caryophyllene and limonene. spicy, sour and of course DANK!

This bud is grown in strain-specific micro-climate conditions that are inspired by the mountainous environments indica thrives in. Product Long Description:

Our version of Animal Face was selected out of 100 different phenos, not only for its high potency and terpene profile, but also because of its unique flavours of lemon and cake. 
Because it’s just the right thing to do, all our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch that features a perfect airtight seal.
Non irradiated, obviously.

The sweet aromas come from a dominant limonene terpene profile, also found in lemons and oranges and balanced with skunky, diesel notes from β-Caryophyllene and humulene. Product Long Description: Designed for exclusive interface with G Pen Gio® Cartridges, the G Pen Gio Battery features an ergonomic and durable zinc-alloy casing and powerful 180 mAh battery with pass-through charging via micro USB.

Product Short Description: Includes a 510 thread rechargeable lithium ion battery and USB charger – calibrated specifically for B40 Vape Cartridges (sold separately).
Product Long Description: The Back Forty Vape Battery & Charger includes a 510 thread rechargeable lithium ion battery and USB charger. The Back Forty Vape Battery is calibrated specifically for B40 Vape Cartridges. Back Forty Vape Cartridges are sold separately.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: Rechargeable, safety-certified vape battery with push-button activation, three power settings and micro-USB charging port.
Product Long Description: -ness rechargeable vape batteries not only offer the convenience of push-button activation and three power settings, but they’re also independently verified for safety through Health Canada’s UL 8139 certification, which means they have been evaluated across the battery, heating, electrical and charging systems so you can feel confident that they are safe to use. Cartridge sold separately.

Product Short Description: Easy to use for the simplest experience. Longer lasting pods deliver full flavour from start to finish. Extended battery life in PAX’s compact design.
Product Long Description: Instant on. Just use your pod to switch between 4 temperature settings for best flavour and vapor. Full-flavor, hand-selected strains: Local, high-quality cannabis, curated for the best, natural flavours. Perfected over a decade: PAX’s smallest device yet. 150 puffs per charge and easy-to-read LEDs ensure it's always ready.

Product Name: The Snack Pack: Sour OG Cheese
Product Short Description: The Snack Pack: Sour OG Cheese is craft quality flower in a convenient compact container. Break off a bite or pop the whole thing in your pipe.
Product Long Description: The Snack Pack: Sour OG Cheese comes by its name honestly, as the obvious funk of sour cheese and earthy aromas fill the air where it grows and chunky, colourful flowers produce potent, sturdy buds. This cross between Kosher Kush x Citral Skunk and Colin OG offering is discreetly and can be enjoyed in either your bowl or pre-roll.

Product Name: Thin Mint GSC x Sunset Sherbet
Product Short Description: Thin Mint GSC and Sunset Sherbet combine the sweet aromas of both cultivars to produce a well-balanced hybrid strain with notes of earth and mint.
Product Long Description: Thin Mint GSC and Sunset Sherbet combine the sweet aromas of both cultivars to produce a well-balanced hybrid strain with notes of earth and mint. Bright orange pistils cover the mint green buds, and just like a sweet dessert, are sugared in frosty trichomes.

Product Short Description: Edison Trop Juice is a sativa dominant cross between Tropicana Cookies x OG Kush Breath featuring a sweet orange juice aroma with a spicy pine finish.
Product Long Description: Edison Trop Juice is a potent sativa dominant cross between Tropicana Cookies (Mtn Cut) and OG Kush Breath. Much like the name suggests, this scintillating flower has a bold, sweet orange juice aroma up front and gets finished off with spicy pine. Rather than pulp this Trop Juice is painted with a heavy trichrome frost, making it almost too pretty to smoke. Trop Juice is a pretty potent flower.

Product Short Description: A hybrid strain with a slight sativa dominance strain and tropical flavour that is sweet, sticky, pumped up and highly potent.
Product Long Description: A hybrid strain with a slight sativa dominance strain and tropical flavour that is sweet, sticky, pumped up and highly potent. Covered with glistening, sweet tropical fruit scented trichomes, Tropicana Banana is a strain from Dutch breeder Barney’s Farm. This cultivar is a cross between Tropicana Cookies and Banana Kush. Tropicana Cookies is a cross between GSC and Tangie. Banana Kush is a cross between Ghost OG and Skunk Haze. Grown in Delhi, Ontario, this flower is the first in Canada to be kiln dried. Kiln-drying can remove as much as 90% of the moisture, making the product resistant to fungal decay.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: This phenotype of Turpy Slurpy is a strong indica. The flavour and aroma profiles stem from its lineage of GMO and Orange Zktlz.
Product Long Description: This phenotype of Turpy Slurpy is a strong indica. The flavour and aroma profiles are fascinating, stemming from its lineage of GMO and Orange Zktlz. Sweet, citrus and earthy notes abound and come partnered with high THC levels.

Product Short Description: Tweed Kush Mints is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD.
Product Long Description: Tweed Kush Mints is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD. Kush Mints comes from a cross of Animal Mints and Bubba Kush. Its buds are known to be dense and dark green with hints of lime. Some associate minty, earthy and pine flavours with the Tweed Kush Mints strain.

Product Short Description: Named for its super delicious flavour and gorgeous appearance, Jet Fuel Flo has a super sweet vanilla flavour with a lightly skunky pine exhale.
Product Long Description: Named for its super delicious flavour and gorgeous appearance, Jet Fuel Flo is the perfect bud for any indica lover. Jet Fuel Flo has a super sweet and sugary vanilla flavour with a lightly skunky pine exhale. RC Supply Co. is the name of the farmgate storefront on site of Medz Cannabis Inc., a unique federally licensed, small batch cannabis production and processing facility in the Greater Toronto Area. RC Supply Co. brings this offering of indoor-grown craft cannabis that is free of pesticides, non-irradiated, was hand harvested and trimmed after a long cure time.

Product Short Description: Bred By Compound Genetics. This strain is a cross of Pinesoul and Jet Fuel Gelato. The aroma is very gassy with earthy tones. Sticky dense buds.
Product Long Description: This broadleaf indica selected from Compound Genetics is a cross of Pinesoul and Jet Fuel Gelato. It takes after the Pinesoul with its lemony pledge taste and hints of fuel.

Product Short Description: Wappa by Redecan is an indica-dominant strain with a strong yet sweet aroma that verges on skunkiness, and strong THC potency.
Product Long Description: Standing firm at a moderate height and with a stocky build, Redecan Wappa is an indica-dominant strain, characterized by its large, densely packed flowers with a broad base, and tapered, pointed tip. Its flowers grow a beautiful green and yellow, sporting vibrant hues of purple in the fall as a response to its cooler growing environment. Wappa exudes an overwhelmingly skunky, yet fruity aroma, thanks to high levels of myrcene and caryophyllene. Consistently testing at high THC levels, Redecan's Wappa strain is the go-to choice for cannabis lovers across the nation. All of our bud is carefully harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand and inspected.

Product Short Description: Warlock by Redecan is an indica dominant strain (85:15) that was derived through purposeful breeding and backcrossing strains of Skunk #1 and Afghani.
Product Long Description: Warlock is a storied award winning indica dominant strain (85:15) that was derived through purposeful breeding and backcrossing classic strains of Skunk #1 and Afghani to extract favourable genetic traits. Warlock buds are characteristically dense and pepper shaped with emerald green hues with sparse thick furry orange hairs dusted with a fine sweet sticky layer of nearly translucent trichomes. This magical strain achieves a high THC level with a terpene profile that includes caryophyllene, myrcene and bisabolol which showcase its earthy skunky origins while elevated by its fragrant fruity sweet and sour nuances. Warlock by Redecan is further improved upon through the care and attention given to each plant through every stage of growth, harvest and curing that is complemented by being expertly hand trimmed to ensure high quality in every batch.

Product Short Description: Warlock by Redecan is an indica dominant strain (85:15) that was derived through purposeful breeding and backcrossing strains of Skunk #1 and Afghani.
Product Long Description: Warlock is a storied award winning indica dominant strain (85:15) that was derived through purposeful breeding and backcrossing classic strains of Skunk #1 and Afghani to extract favourable genetic traits.
