Product Short Description: Wedding Cake is an indica with a full-bodied berry-sweet flavour.
Product Long Description: Wedding Cake is an indica with a full-bodied berry-sweet flavour. Bred from Sour Hybrid, Cherry Pie, and GSC strains. Sealed for freshness with a humidity pack included. Discover the quality of Sundial cannabis, grown naturally in Alberta.

Product Short Description: Wedding Singer is a White Wedding, Kush Mints 11 cross with a green/silvery hue & the aroma of pine, frosted cereal, custard & a fuel/funk finish.
Product Long Description: Team MSIKU presents the first cross from their In-House breeding selections. Wedding Singer is the female 'White Wedding' crossed with the 'Kush Mints 11' Male. Wedding Singer is painted in a green, silvery hue and has astonishing resin production. The strain has the aroma of pine and frosted cereal on the top, custard in the middle, and is rounds out with fuel and funk on the bottom. Hang dried and hand trimmed to preserve aroma and flavour.

Product Short Description: A slightly indica-dominant hybrid strain created through crossing Purple Punch and Blissful Wizard strains, Wizard Punch brings on a heavy potency.
Product Long Description: Wizard Punch is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing Purple Punch and Blissful Wizard strains. New consumers of cannabis should start with a very low dose. Wizard punch brings on a heavy potency behind its high. It is perfect for those experienced smokers who can handle the very high THC levels of Wizard Punch. Wizard Punch has a sweet and creamy fruity berry flavour with a lightly peppery grape exhale. It has an aroma of sweet fruity berries with a heavily spicy earthy grape effect that lingers long after your final toke. Wizard Punch has fat-dense grape-shaped dusty green buds with dark purple undertones, furry orange hairs and a coating of frosty minty green crystal trichomes.

Product Short Description: Wreck & Leisure (Powdered Donuts) is a hybrid strain with a tangy aroma of sweet citrus. This flower yields a high level of THC.
Product Long Description: Wreck & Leisure (Powdered Donuts) is a hybrid strain, crossed between Jet Fuel Gelato (hybrid) and Orange Cookies (sativa-dominant). This robust flower has a tangy aroma of sweet citrus. A pleasant fruity citrus on the inhale and a sour earthy taste on the exhale. Wreck & Leisure consistently yields a high level of THC. Wreck & Leisure (Powdered Donuts) is a very dense, light green bud, covered with beautiful crystal trichomes and dense patches of fiery orange hairs.

Product Short Description: TF Pink Kush has a sweet, sour, and earthy profile. CanWe is Ontario grown in an indoor hydroponics setup fed by a deep fresh water source.
Product Long Description: TF Pink Kush is classic high-THC indica strain with an instantly recognizable sweet, sour, and earthy profile. CanWe is a minority owned producer located in Grand Valley, Ontario. From our deep fresh water source to the hydroponic small batch indoor grow and hang dry finish, every step of our process is designed to enhance and elevate the flower's natural characteristics.

Product Short Description: A potent but flavourful 50/50 hybrid strain with serious frost factor. Explosion of skunky, woodsy forest fruit aromas.
Product Long Description: Liiv THC bomb is a potent but flavourful 50/50 hybrid strain with serious frost factor, offering an explosion of skunky, woodsy forest fruit aromas. Packed with earthy aromas, THC Bomb will still surprise with hints of floral fermented fruits and skunky after-effects. Although potent in nature, THC Bomb was named for its typically bomb-shaped buds, those dense buds recognizable by their bright orange pistils and super frosty texture.

Product Name: The Craft Tasting Flight: Micro Edition
Product Short Description: A unique craft experience for the connoisseur. Limited Edition #2
Product Long Description: Welcome to Flight #2 – The Micro Edition. Crafted for connoisseurs, experience a curated selection of small batch handcrafted flower from some of Canada’s up-and-coming micros. Meticulously designed to offer a sampling of 3 premium cultivars which were hand-picked and packaged in a sleek, reusable box. A limited edition offering.

Product Short Description: BC grown Sour OG Cheese is dank in all the right ways. A craft cultivar that combines the best traits from (Kosher Kush x Citral Skunk) x Colin OG.
Product Long Description: BC grown Sour OG Cheese is dank in all the right ways. A craft cultivar that combines the best traits from (Kosher Kush x Citral Skunk) x Colin OG. The upfront sour notes are followed closely by earthy, gassy and floral undertones. A similar funk carries through the flavour of the thick, smooth smoke. The tight green buds have burnt-orange pistils and exceptional trichome coverage. Grown in BC by a micro producer with decades of legacy experience, every plant receives exceptional care, along with a hang dry, thorough hand trim and a three-week cure to achieve an exceptional end product.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and distinct vanilla and minty flavours.
Product Long Description: Sticky Buns from TABLE TOP is a flavourful indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and distinct vanilla and minty flavour from a terpene blend of caryophyllene, myrcene and linalool. The sticky name comes from the big, sticky trichomes that cover the dense, deep green buds. We’ll leave the buns up to your imagination, but you can rest assured It’s Got Legs™.

Product Short Description: Bred by In-house Genetics, is a high-THC indica-dominant cultivar. Expect a sweet, fruity fresh concord grape flavour with sour gas undertones.
Product Long Description: Supreme Grapes, bred by in-house genetics, is a high THC indica-dominant cultivar. Expect a sweet, fruity fresh concord grape flavour with sour gas undertones. These large bulbous calyxes are covered in dense trichomes and include a mix of green and purple tones. The bag appeal and aroma will keep your senses wanting more. Supreme Grapes is cultivated indoors, in precision-controlled environmental conditions. All Natural History flower is thoughtfully hung to dry, hand trimmed and cured for 21 to 30 days. This new seasonal cultivar from Natural History will be available for a limited time only.

Product Short Description: Dark green in colour with beautiful royal purple stripes, light green underbelly, bright orange pistils and a sweet aroma with herbal/hops undertones.
Product Long Description: Dark green in colour, with beautiful royal purple stripes and light green underbelly, with bright orange pistils. Chunky, medium-large, rounded elongated triangles in shape. Layers of sweetness aroma, with undertones of herbal/hops.

Product Short Description: Market leading THC. Certified organic, craft designated, and packaged in 100% home compostable packaging.
Product Long Description:
Coterie Select Pheno #7 is an elevated pheno-hunted variant of our Mendo Breath hybrid genetics. This indica-dominant potent cultivar features
2% terpenes. It is certified organic, craft designated, and packaged in 100% backyard compostable packaging. The dominant terpene profile of Caryophyllene, Eucalyptol, and Nerolidol offers a unique balance of earthy musk and sweet floral notes.

Product Short Description: Unique in Canada, Skullcap is an indica-leaning hybrid that delivers complex fruity flavours with an alluring diesel twist.
Product Long Description: Unique in Canada, Skullcap is an indica-leaning hybrid that delivers complex fruity flavours with an alluring diesel twist.

Product Name: Slap N Tickle by Frost Cannabis
Product Short Description: Micro-grown by Frost Cannabis, a cross of GMO and Grape Pie. Indica dominant with dank earthy spice and a sweet grape aroma.
Product Long Description: OMG presents, Slap N Tickle. Micro grown in soil by Frost Cannabis. Appropriately named, this indica dominant hybrid has a dank earthy spice with a sweet grape finish. This flower has legacy roots and is now grown freely. Elite clones, hang-dried, slow cured, hand-trimmed and hand-packaged, the way its always been. This premium small-batch harvest is limited in quantity, get it while it lasts!

Product Short Description: Dialling up the apple rind, sweet flesh and juicy elements of the MAC with the potent, dank and citrus rich diesel of Trophy Wife.
Product Long Description: Qwest est né d’une profonde appréciation de la plante et de son processus. Nous sommes ici pour le voyage que chaque producteur entreprend à chaque nouvelle récolte et nous respectons le fait que même avec les cultivars les plus familiers, il est toujours possible d’aller au-delà de l’ordinaire. Arrivez du côté mûr de l’AMC. Composez le zeste de pomme, la chair sucrée et les éléments juteux du MAC avec le diesel puissant, excellent et riche en agrumes de Trophy Wife vous donne plus que votre Red Delicious. Pas digne d’une tarte et certainement introuvable dans n’importe quel verger, Apple Mac vaut la peine.

Product Short Description: Cherry Cookies is an offshoot of GSC. It's dank, cakey and earthy with a kick of fruit, sweetness and potency thanks to its cross with The White.
Product Long Description: Qwest est né d’une profonde appréciation de la plante et de son processus. Nous sommes ici pour le voyage que chaque producteur entreprend à chaque nouvelle récolte et nous respectons le fait que même avec les cultivars les plus familiers, il est toujours possible d’aller au-delà de l’ordinaire. Givré, baie et très lumineux, rencontrez les biscuits aux cerises givrées. Cherry Cookies, une émanation de la dynastie génétique GSC, vous donne cette qualité riche, grasse et terreuse avec une touche de fruit et de douceur et une montée en gamme dans le département de la puissance grâce à son croisement avec The White. Il a un profil brillant et une saveur distincte qui reflète un cultivar Sour.

Product Short Description: Sour tart berries, a bit of chemical fumes and elements of diesel and pine, White Sherbet crossed with Jet Fuel Gelato will do that.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Sour tart berries, a bit of chemical fumes and elements of diesel and pine, White Sherbet crossed with Jet Fuel Gelato will do that. A cone dipped in petrol and sprinkled with whiffs of grape is what Icicle entails. Frosted buds to match the icy quality of its trichomes against colours of emerald and hues of purple.

Product Short Description: Bred by Cookies in California, RNTZ has an aroma of a creamy berry syrup with gassy notes and a fruity flavour with tropical citrus and sweet berries.
Product Long Description: Bred by Cookies in California and grown by Strains Ltd in Ontario. RNTZ is a 50/50 hybrid cross between Zktlz and Gelato #33. It carries a pungent aroma of creamy berry syrup with plenty of gassy notes followed by a super delicious fruity flavour with tropical citrus and sweet berries. The bag appeal is incredible. The colours range from purple and pink to shades that go as deep as a dark blackish purple, caked with trichomes.

Product Short Description: San Fernando Valley OG Kush is an indica-leaning cross of Larry OG and Legend OG.
Product Long Description: San Fernando Valley OG Kush is an indica-leaning cross of Larry OG and Legend OG. This legendary cultivar packs abundant earthy and diesel aromas with a very high concentration of flavourful terps.

Product Short Description: High potency Cali dessert strain offering sweet moorish fruit and cream aromas as well as a kushy punch. Bright, round, dense grape-like purple buds.
Product Long Description: It’s officially in Canada! Fan-favourite Grapes and Cream has landed. This famous high potency Cali dessert strain from Cannarado is a recognizable hybrid of Grape Pie and Cookies & Cream, offering sweet moorish fruit and cream aromas. But don’t be surprised by liiv G&C’s kushy punch among the cake and cookie profiles. True to its name, this first-gen grape strain has bright, round and frosty grape-like purple buds.

Product Short Description: G-13 Nepali is a potent indica hybrid known for its woody, earthy aroma and classic Kush flavour with sour and spicy undertones.
Product Long Description: G-13 Nepali is a potent indica hybrid known for its woody, earthy aroma. G-13 Nepali ties together a unique appearance reminiscent of a lush mountain forest with a classic Kush flavour highlighted by sour and spicy undertones, always at a consistent high THC profile. As an offspring of Nepali OG and G-13 Hashplant, its lineage has a mysterious background that is rumoured to have stemmed from a government research program in the ‘60s or ‘70s. Cultivated in BC by a seasoned team of growers, the lush green buds are coated in trichomes and vibrant orange pistils.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: This potent sativa strain is a cross between Purple Punch and Clementine. The buds are predominantly green but can also have a pink and orange hue.
Product Long Description: This potent sativa strain is a cross between Purple Punch and Clementine. The buds are medium density that are predominantly bright green but can also have a pink and orange hue. Woody, floral and earthy notes dominate the aroma but are balanced out with a bright citrus undertone. Purple Clementine #37 promises a smooth smoke that is full of citrus flavours but has sour and earthy nuances that bring balance. Purple Clementine #37 is a potent, bright and happy strain that delivers powerful sativa effects.

Product Short Description: A BLKMKT exclusive. Power-iced buds which are sweet, with hints of gas.
Product Long Description: Bred & Cultivated in BC. This pheno of Candy Rain x Cherry Punch produces beautifully large, power-iced buds which are dark purple and black. Imagine opening a pack of assorted candy, smashing them all up and taking a whiff.

Product Short Description: Sweet, savoury and stunning. This unique cultivar features tight buds with deep green and purple colouration, amber pistils and a coat of trichomes.
Product Long Description: Platinum Garlic is sweet, savoury and absolutely stunning. This unique cultivar features tight buds with remarkably deep green and purple colouration, fiery amber pistils and a thick coating of large, sticky trichomes. It’s a hybrid with high THC potency, 2-4% terpenes and features pungent onion and bold garlic aromas with an intense sweetness and a touch of vanilla owing to their abundant caryophyllene, myrcene and terpinolene terpenes. It’s a truly glorious strain that we can’t wait to share. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang cured and hand trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Product Short Description: 7ACRES Platinum Kush Breath is a high THC, high terpene indica leaning hybrid with a beautiful dense bud structure and abundant trichome coverage.
Product Long Description: 7ACRES Platinum Kush Breath is a high THC, high terpene indica leaning hybrid with a beautiful dense bud structure and abundant trichome coverage. This cultivar exhibits a pungent and complex aromatic profile of sweet lemon, fruity berry, funky earth and a hint of black pepper. Cross of OG Kush Breath and Platinum. Indoor grown in Ontario, whole plant hang dried and meticulously hand polished.

Product Short Description: Cookieberry OG is a 22-28% THC indica-dominant hybrid. You can’t miss its berry-forward flavour, complemented by an earthy sandalwood finish.
Product Long Description: Remember the excitement of shopping for your fav treat in the candy store? It’s similar to the feeling you’ll get right before you open this indica-dominant hybrid. Edison’s Cookieberry OG is bound to delight with its sweet and sour berry flavour complemented by an earthy sandalwood finish. Cookieberry OG is the sweet sweet offspring of Lemon Berry Candy OG x Ethos Cookies. Don’t let its bold, yet pleasant aromas fool you — Cookieberry OG is not for beginners, with a THC range of 22-28%.

Product Short Description:
The Micro Batch facility houses and cultivates exclusive genetics that are released in limited drops,
province by province.
Product Long Description:
The Micro Batch facility houses and cultivates exclusive genetics that are released in limited drops,
province by province.

Product Short Description: WINK CRAFT BLUEBERRY SLURR is a fruity, gassy hitter, with frosted lime-green and purple buds. The perfect balance of dank and sweet.
Product Long Description: WINK CRAFT BLUEBERRY SLURR is an indica-dominant cross of SlurriCrasher and Slurmint IX, originally a phenotype of In-House genetics “Slurrup”. This cultivar was hunted and grown by Noble Growth Corp and as a result, you can expect dense light green flowers with a beautiful blue and purple tint. Coined the "Blueberry Slurr” phenotype of Slurrup, it boasts notes of blueberry cream with a delicious dessert-like after taste. The unique blueberry-like qualities, along with fruity-gassy aromatics and high potency yields deliver a bomb experience. Craft grown by a team with over 60 years of combined legacy growing experience WINK CRAFT BLUEBERRY SLURR is indoor-grown, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and slow-cured to protect trichomes, preserve terpenes, and retain bud moisture. This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: Introducing Puffing Season, the deep hue buds of this sativa-dom are coated with frosty hairs and pack a flavour blast of musk, gas and lemons.
Product Long Description: Introducing Puffing Season, the newest limited-edition flower from Cruuzy. The Chem Cake strain is a rare, sativa-dominant hybrid that has scents of musk, gas and lemons. The deep hue buds of this sativa are coated with frosty hairs. Remember that Puffing Season isn’t here forever. One puff and you’ll be in love!

Product Short Description: An evenly-balanced hybrid cross of Blueberry, GG and OG Kush. This triple threat strain has a fruity, blueberry flavour with bright hints of citrus.
Product Long Description: Redecan Glueberry OG is an evenly-balanced hybrid strain characterized by bright green buds, orange pistils and frosty, white trichomes. With high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene and farnesene in its terpene profile, Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity and earthy aroma. Derived from crossing OG Kush, GG and Blueberry strains. Like all Redecan flowers, Glueberry OG is harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand, and inspected for quality.

Product Short Description: GMO Cookies have a dank and musty smell with diesel and citrus undertones.
Product Long Description: GMO Cookies is notorious for its high THC potency and powerful aromas. An all-star cross between Chemdawg x GSC, this indica strain has a massive aroma profile with a dank and musty smell right from the beginning, followed closely by an intense diesel and citrusy undertone. These potent crown-shaped buds are dark green with patches of purple and bright orange pistils. The colourful buds are dripping in a shiny layer of trichomes.

Product Short Description: Crafted by Prairie Craft Canopy in Richardson, SK. Homage Grape Escape provides sweet, sour and berry aromas with a hint of citrus.
Product Long Description: Crafted by Prairie Craft Canopy just outside of Regina, in the heart of Canada's agricultural breadbasket. Homage Grape Escape provides sweet, sour and berry aromas with a hint of citrus. Its deep purple buds are complemented with bright orange pistils. A hybrid strain with the lineage Grape Gas and Unknown. At Prairie Craft Canopy, we practice indoor grows, hand-trimming and a full-plant cure process. Homage connects you with each craft grower and their story. Because every story is different and just as meaningful as the next. This is why Homage simplifies cannabis for local producers and the people for whom they perfect their craft.

Product Short Description: WINK GRAPES & CREAM, an indica-dominant hybrid, has a sweet vanilla and tart grape profile. Cultivated carefully to yield full, round, frosty buds.
Product Long Description: WINK GRAPES & CREAM is an indica-dominant cross between Grape Pie and Cookies & Cream. Cultivated by the brilliant plant specialists at Greenway Pharma in Alberta, who take pride in growing in small batches with organic salt nutrients. Grown indoors in living soil, this strain is hand-watered, hand-manicured, and hang-dried as a whole plant for 10-14 days, then cured to perfection for 7-14 days. Bred by the legendary Cannarado Genetics this strain offers a fruity forward profile that provides a sweet-vanilla-like aroma, with tart grape flavours. This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: This potent indica has large dense buds covered in trichomes and stinks of gas. The buds have berry bright colours and are white from trichomes.

Hollywood OG has a kush-style aroma, meaning it’s dank and earthy, with a diesel mid-range, and is accented by citrus, and other tropical fruit notes, leaving you with a playful aftertaste and experience.

Plus, the Stinky Greens Organic greenhouse facility is a closed loop and CO2 enhanced, ensuring no elements from the outdoors make their way in. Grown using the sea of green method, Donny Burger is hand-watered then hang dried and cold-cured for 14 days. The buds are dry trimmed, then finished by hand—courtesy of the Master Grower—to keep the integrity and the trichomes intact. Stinky Greens Organic Larry Burger is a rare indica-dominant cultivar offering a savoury, funky and spicy terpene profile. This cross between Sticky Larry x Donny Burger produces green, frosty, and sticky, buds coated with high-resin trichomes.

Product Short Description: Selects cannabis flower.
Product Long Description: Simply Bare Selects is a collection of rare cultivars that we are testing in our greenhouse. Every few weeks, our growers assess what has performed the best on potency, bud size, trichome content and taste. We then select one standout cultivar to join the Selects rank. Every selection starts with our never irradiated whole bud, cold cured to perfection, then packed away in our moisture locking glass jars.

Brand: The Original Fraser Valley Weed Co.
Product Short Description: An unmistakable high-THC indica with pungent aromas of garlic, skunk and gas.
Product Long Description: Donny Burger is deliciously savoury, pungent and gassy — think grilled cheese and dark garlic in a bulk bag. This high-THC indica is a cross of GMO and Han Solo Burger. Dense green buds and tufts of orange hairs, our Donny Burger’s unmistakable bud is greenhouse grown in BC’s Fraser Valley.

Product Short Description: Presenting a new cannabis quality product. Offering sativa flower strains from across Canada.
Product Long Description: Presenting a new cannabis quality product from Weed Me. Offering sativa flower strains from across Canada. Weed Me Limited Batch products are packaged in sealed tinted glass jars with a pack of integra to preserve terpenes and flavour. The label includes both terpene and genetic information.

Product Short Description: Presenting a new cannabis quality product. Offering indica flower strains from across Canada.
Product Long Description: Presenting a new cannabis quality product from Weed Me. Offering indica flower strains from across Canada. Weed Me Limited Batch products are packaged in sealed tinted glass jars with a pack of integra to preserve terpenes and flavour. The label includes both terpene and genetic information.

Product Short Description: Versus Rockstar is an indica-dominant flower that delivers notes of spice, sweet fruit, skunk and pine.
Product Long Description: Versus Rockstar is an indica-dominant flower that delivers notes of spice, sweet fruit, skunk and pine.

Product Short Description: Terpee Slerpee is a cross of GMO and Orange Zktlz. Notable terpenes limonene, linaool and pinene bring serious flavour and a robust citrus profile.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. Terpee Slerpee represents the next generation of infamous West Coast genetics. It's a cross of GMO and Orange Zktlz. Notable terpenes limonene, linaool and pinene bring serious flavour and a robust citrus profile bolstered by a dank undercurrent and skunky aroma. Light, fluffy and frosted, Terpee Slerpee is the potent and flavourful product you can expect from the Qwest family.​

Product Short Description: Hectane is a cross between Hightech and Grandiflora Project 4516, featuring olive green buds, amber hairs and a blanket of white crystal trichomes.
Product Long Description: Bred by Grandiflora. Hectane is a cross between Hightech and Grandiflora Project 4516. This cultivar features oversized olive green buds with vivid amber hairs and a thick frosty blanket of glittering white crystal trichomes. Aromas of spicy mocha coffee and fruity herbs are released. The flavour is of sweet chocolate with hints of fresh ripe berries.

Product Short Description: When people tell you to “stay golden” there’s a good chance they’re talking about this super juicy and super fruity sativa.
Product Long Description: Is there anything better than strolling down a beach, sand sifting between your toes, sipping something fruity out of a coconut and scratching your back on a random palm tree you happen to pass by? Palmetto Tropicanna Gold is a super juicy and super fruity sativa. Get your hands on our iconic orange jar with humidity pack. Palmetto is grown by cannabis lovers for cannabis lovers, found somewhere deep in the mystic shadows of the majestic Rocky Mountains of Alberta.

Product Short Description: Peanut Butter Lava Cake is a unique blend of the rare Lava Cake and flavourful Do-Si-Dos. A rich chocolate aroma with hints of earth and spice.
Product Long Description: You’re in for a treat with these novel genetics. Legend’s Peanut Butter Lava Cake is a unique blend of the rare Lava Cake and flavourful Do-Si-Dos. A rich chocolate aroma is revealed with refreshing flavours of earth, spice and pine.

Product Short Description: JB Cookies greets you with sweet notes of apple pie, earth and gas. A potent hybrid that's a spin off on the renowned GSC and Romulan strains.
Product Long Description: JB Cookies greets you with sweet notes of apple pie, earth and gas. A spin off on the renowned GSC and Romulan strains, this potent hybrid does not fall far from the tree with an equally impressive THC profile. Grown indoors in BC, one of Canada’s top growing regions, these dense buds are frosted with trichomes and dazzling purple hues are complemented by vibrant orange hairs.

Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid grown in living soil using natural sunlight and purified rainwater. Pungent, frost-covered buds with roasted-cream flavour.
Product Long Description: Gold Butter MAC is an indica dominant hybrid, grown in living soil using natural sunlight and purified rainwater. This innovative TGOD original phenotype is grown from a Peanut Butter Breath and Quebec Gold male, and a MAC-1 female. The result is a truly unique cultivar, bringing pungent, frosty buds with smooth, roasted-cream flavour. Slow dried and cured, this unique high-THC strain produces sticky, large, floral buds that are easy-burning.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: A cross of Lemon Tree and Sour Diesel, this hybrid strain is crusted with large, sticky trichomes. It has citrus and fuel flavours.
Product Long Description: A cross of Lemon Tree and Sour Diesel, this hybrid strain is crusted with large, sticky trichomes. The flavour hits citrus and fuel heavily but maintains a distinct note of Kush. WAGNERS delivers on consistent quality and full flavour.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: WELL MADE by WAGNERS zips look to hit the right quality of flower, potency and price for the large format consumer. Featuring great genetics.
Product Long Description: WELL MADE by WAGNERS zips look to hit the right quality of flower, potency and price for the large format consumer. Featuring great genetics and the same high level of consistent quality that has made WAGNERS popular across Canada. WELL MADE is perfect for those looking for larger quantities of high quality cannabis.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: WELL MADE by WAGNERS zips look to hit the right quality of flower, potency and price for the large format consumer. Featuring great genetics.
Product Long Description: WELL MADE by WAGNERS zips look to hit the right quality of flower, potency and price for the large format consumer. Featuring great genetics and the same high level of consistent quality that has made WAGNERS popular across Canada. WELL MADE is perfect for those looking for larger quantities of high quality cannabis.

Product Short Description: This hybrid strain is a mix of Kosher Kush and Lemon Skunk, featuring a citrus and Kush flavour.
Product Long Description: Introducing the next cultivar from Golden Lemons. This hybrid cultivar is a mix of Kosher Kush and Lemon Skunk. This cultivar is known to have a prominent citrus and Kush aroma profile, with dominant terpenes limonene and myrcene. This cultivar produces a golden, light green bud with orange and golden pistils.

Product Short Description: Bred from Baby Gluey and C99. Plenty of spice and sour notes with hints of skunk.
Product Long Description: Bred from Baby Gluey and C99. Plenty of spice and sour notes with hints of skunk.

Product Short Description: Citizen Stash Ape Tape delivers diesel, skunk, earthiness and chocolate notes with a black coffee finish.
Product Long Description: Citizen Stash Ape Tape delivers diesel, skunk, earthiness and chocolate notes with a black coffee finish.

Product Short Description: Known for their potent and gassy smell, GP20 buds are minty green with bright orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.
Product Long Description: GP20 is a coveted hybrid strain collaboration between Cookies and Powerzzz Genetics combining the strains Y-Griega and Snowman. This strain is known for having a very potent gassy smell. From the legendary Cookies team, masterfully grown in Canada.

Product Short Description: Known for having a musky scent with a hint of gas, Medellin buds are a deep purple with flecks of vibrant green throughout.
Product Long Description: Medellin is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain originally cultivated by Lemonnade. This strain is known for having a musky scent with a hint of gas. Medellin buds are a deep purple with flecks of vibrant green throughout. From the Cookies and Lemonnade team, masterfully grown in Canada.

Product Short Description: This strain is characterized by dense, small to medium sized buds covered in frosty trichomes with up to 5% terpenes.
Product Long Description: If you're looking for something frosty, then you’ve found a friend in this Animal Cookies and SinMint Cookies cross. With a touch of mint, the scent of cookie dough breaks through along with a hint of diesel and pine and a flavour profile to match the nose. This strain is characterized by tight, dense and small to medium sized buds with up to 5% terpenes. This small batch flower is grown indoors without pesticides, hand trimmed and hand packed in batches small enough to treat each plant like family.

Product Short Description: Strawberry Guava is proudly grown in Quebec and offers sweet, fruit flavours and aromas.
Product Long Description: Tasty indeed, Tam Tams’ own Strawberry Guava is a sativa-dominant hybrid with sweet, fruity flavours and aromas. From Huntingdon, Quebec and grown indoors, this cross between Strawberry Banana and Papaya packs hardy potency into colourful buds with frosty trichomes.

Product Short Description: Complex and distinguished – a fruity lineage of Purple Punch x Kush Mints #11. PPMs terpene profile is a combination of grape and blueberry.
Product Long Description: Complex and distinguished. Purple Punch Mints is a fruity lineage of Purple Punch and Kush Mints #11. PPMs terpene profile is a creamy combination of grape juice and blueberry muffins and upon a glance, looks as if it has candied layers due to its dense coating of trichomes. At Joi, we hang dry, hand trim and cure in stainless steel containers for at least 14 days to ensure a quality finish. Packages are filled by hand and include humidity packs inside to maintain optimal freshness. Enjoi!

Product Name: Pineapple Buds - Pineapple Upside Down Cake
Product Short Description: This indica-dominant hybrid combines Pineapple Trainwreck with Cookie Monster. The aroma is sweet & tropical with an earthy, spicy cake batter finish.
Product Long Description: This Indigenous Okanagan Valley Facility is where you’ll find master growers Laine Keyes and his teenage crush Kyra Horvath hunting for the most unique genetics craft cannabis consumers have ever seen. Growing in deep water culture, Laine and Kyra’s plants are healthy, hearty and lush, and they yield some of the most original terpene profiles available. Pineapple Upside Down Cake, is an indica-dominant hybrid combining Pineapple Trainwreck with Cookie Monster. This strain was bred by Humboldt Seed Co and adopted by Pineapple buds due to its delicious taste and high potency. The aroma is sweet and tropical, with herbal nutty overtones which dissipate to earthy, spicy notes and a cake batter finish. Pineapple Upside Cake's flowers are chunky evergreen beauties interspersed with orange pistils and finished with a heavy frosting of trichomes, while others are lime in colour and drip with a cloak of plum projecting ghostly flames of blonde fire.

Product Short Description: This highly potent indica is best for experienced consumers. Triple OG gets its name from Triangle Kush, Constantine Kush and Master Yoda Genetics.
Product Long Description: The holistic and regenerative growing methods utilized by Indigenous growers, Living Cannabis, have been honed for over 40 years as they produced cannabis for compassion clubs. Live, organic inputs into the soil fill it with nutrients and give the plants at Living Cannabis optimal conditions to thrive. These same growing methods are responsible for the super terpy flavour and dank aroma usually only found in the sun drenched fields of the Emerald Triangle in California. Triple OG, grown by Living Cannabis and bred by Exotic Genetix, is a strong Kush originating from Florida. This highly potent indica is best for experienced consumers. Triple OG gets its name from Triangle Kush, Constantine Kush and Master Yoda. Triple OG has healthy green hues speckled with milky trichomes and interspersed with burnt orange pistils. With a nose of skunk, earth, and pine, this cultivar has been a favourite of BC connoisseurs for years.

Product Short Description: Grape Pop Rocks is a cross of Pop Rocks and Grape Stomper, two potent indica-dominant strains which create a tasty grape explosion.
Product Long Description: Master Grower Travis Tully first learned his craft as a teenager over the shoulder of his OG grower Dad. He mastered his skills over the next 20 years in Kelowna BC and helped open Okanna Craft, a family run small business with a grass roots approach. Travis’ intimate relationship with the cannabis plant extends well beyond their facility to the private garden where Travis is a very humble bee keeper and steward of the land. Okanna Craft was known for growing the highest quality medicinal cannabis and now brings that same attention to quality to the recreational market. Grape Pop Rocks is a cross of Pop Rocks and Grape Stomper, two potent indica-dominant strains which create a tasty grape explosion. This unique offering has the most beautiful purple hued flowers, with every surface sparkled with frosty trichomes. The strong grape candy aroma hits your nose first, with subtle notes of earth and diesel to follow.

Product Short Description: Jenn’s OG’s Tire Fire is an indica dominant hybrid. Crossing the powerful Hi-Octane and Do-Si-Dos, the resulting flower provides a pungent gassy hit.
Product Long Description: Tire Fire combines a High Octane Cut of OG from the San Fernando Valley with the classic Do-Si-Dos, producing a potent indica dominant hybrid with a heavy diesel kick. The flower is dank and stinky, and the fat popcorn shaped buds are filled with bright orange hairs and an overly generous coating of frosty white trichomes. Jenn’s OG Tire Fire brings a diesel-rich flavour profile, complemented by spicy and peppery notes brought forth by the dominant terpene, caryophyllene. The rich and pungent flower is pleasantly blended with a slightly minty and nutty cookie aftertaste, dominated by a typical hot rubber aftertaste hence the name, a true fire strain.

Product Short Description: Bread by Skunk House Genetics from Forum Cut GSC and legendary Chem Dawg, selected by Mother Labs to deliver high THC with classic dank fuel flavours.
Product Long Description: All gas, no brakes. Koko's Cookies was bread by Skunk House Genetics from the world-famous Forum Cut GSC and the legendary Chem Dawg, selected by Mother Labs to deliver high THC with classic dank fuel flavours. Grown in small batches, thoughtfully hang dried, carefully hand trimmed and packed to deliver bold flavour in every bud.

Product Short Description: We selected this flower to have a sweet, doughy flavour with a visual coating of sugary crystals.
Product Long Description: We selected this flower to have a sweet, doughy flavour with a visual coating of sugary crystals.

Product Short Description: Gas Berries #112 holds a special place in hearts (and grinders) and is named for its blend of rich berry and gas aromas.
Product Long Description: Gas Berries #112 holds a special place in hearts (and grinders) and is named for its blend of rich berry and gasoline aromas that flow through to its taste. In addition to its memorable aroma and flavour, this indica-dominant pheno stood out for its bulky green buds and vibrant orange pistils. OGEN's most requested cultivar is making a comeback for a limited time.

Product Short Description: Space Cake is a new cultivar with some serious rocket fuel. Indica-dominant that's pungent and potent with warm coffee undertones.
Product Long Description: Calling all space cadets. We’ve programmed a sweet treat for you that packs some serious rocket fuel. Ready for lift-off? Ok, that’s enough space puns for now. Space Cake is a new indica-dominant cultivar from Edison that’s as spicy as it is pungent. Space Cake’s lineage can be traced back to GSC and Snow Lotus. You’ll find its aromas fall into a Kush territory meaning it has spicy and gassy notes, with a warm roasted coffee undertone.

Product Short Description: Pink Krush is a relative of OG Kush. Beta-caryophyllene, myrcene and humulene are primary terpenes of this high THC indica.
Product Long Description: Favours is an emerging cannabis brand that always has a good time through smalls acts of kindness and joyful gestures. We proudly introduce Favours and its first product, Pink Krush. This popular strain is a relative of OG Kush and has a flavour-rich strong and gassy aroma with citrus and earthy notes from a terpene profile that includes beta-caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol and linalool. The dense and sticky green buds dance in the sunlight with sparkling trichomes throughout.

Product Short Description: A cross of the popular Orange Cookies and High Octane. A craft  grown cultivar with amazing trichome coverage and a bright , beautiful bud structure.
Product Long Description: A cross of the popular Orange Cookies and High Octane. A craft indoor grown cultivar with a bright and beautiful bud structure, and amazing trichome coverage. Hang-dried and hand-trimmed.

Product Short Description: This indica-dominant hybrid is a cross between Slurricane and TMAC. Expect a flavour that leans sweet with subtle grape and berry undertones.
Product Long Description:
With 20 years of experience in the legacy market, the Pistol and Paris team is now bringing the
same BC Bud you've smoked for years to the legal market. The Pistol and Paris brand is all about high-end, gassy, cannabis from specialized small gardens. Our team personally inspects every lot, traveling throughout B.C. to find top craft quality to put into our brand.

This indica-dominant hybrid is a cross between Slurricane and TMAC bred by Sacred Cut Genetics and grown by JBuds in Summerland, BC. Expect the buds to be heavily frosted and dense to the touch while the flavour leans sweet with subtle grape and berry undertones.

The dominant terpenes in this cultivar are limonene, trans-caryophyllene and ocimene.

Grown in soil, hand-watered, hand-trimmed, hang dried with a ten-day cure. Packaged in a glass jar.

Product Short Description: A high-THC sativa hybrid with sticky, dense, floral buds that bring with it a smooth berry flavour and aroma, with a hit of menthol undertone.
Product Long Description: Organic Cherry Mints is a high-THC sativa hybrid with genetics originating from Seed Junky. It is a sticky, dense, floral bud that brings with it a smooth berry flavour and aroma, with a hit of menthol undertone. Grown in living soil, Organic Cherry Mints grows tall and bushy and is supplemented with natural sources of carbohydrates like molasses and maple syrup that bring its sweet scent to life.

Product Short Description: Organic Crunch Berry Kush is an indica dominant hybrid with distinct sweet berry aroma inherited from its parents, the renowned Blueberry x Triple OG.
Product Long Description: Organic Crunch Berry Kush is an indica dominant hybrid with distinct sweet berry aroma inherited from its parents, the renowned Blueberry and Triple OG. The nose on this cultivar is a scintillating tangy/sour affair infused with touches of vanilla, fresh hazelnuts and pine. The flavour is a remarkable fruiting bouquet that leaves a pleasant after-taste.

Product Short Description: A TGOD original cross between Koloa Sunrise x GG4, Organic Maple Kush gets its name from the natural carbohydrate source used to feed the soil.
Product Long Description: Organic Maple Kush is a certified organic Indica bud grown in living soil, using natural sunlight and purified rainwater. A TGOD original cross between Koloa Sunrise and GG4, Organic Maple Kush gets its name from the natural carbohydrate source used to feed the soil it grows in – Canadian organic maple syrup. Its dense round buds with dark purple and green leaves are covered in frosty-white trichomes and bright orange pistils. This beautiful bud brings with it a tropical, fruity, kush-like finish, a result of myrcene and farnesene terpenes that dominate this strain's aroma and flavour.

Product Short Description: Cannabis flower, Organic Romulan.
Product Long Description: Our FVOPA Certified Organic Romulan is an indica-dominant derived from the North American Indica and White Rhino lineages. It produces dense, frosty buds and has a refreshing flavour profile that boasts notes of pine, earth, and citrus. It is a popular choice among legacy growers in the Pacific Northwest. Grown in living soil, hang-dried for 14 days and cold cured.

Product Short Description: Cannabis flower, Organic Romulan.
Product Long Description: Our FVOPA Certified Organic Romulan is an indica-dominant derived from the North American Indica and White Rhino lineages. It produces dense, frosty buds and has a refreshing flavour profile that boasts notes of pine, earth, and citrus. It is a popular choice among legacy growers in the Pacific Northwest. Grown in living soil, hang-dried for 14 days and cold cured.

Product Short Description: Durban P is noted for its large over-sized resin glands, and delivering a sweet aroma.
Product Long Description: Durban P is a famed landrace cultivar, said to date back centuries to the modern-day port city of Durban. Brought to and refined by breeders in North America, this sativa-dominant strain has buds with frosty trichomes all over, and a sweet aroma.

Product Short Description: A cross between Jelly Breath and GMO, very dense buds deliver aromas of gas and spices.
Product Long Description: Garlic Jelly, aka JMO, is a modern indica-dominant cross, containing impressive lineage from its parents Jelly Breath (OG Kush Breath, thought to be a descendent from GSC) and GMO (another GSC line crossed with Chemdog). For those not in the know, those respected genetics inspire a sticky sweet and sharp spicy aroma.

Product Short Description: Powdered Donuts is an indica-dominant hybrid that delivers wonderful aromas of gassy citrus and fruity pastry.
Product Long Description: Powdered Donuts is an indica-dominant hybrid with very sweet lineage. Its parents, Orange Cookies and Jet Fuel Gelato, share traits from some famed cultivars within this genetic line that came before, including OG Kush, Girl Scout Cookies, California Orange and East Coast Sour Diesel. This cultivar delivers wonderful aromas of gassy citrus and fruity pastry.

Product Short Description: An offshoot from the Wedding Cake family, Papaya Cake is tart lemon, overly ripe mango and black bananas that give off an astringent like finish.
Product Long Description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest, and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. An offshoot from the Wedding Cake family, Papaya Cake is tart lemon, overly ripe mango and black bananas that give off an astringent like finish to make up the heart of this dank bouquet. Frosty, triangular buds range in colour from bright green, deep emerald and occasionally mauve hues making this exotic cultivar a sight for sore eyes in addition to an intriguing terp ride - fruity with a pungent sourdough on exhale.

Product Short Description: Bred by Ethos Genetics, Peach Crescendo is a hybrid strain with notes of diesel and fermented peach. Small batch,  hang dried,  trimmed and packaged.
Product Long Description: Bred by Ethos Genetics, Peach Crescendo is a hybrid strain with notes of diesel and fermented sweet peach. Grown and processed in small batches, hang dried and hand trimmed, this beautiful flower is light green with pronounced orange pistils. A balanced terpene profile of caryophyllene, limonene, and farnesene creates a delicious and smooth experience. Our product is grown without the use of any form of pesticides, and is non-irradiated. Small batch (under 700 sqft rooms), hang dried, hand trimmed, and hand packaged.

Product Short Description: BC Organic Pemberton Pink (Island Pink Kush) is known for its beautiful looks, sweet taste, and aroma of vanilla, earth, and pine.
Product Long Description: 100% Certified Organic by PACS. Ultra-Premium. BC grown. Grown indoors in organic living soil without the use of artificial pesticides or fertilizers. Flowers are dried using a slow cold cure, before being carefully hand trimmed and packed in glass jars. BC Organic Pemberton Pink (Island Pink Kush) has the lineage of King and Afghan Kush. Known for its beautiful looks and great taste, this ancient and elusive strain has the three dominant terpenes of beta- caryophyllene, myrcene, and limonene resulting in its sweet taste and aroma of vanilla, earth, and pine. Important to us and our community, we have committed to plant 1 tree for every cannabis plant we harvest through our partnership with One Tree Planted.

Product Short Description: Naturally balanced THC & CBD with notes of earth, herbs, and fresh cut grass.
Product Long Description: Pennywise 1:1 is a strain offering naturally balanced THC and CBD, for those seeking the advantages of both cannabinoids. A hybrid of CBD-rich Harlequin and a high-THC Jack the Ripper, Pennywise 1:1 offers aromas of sweet earth, woody herbs, and fresh cut grass, from dominant terpenes including myrcene, guaiol, and bisabolol. It has tightly packed buds which showcase a blend of olive-coloured leaves and burnt orange pistils under a cover of milky trichomes.

Product Short Description: The Miigwetch comes from an unknown cross that gives its flowers an earthy, metallic sweetness and a subtle purple green colouration.
Product Long Description: Red Market Brand's Miigwetch was selected for its unique sour spicy aroma, indica-dominant ancestry and its timeless subtle purple and green colours. Migwetch is an indica-dominant hybrid with a sour blackcurrant taste and subtle radish aroma with a citrus finish. The Miigwetch comes from an unknown cross that gives its flowers an earthy, metallic sweetness and a subtle purple green colouration. Chi Miigwetch is Ojibwe and translates to “Big Thank You" and reflects the gratitude Red Market has for the cannabis plant and support from the cannabis community, including its LP partner Royal City Cannabis, and most importantly consumers who support Red Market Brand's vision of giving back to First Nations communities and Indigenous participation in the legal cannabis market.

Product Short Description: The Miigwetch comes from an unknown cross that gives its flowers an earthy, metallic sweetness and a subtle purple green colouration.
Product Long Description: Red Market Brand's Miigwetch was selected for its unique sour spicy aroma, indica-dominant ancestry and its timeless subtle purple and green colours. Migwetch is an indica-dominant hybrid with a sour blackcurrant taste and subtle radish aroma with a citrus finish. The Miigwetch comes from an unknown cross that gives its flowers an earthy, metallic sweetness and a subtle purple green colouration. Chi Miigwetch is Ojibwe and translates to “Big Thank You" and reflects the gratitude Red Market has for the cannabis plant and support from the cannabis community, including its LP partner Royal City Cannabis, and most importantly consumers who support Red Market Brand's vision of giving back to First Nations communities and Indigenous participation in the legal cannabis market.

Product Short Description: Rotating small-batch, BC-grown single strains. Here for a limited time only.
Product Long Description: The Limited Release Flower series features a rotating selection of small-batch, single strains. Pure Sunfarms is always trialing cultivars in its sunlit Fraser Valley greenhouse, making this a unique way to experience new cuts which won’t be around for long. Every batch is grown to express the true nature of that cultivar, from its potency to aromatics and flavour. Grown with care and harvested by hand. Available for a limited time only.

Product Short Description: A sour tart aroma, with hints of spice and earthy tones, and a sour and chamomile flavour.
Product Long Description: A sour tart aroma, with hints of spice and earthy tones, and a sour and chamomile flavour.

Product Short Description: London Pound Cake has a grassy, sweet, blueberry/lemongrass aroma and a menthol, OG musk flavour with a sweet finish.
Product Long Description: London Pound Cake has a grassy, sweet, blueberry/lemongrass aroma and a menthol, OG musk flavour with a sweet finish.

Product Short Description: A sativa-dominant flower with an ancient-dwarfed bonsai tree look, dense, green buds with large, robust, crusty calyx and a coat of trichome resin.
Product Long Description: Lost Cause is a sativa-dominant gem found at the intersection of Amnesia Haze x Do-Si-Dos. Both the studied precision of that phenohunt and its visually attractive flower are reminiscent of sculpted, ancient bonsai trees – dense and tightly-woven green buds with large, robust crusty calyx embraced with a coating of sticky trichome resin. The rare terpinolene leads a harmonically-peaceful multidimensional terpene profile featuring sweet berry, minty and lemony aromas and flavours amplified by piney and dark earthy undertones. A floral, herbaceous and citrusy journey is directed onward with the additional presence of caryophyllene (found in pepper and cinnamon) and myrcene (mangoes and hops).

Product Short Description: A hybrid strain with frosty white buds, a citrus-diesel aroma and a peppery-cedar finish. Its main terpenes are myrcene, limonene, and caryophyllene.
Product Long Description: Purplefarm Genetics’ Sour Glue is a cross between Gorilla Glue #4 and Sour Diesel. Purplefarm Genetics combines decades of practical growing knowledge with data and technology, producing terpene-rich and cannabinoid-rich cannabis. Sour Glue is grown indoors in environmentally controlled grow rooms using ProMix HP+ with Mycorrhizae and Californian Luxx HPS lighting. Heat, humidity, air pressure and CO2 are controlled while the plants are dosed with nutrients on a weekly basis. Each plant is hand harvested and hang-dried cold for two weeks. From there, they’re hand-trimmed, cold-barrel cured, and burped daily for 21 days to ensure ideal quality. The large to medium buds are nearly entirely covered in frosty trichomes, with a citrus diesel aroma and a peppery, cedar finish. Purplefarm Genetics Sour Glue has >3% terpenes, led by myrcene, limonene, and caryophyllene.

Product Short Description: Let the Rhythm take control with Rhythm ZK Pebbles from Loop / Pool. This sativa-dominant whole flower features a fruity, tropical and sweet mix.
Product Long Description: Let the Rhythm take control with Rhythm ZK Pebbles from Loop / Pool. This high-THC, sativa-dominant. indoor-grown, whole flower features a fruity, tropical and sweet mix that will carve a unique place in your palette. Grown in a state of the art, climate-controlled hybrid greenhouse.

Product Short Description: Root Beer Float is an indica-dominant strain created through crossing XXX OG and Vanilla Kush with a sweet, earthy aroma with hints of lemon and pine.
Product Long Description: Root Beer Float is an indica-dominant strain created through crossing XXX OG and Vanilla Kush. Enter into a sweet, earthy aroma with hints of lemon and pine. Enjoy the classic Root Beer flavour combined with frothy vanilla notes. BOLD’s Root Beer Float is hang-dried, slow cured and dry trimmed by hand to accentuate the rich amber pistils and creamy vanilla trichomes.

Product Short Description: A strain curated for the Liiv consumer with an excessive gassy flavour and smell.
Product Long Description: Introducing Liiv Route 66, a new strain carefully curated with the Liiv consumer in mind. Named after its excessively gassy flavor and smell, Liiv Route 66 crosses Chemdog and SFV OG Kush. This popular strain produces a flavorful smoke with notes of fuel, earth, and citrus. If you’re an OG fan, Liiv Route 66 is a must-try.

Product Short Description: Freedom Cannabis' Secret Formula is an indica strain with 2.5-3.5% terpenes. You’ll love the lemony sour citrus taste and aroma.
Product Long Description: Freedom Cannabis' Secret Formula is an indica dominant strain with total terpenes between 2.5 and 3.5%.  A cross of White Fire #43 and Do-Si-Dos, this cultivar possesses a sweet, fruity diesel aroma with a lemony sour citrus taste. Freedom Cannabis grows all product indoors and offsets our carbon footprint by showcasing Canada's largest solar panel rooftop.

Product Short Description: Freedom Cannabis' Secret Formula is an indica strain with 2.5-3.5% terpenes. You’ll love the lemony sour citrus taste and aroma.
Product Long Description: Freedom Cannabis' Secret Formula is an indica dominant strain with total terpenes between 2.5 and 3.5%.  A cross of White Fire #43 and Do-Si-Dos, this cultivar possesses a sweet, fruity diesel aroma with a lemony sour citrus taste. Freedom Cannabis grows all product indoors and offsets our carbon footprint by showcasing Canada's largest solar panel rooftop.

Product Short Description: Our small-batch Black Label Skullcap indica-leaning hybrid delivers complex fruity flavours with an alluring diesel twist.
Product Long Description: This resinous beauty will have you salivating before the bag is opened. Our small-batch Black Label Skullcap is an indica-leaning hybrid that delivers an alluring gassy diesel aroma with fruity berry undertones. A rare cross between Sour Headstash and Biker Kush from legendary Karma Genetics, this indoor-grown cannabis is carefully hang-dried, hand-trimmed and hand-packed with a 2-way humidity control pack for a clean, fresh smoke.

Product Short Description: A rare cross of SFV Kush x Lemon Larry Hybrid. OG Kush potent gas terps and multi-layered flavour effect complement its earthy, piney qualities.
Product Long Description: Something About Larry is a rare cross of SFV Kush x Lemon Larry Hybrid (high-THC Cali genetic). This hybrid Kush offering is designed for the OG, Chem and Sour aficionados with a high-THC potency. A lemon-pledge fuel funk sativa-leaning hybrid with piney and Kush back notes, this strain boasts rock solid rounded buds with a white frost and light green appearance.

Product Short Description: Sorbetto is an award-winning strain that features dense purple shaded buds with mouth-watering flavours that live up to its legendary lineage.
Product Long Description: Sorbetto is an award-winning strain that features dense purple shaded buds with mouth-watering flavours that live up to its legendary lineage. Upon inhale expect to be hit with sweet notes of citrus and fruit followed by notes of honey and herbs on the exhale.

Product Short Description: Space Cake indica-dominant hybrid has a strong THC potency potential and gassy aroma. A cross between cultivars GSC and Snow Lotus.
Product Long Description: Color Space Cake is an out of this world indica-dominant hybrid strain, a rare cross between legendary cultivars GSC and Snow Lotus. Its buds have dark purple hues and blazing orange pistils caked with trichomes. Expect high THC potency with notes of musk and creamy diesel cues.

Product Short Description: OGEN’s cosmic hybrid pheno with aromas of gas and candy. Its lime green buds have fiery orange pistils and sparkling trichomes.
Product Long Description: Space Flight Superstar #11 is OGEN’s cosmic hybrid pheno. Launching with smells of rocket fuel and candy, a blast of aromas is unlocked after being busted – yielding an interstellar mix of fruity, creamy, pastry like flavours. Its cone shaped, lime green buds have fiery orange pistils and sparkling trichomes that will have you counting down to liftoff!

Product Short Description: Smooth tasting that features lemon and diesel, and notes of vanilla on the exhale.
Product Long Description: Smooth tasting that features lemon and diesel, and notes of vanilla on the exhale. Has been grown in a micro cultivation cannabis facility located in the Valleys of British Columbia with years of high-quality boutique growing experience. Hung dry for 21 days.

Product Short Description: Stankasaurus is an indica dominant hybrid strain with a pungent diesel aroma, earthy diesel taste and hints of sour peppery skunk upon exhale.
Product Long Description: Stankasaurus is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the Dino Meat #8 X Mr. Stinky strains. Stankasaurus has a super pungent and dank skunky diesel aroma. The flavour is on the lighter side, with an earthy diesel taste and hints of sour peppery skunk upon exhale. This bud has fat oversized spade-shaped forest green shape with thin yellow-orange hairs and a coating of tiny purple-tinted white crystal trichomes. These flowers were grown in a small batch craft system with maximum TLC. The flowers were grown using sea of green, drip irridated, hand harvested, hand trimmed and hand packaged.

Product Short Description: A hybrid strain with a tasty, piney flavour profile and a sweet aroma. Its buds are chunky, light green and frosty.
Product Long Description: Grown using the sea of green method, Donny Burger is hand-watered then hang dried and cold-cured for 14 days. The buds are dry-trimmed, then finished by hand—courtesy of the Master Grower—to keep the integrity and the trichomes intact. Donny Burger is a cross between GMO and Larry OG, and is a hybrid strain with high THC. Donny Burger’s main terpenes are alpha-pinene, camphene, and beta-myrcene, and the light green, frosty buds have a piney taste with a sweet aroma. Led by Master Grower Giuseppe “Joe” Leandro, Stinky Greens Organic has been earning trust and admiration among their customers since 2018. Their dedication and care for each plant is what makes their cannabis stand out. Donny Burger is grown in coco soil to allow sufficient air flow and water circulation. Plus, the Stinky Greens Organic greenhouse facility is a closed loop and CO2 enhanced, ensuring no elements from the outdoors make their way in.

Product Short Description: Pura Vida Legacy Strawberry Octane dried flower
Product Long Description: Pura Vida Legacy Strawberry Octane Flower is a sativa that offers a classic strawberry taste with sour undertones and a spicy exhale. Pura Vida has taken special care in selecting genetics to provide you with the highest quality experience that will leave you expecting the best.

Product Short Description: Sunset Sherbet may be our most fruit-forward strain yet, evoking the truly unique smell and taste of a basket of strawberries and guava.
Product Long Description: Sunset Sherbet is one of the more coveted cultivars ever grown by Broken Coast. Exhibiting dense indica flowers with deep purple and silver colouration, the large swollen calyxes are covered so thickly in glandular trichomes they're almost white. With the most abundant terpenes being caryophyllene, myrcene and limonene, Sunset Sherbet may be our most fruit-forward strain yet, evoking the truly unique smell and taste of a basket of strawberries and guava. But don’t let those rich aromas fool you, there’s prominent dank and pungent undertones that any great cannabis cultivar should have. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang cured and hand trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: An indica leaning hybrid cross between Pink Kush and Bubba Kush, the weed has a compact structure that shows stunning mint green & deep purple hues.
Product Long Description:
Pink Bubba is a beautiful example of an indica leaning hybrid in both effect and flavour.

A cross between Pink Kush and Bubba Kush, the weed has a compact structure that shows stunning mint green and deep purple hues. Bright orange hairs and a thick coating of trichomes add texture and depth to this beautiful flower.

Aromas of pungent earth and pine are predominant and the smoke itself is smooth. It is full of flavour and slightly sweeter and more floral than the nose would suggest but leaves a unique aftertaste of pine and juniper. 

WAGNERS believe in hard work and Well Made Weed. Our Pink Bubba strain is just that, Well Made.

Product Short Description: Pink Rozay is a potent indica-dominant hybrid that carries a bright, floral aroma and tastes like sweet velvet cake.
Product Long Description: Pink Rozay is a potent indica-dominant hybrid that carries a bright, floral aroma and tastes like sweet velvet cake. You can identify Pink Rozay by its dense olive green buds with deep pink and purple undertones.

Product Short Description: Tweed Powdered Donuts is an indica strain comes from a cross of Jet Fuel Gelato and Orange Cookies.
Product Long Description: Tweed Powdered Donuts is an indica strain comes from a cross of Jet Fuel Gelato and Orange Cookies. Its buds are tight, with orange hues and dense trichome coverage. Some associate citrus, floral, and fruit flavours with the Tweed Powdered Donuts Strain.

Premium small-batch flower. SensiMila Powdered Donuts is a potent indica with aromas of tangy citrus and sweet cream. Our high terpene, high-THC flower comes equipped with a humidity device in a premium for maximum terpene retention. To preserve the integrity and freshness of the product, SensiMila flower is packaged by hand. Enjoy the finest cannabis from local cultivators. Curated by SensiMila.

Product Short Description: An exclusive, bred by LIT Farms, Landslide contains a deliciously sweet flavor profile that puts out exceptionally smooth and cakey terpenes.
Product Long Description: An exclusive, bred by LIT Farms, Landslide is a cross of Lava Cake and Mac that brings its loud, obnoxiously pungent strain that is sure to please. It contains a deliciously sweet flavor profile that puts out exceptionally smooth and cakey terpenes. Some users that smoke this strain say it smells like freshly baked goods.

Product Short Description: This amazing cultivar is covered in trichome crystals and has and amazing aroma comprised of sweet creamy dessert with hints of gas coming through.
Product Long Description: Great solid grower with a great genetic!! It’s grown in a micro grower cultivation facility located in the Valleys of British Colombia. This amazing cultivar offers a wide spectrum from greens to cloudy creamy whites. Its covered in trichome crystals and has an amazing aroma comprised of sweet creamy dessert with hints of gas coming through. Hung dry for 21 days.

Product Short Description: This sativa-dominant strain boasts a sweet fresh grapefruit flavour with slight earthiness on exhale.
Product Long Description: New York 47 is a sativa dominant strain of very potent THC potential. It is made by crossing NYC Diesel with AK-47. It boasts a sweet, fresh grapefruit flavour with slight earthiness on exhale. The aroma is sweet citrus with a floral diesel overtone. Its light minty green buds are coated with bright crystal trichomes and dark red pistils.

Product Short Description: Niichii is a hybrid that gives its flowers light purple and green colours and delicious creamy chocolate aroma with a fruity sugar flavour.
Product Long Description: Red Market Brand's Niichii was selected for its delicious creamy and fruity aroma, hybrid ancestry and beautiful light speckled colours. Niichii is a hybrid that gives its flowers light purple and green colours and delicious creamy chocolate aroma with a fruity sugar flavour. Niichii is Ojibwe and translates to “my friend" and reflects the openness and inclusivity of Red Market Brand’s vision.

Product Short Description: Nishin is an indica hybrid from an unknown cross that with deep purple and green colours, and unique licorice wetland flavour with a gassy aroma.
Product Long Description: Red Market Brand's Nishin was selected for its distinct earthy gas aroma, indica-dominant ancestry and strong purple and green colours. Nishin is an indica-dominant hybrid from an unknown cross that gives its flowers deep purple green colours and a unique licorice wetland flavour with a gassy aroma. Nishin is Ojibwe and translates to “finest, best, good" and reflects a commitment to quality and its vision of giving back to First Nations communities and Indigenous participation in the legal cannabis market.

Product Short Description: Slurricane is a cross between Dosidos and Purple Punch and has a sweet flavour profile, with notes of subtle grape and sugary berries.
Product Long Description:
Slurricane is a cross between Dosidos and Purple Punchand has a sweet flavour profile, with notes of subtle grape and sugary berries. The buds are dark green in colour with burnt orange pistils and a thick layer of white trichomes that take on a purple hue in the right light. With a total terpene content of 2.7%, the top terpenes are alpha-cedrene, beta-caryophyllene, limonene, linalool and fenchol.

As part of the Kolab Growers Series, Kolab has partnered with Safari Cannabis to launch Slurricane. In an effort to build community, profile our partners and offer transparency to consumers, Kolab launched the Growers Series. A series is dedicated to showcasing the quality, consistency and difference it makes when cannabis is grown in small-batches, hand-tended and cared for by dedicated growers.

Product Long Description: Top-shelf flower always start with a pheno hunt, where untold hours are spent popping seeds in the pursuit of finding a unicorn. Drew’s pheno features a rotation of limited drops grown by our partner craft growers and hand selected by our Master Grower.

Product Short Description: This popular sativa-dominant Super Lemon Haze has a tart, zesty lemon flavour and aroma, with sweet notes.
Product Long Description: When life gives you lemons, smoke 'em. Versus Super Lemon Haze is bred from Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze to produce a sativa-dominant strain that wears a dense coat of trichomes. Its terp profile features trans-caryophyllene, beta-myrcene, limonene, and farnesene which delivers a zesty, citrusy aroma and tastes of sour lemon that develops into a slightly sweet finish.

Product Short Description: Sun grown organically on Texada Island, this unique sativa has an amazing terpene profile. Camphene,  linalool and  myrcene enhance this hidden gem.
Product Long Description: Sun grown organically on Texada Island, this unique sativa dominant strain has an amazing terpene profile revealing sweet, lavender and woody aromas. Every small batch of this coastal island flower receives only the highest quality inputs, including seaweed, high quality compost and Indigenous microorganisms. Our gardens, surrounded by specific flowers, attract beneficial insects that control pests while also naturally encouraging a more fragrant flower. High amounts of camphene and linalool with low amounts of myrcene emboldens the sativa in this Weathered Islands hidden gem.

Product Short Description: This flavour-heavy strain of Tangerine Sunrise gushes tantalizing aromas of sweet citrus.
Product Long Description: This unique, flavour-heavy strain of Tangerine Sunrise has your cravings for a refreshing orange creamsicle in check. Tangerine Sunrise’s big, green buds are accented with orange hairs and a white crystal frosting, but they’re more than just beautiful. Their tantalizing aromas of sweet citrus are reminiscent of a frozen treat on a hot day – no sunblock required.

Product Long Description:
A soapy aroma, with a hint of sweet cake that tastes sweet & aromatic.
This dried flower has a potent flavour.

Tommy's Dosi Punch is an indica-dominant hybrid known for its tall, fluffy buds, purple-tinged crystals and honey-tipped tea-green hairs. This strain brings notes of lemon, musk and wood, derived from limonene, beta-caryophyllene and cedrene. All our pre-rolls are hand-packed with flower only. What's more, our reusable and recyclable container will keep each pre-roll fresh from the first to the last, maintaining terpenes and locking in moisture. Enjoy this cross between Do Si Dos and Purple Punch.

Product Short Description: Gelato 29 is a distinctive sativa-dominant hybrid with fluffy light green buds, sweet and fruity aromas, and undertones of vanilla and cream.
Product Long Description:
Gelato 29 is a distinct sativa-dominant hybrid that maintains traits that make Gelato hybrids highly popular – fluffy buds with touches of purple, orange pistils and super sweet terpene profile. Gelato 29 sets itself apart with lighter green buds and shiny white trichomes all over. Not just pretty to look at, Gelato 29’s aroma is a mouth-watering crowd-pleaser — bold fruity and berry with slight undertones of vanilla and cream.

Gelato 29 UP20™ flower is indoor-grown in our Atholville, New Brunswick facility and promises to deliver 20% THC or higher. Every time.

Product Short Description: Ultra Sour is a sativa-dominant hybrid with light green buds, dense trichome coverage and dank diesel and zesty citrus aromas.
Product Long Description:
Pucker up, because Ultra Sour is a sativa-dominant hybrid with light green buds, dense trichome coverage and fiery orange pistils. Upon opening the bag, your nose will be greeted by a complex dank diesel and zesty citrus aroma thanks to its dominant terpenes terpinolene, limonene and caryophyllene.

All UP20™ flower is indoor-grown in our Atholville, New Brunswick facility and promises to deliver 20% THC or higher. Every time.

Product Short Description: Grown indoors in small batches and hang dried. Sativa dominant - cross between Viper City OG and GSC that provides a spicy flavour with sweet notes.
Product Long Description: Viper Cookie (VCO) contains 10 different Terpenes (>7%), beta-caryophyllene dominant (2%), with farnesene, humulene, linalool, and limonene.  Grown indoors in small batches and hang dried with extra care. This hybrid strain is a cross between Viper City OG and GSC that provides a spicy flavour with sweet notes. No harshness on inhalation, white ash.

Product Short Description: This beautiful flower is a combination of Gelato 41 x Triangle Kush x Watermelon OG. The buds are round and dense with a strong sweet nose.
Product Long Description: This beautiful flower is a combination of Gelato 41 x Triangle Kush x Watermelon OG. The buds are round and dense with a strong sweet nose of citrus and fruit. The trichome production is very intense and whatever is not green or purple is surely a trichome. The flowers are grown in a small batch drip feed system, hand-harvested, hand-trimmed and hand-packed. We feel strongly that this creates the highest level products for our customers.

Product Short Description: Wedding Crashers is a staple in the trend of dessert strains, blending smooth vanilla of Wedding Cake with sweet notes of Purple Punch.
Product Long Description: Wedding Crashers is a staple in the trend of dessert strains, blending smooth vanilla of Wedding Cake with sweet notes of Purple Punch. It’s an indica-dominant hybrid showing dark green and often purple hues, with a smoke that is smooth, sweet, and potent.

Product Short Description: The marriage of Wedding Cake x Grape Pie. These vibrant green buds have a flair of purple, 2.89% total terpenes and a spicy, cracked pepper profile.
Product Long Description: Wedding Pie is the marriage of Wedding Cake x Grape Pie. These vibrant green buds have a flair of purple, 2.89% total terpene content and a spicy, cracked pepper profile. The top terpenes are beta-caryophyllene, alpha-cedrene, bisabolol, linalool, and limonene. Always packaged in a resealable foil pouch to make sure your bud stays fresh.

Product Long Description: Zktlz Glue is a cross of the famous Zktlz and GG4, this sticky indica-dominant strain packs a powerful terpene profile with sweet and sour fruit undertones.

Product Short Description: A well-balanced, indica-leaning hybrid that is as delicious as it is potent with a lineage of Animal Kookies and GG, and an unmistakable smell.
Product Long Description: Flint & Embers’ Zookies (Animal Kookies x Gorilla Glue) is a well-balanced, indica-leaning hybrid that is as delicious as it is potent. With a lineage of Animal Kookies and Gorilla Glue, this punchy flower has an unmistakable smell - smooth nutty flavours, dotted with vanilla bean and a hint of tropical citrus. Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in - Zookies is hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and then carefully sorted and packed to capture the best bud. These frosty flowers are completely coated in trichomes from tip to tip and feature a dense forest green flower structure, spotted with wavy orange pistils.
