Product Short Description: The Ghost Drops cut of Z-Splitter was bred by Uprising Seed Co. It has a pungent stench of gas and its flavour carries citrus notes.
Product Long Description:
The Ghost Drops cut of Z-Splitter was bred by Uprising Seed Co, hunted by Cultivating Happiness at Mother Labs and grown by ultra-premium craft micro-producer, Natural Earth Craft Cannabis. 
 
Buds are typically large, light green in colour and feature an array of brilliant golden pistils protruding from of a dense layer of trichomes.
 
Z-Splitters overly pungent stench of gas is noticeable as soon as the seal on the jar is broken and its flavour carries citrus notes with a clear reminder of its gassy roots on the exhale.

Product Short Description: Sister plant to Oreo Mint Kush, HHH is an indica with a sweet Limonene smell that smokes smooth. Hand trimmed, hang dried and cured for 11 days.
Product Long Description: Sister plant to Oreo Mint Kush, HHH presents large, beautifully frosted buds with incredibly strong odors of pine, lemon, menthol, and skunk that deliver a smooth smoke. Hand trimmed, hang dried, cured for 11 days, and hand packaged in glass jars.

Product Short Description: Sugarbud GMO Cookies is a hybrid strain cross of GSC and Chemdog, with aromas of musty cellars, savory garlic, sweet spice, and earthy coffee.
Product Long Description: GMO Cookies is an indica-dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the world-famous GSC and classic Chemdog. The buds are thin, long, open-structured and delicate, with a mix of olive green and purple, accentuated by orange hairs and a sugary coat of shimmering trichomes. Sugarbud’s GMO shows all the classic aromas of musty cellars, savory garlic, sweet spice, and earthy coffee. Our collection of unique strains is methodically curated to the highest standards throughout the entire growing cycle. Hang dried and cold barrel cured for up to 28 days, meticulously hand finished and packaged with care. We take Pride. We take our Time.

Product Short Description: A cross between GMO and Sophisticated Lady, Unicorn Poop is a potent hybrid strain bred by ThugPug Genetics.
Product Long Description: Bred by ThugPug Genetics, Unicorn Poop is a cross between GMO and Sophisticated Lady. ThugPug (Gromer Juana) is known for exotic strains with names to match, such as other cultivars like Meat Breath and Stankasaurous. Unicorn Poop follows suit, expressing a rainbow of colour on the buds and strong scents of citrus and fuel.

Product Short Description: Pacific OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid, a Tantalus curation of Goji OG, bred from Nepali OG and Snow Lotus.
Product Long Description: Pacific OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid, a Tantalus curation of Goji OG, bred from Nepali OG and Snow Lotus. Nepali OG, aka Nepali Kush, is a long-lineage classic close to Tahoe OG that brings conical-shaped buds and earthy notes of an OG aroma, while Snow Lotus lays an undercurrent of black cherry and subtle hints of liquorice. The colas of Pacific OG are caked, hand-harvested, and cured, providing a full flavour due in part to dominant terpenes of pinene and nerolidol.

Product Short Description: Premium small-batch flower for the true cannabis connoisseur. SensiMila Legendary Larry is a potent Indica with a very clean and piney aroma.
Product Long Description: Premium small-batch flower for the true cannabis connoisseur. SensiMila Legendary Larry is a potent indica with a very clean and piney aroma that can help you relax and just enjoy the ride.

Product Short Description: For the discount smoker, Potluck is a new take on the “value ounce” – featuring whole flower pouches designed for mixing & matching your ounce.
Product Long Description: For the discount smoker looking for something different, Potluck is a new take on the “value ounce” – featuring whole flower pouches designed for mixing and matching your way to an ounce. Potluck is available in indica, sativa, hybrid 7 g options. The word “pot-luck” appears in the 16th century English work of Thomas Nashe, and used to mean "food provided for an unexpected or uninvited guest, the luck of the pot." Potluck dinners are events where the attendees bring a dish to a meal - a different meal. Potluck indica-dominant hybrid will launch with Banana Cream and will continually introduce new boutique strains as product sells out. This strain emits strong notes of bananas, with a hint of orange and spearmint, and expresses tight lime green buds.

Product Short Description: Upon opening, Tang Breath will hit you with a strong orange aroma and produces buds that are dense and coated in glistening trichomes.
Product Long Description: Tang Breath is a potent THC, Indica-dominant strain that was bred by ThugPug Genetics and cultivated by Jonny Chronic in-house from seed. After testing several phenotypes we found our keeper pheno that glistens with trichomes and has thick orange pistils. This cultivar has a strong orange-citrus aroma with hints of gas.

Product Short Description: Lemon Cheese combines citrus and cheese aromas in a bright green bud made famous by the late Strain Hunter, Franco Loja.
Product Long Description: Lemon Cheese by Jonny Chronic is a moderate THC, sativa-dominant strain that produces tight green buds with thin orange pistils. Lemon Cheese was created by crossing Exodus Cheese and Super Lemon Haze by the legendary Strain Hunter, Franco Loja. We tested several seeds to find the perfect phenotype — our Lemon Cheese has a strong citrus aroma and mild scent of cheese.

Product Short Description: Blueberry Kush has a sweet berry aroma and produces large green buds with vibrant orange pistils.
Product Long Description: Blueberry Kush by Jonny Chronic is a high THC, indica-dominant strain with large, dense, light-green flowers covered in orange pistils. This strain’s lineage consists of Purple Kush and Blueberry cultivars, which is evident by the predominant blueberry and grape aroma that fills the room when you open the jar. Blueberry Kush's terpene profile features a very high myrcene content, making it an ideal night-time strain for some users. Blueberry Kush is hand-trimmed, cured and packaged fresh for you to enjoy.

Product Short Description: An indica-dominant strain from Whistler Cannabis Co. in British Columbia with very strong THC potency potential.
Product Long Description: Bubba Kush from Whistler Cannabis Co. is an indica-dominant strain with very strong THC potency potential that’s grown indoors in British Columbia under LED lighting. Its main terpene is nerolidol (also found in citronella, ginger and orange peels). Bubba Kush is available in 3.5 g of dried flower.

Product Short Description: Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity, and earthy aroma thanks to high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene, and farnesene in its terpene profile.
Product Long Description: Redecan Glueberry OG is a hybrid derived from crossing OG Kush, GG and Blueberry strains characterized by bright green buds, orange pistils and frosty, white trichomes. With high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene, and farnesene in its terpene profile, Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity, and earthy aroma. Like all Redecan flowers, Glueberry OG is harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand, and inspected. Glueberry OG is offered in 1 g of dried flower.

Product Short Description: Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity, and earthy aroma thanks to high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene, and farnesene in its terpene profile.
Product Long Description: Redecan Glueberry OG is a hybrid derived from crossing OG Kush, GG and Blueberry strains characterized by bright green buds, orange pistils and frosty, white trichomes. With high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene, and farnesene in its terpene profile, Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity, and earthy aroma. Like all Redecan flowers, Glueberry OG is harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand, and inspected. Glueberry OG is offered in 1 g of dried flower.

Product Short Description: Fruity Pebbles OG is an indica-dominant strain with an intense gas profile, backed by sweet, dark chocolate notes.
Product Long Description: Fruity Pebbles OG is an indica-dominant strain with a THC potential, balanced by a solid terpene content led by limonene, myrcene and caryophyllene that give off gobs of gas with a strong hit of sweetness resembling dark chocolate notes. Visually, its olive-green buds are generously laced with extra-long orange-hued filaments and covered in frosty trichomes.

Product Short Description: An indica with a rich taste of lemon, herbal tea, and earthy aromas. Hang dried, hand selected, hand portioned, hand packaged and nitrogen sealed.
Product Long Description: Craft Uppercut is a knockout winner for indica lovers. Its large, dense, trichome covered buds pack a rich taste of lemon and herbal tea, while subtle earthy aromas linger in the air. Hang dried, hand selected, hand portioned and hand packaged and finally sealed in nitrogen to preserve quality, humidity, freshness and terpenes to ensure Mood Ring Craft Uppercut arrives in the customer's hands just as it was when it was selected by our award-winning cannabis sommelier.

Product Short Description: Cherry Bomb Gelato is a well-balanced hybrid strain with a sweet flavour and aroma.
Product Long Description: Cherry Bomb Gelato is a well-balanced hybrid and is good as an all-purpose smoke with a sweet flavour and aroma. It is a cross between an indica strain from California that has not been named yet and Mr. Greengenes, a sativa from Hawaii.

Product Short Description: This cultivar’s fruity and lemony taste is reminiscent of berries, and will surely find a special place in your range of tastes.
Product Long Description: Relatively dense pale green flowers with a light-yellow tint, this cultivar has a very strong odour when crushed. Its fruity and lemony taste is reminiscent of berries, and will surely find a special place in your range of tastes.

Product Short Description: With an Intense grape smell, this strain has the right name. The smell is accompanied with strong citrus points.
Product Long Description: Intense grape smell that is accompanied with citrus points, this strain’s name is very fitting.

Product Short Description: Pale green flowers with orange hairs coated in crystal trichomes. The Zsweet will be appreciated by anybody who loves a super sweet flavour.
Product Long Description: Pale green flowers with orange hairs coated in crystal trichomes. The Zsweet will be appreciated by anybody who loves a super sweet flavour.

Product Short Description: Flint & Embers’ Mint Sherbet  is fully-loaded with flavour - a swirling mix of sweet, caramel, gas, cinnamon, floral, and musk.
Product Long Description:
Flint & Embers’ Mint Sherbet (Thin Mint GSC x Sunset Sherbert) is a 50/50 cross between sativa and indica. Taking its cues from the wildly popular cultivar Gelato #33, this bud is fully-loaded with flavour - a swirling mix of sweet, caramel, gas, cinnamon, floral, and musk.

Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in - Mint Sherbert is hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and then carefully sorted and packed to capture the best bud.

These blissful buds flower in dark purple hues, illuminated by fiery orange hairs and a shining white coat of crystal resin.

Product Short Description: Flint & Embers’ Dosi-D (Chem-D x Dosidos) is a gassy, indica-leaning hybrid. With strong OG roots, this one is dense and resinous.
Product Long Description:
Flint & Embers’ Dosi-D (Chem-D x Dosidos) is a gassy, indica-leaning hybrid. With strong OG roots, this one is dense and resinous — producing an intensely pungent aroma with back notes of citrus flavour.

Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in - Dosi-D is hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and then carefully sorted and packed to capture the best bud.

These flashy flowers are wrapped in crystals, dripping in resin and fiercely freckled with tangerine fur.

Product Short Description: Bred by Compound Genetics – KK Mints is a highly potent hybrid indica, the buds are typically smaller and heavily frosted in dense trichome coverage.
Product Long Description: Bred by Compound Genetics - KK Mints is a name we gave this strain, due to the fact that its legacy name is heavily copyrighted in a galaxy far far away. Its genetic lineage is Khalifa Kush x The Menthol – this highly potent hybrid indica has buds that are typically smaller and heavily frosted in dense trichome coverage with vivid yellow-orange pistils, bright green buds and hints of violets & purples. Sweet & earthy aromas, small batch, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Grown without the use of pesticides or chemicals, and non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Bred by Compound Genetics – KK Mints is a highly potent hybrid indica, the buds are typically smaller and heavily frosted in dense trichome coverage.
Product Long Description: Bred by Compound Genetics - KK Mints is a name we gave this strain, due to the fact that its legacy name is heavily copyrighted in a galaxy far far away. Its genetic lineage is Khalifa Kush x The Menthol – this highly potent hybrid indica has buds that are typically smaller and heavily frosted in dense trichome coverage with vivid yellow-orange pistils, bright green buds and hints of violets & purples. Sweet & earthy aromas, small batch, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Grown without the use of pesticides or chemicals, and non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Tiger Cake is a potent cross of Layer Cake x The Menthol. This indica-dominant strain offers notes of sweet cream with hints of gas, petrol and menthol.
Product Long Description: Bred by Compound Genetics - Tiger Cake is a potent cross of Layer Cake x The Menthol. Known for high THC content and large compact buds, this strain is ideal for users that are knowledgable in regards to their tolerance levels. This indica-dominant strain offers notes of sweet cream with hints of gas, petrol and menthol. Small batch, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Grown without the use of chemicals and non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Tiger Cake is a potent cross of Layer Cake x The Menthol. This indica-dominant strain offers notes of sweet cream with hints of gas, petrol and menthol.
Product Long Description: Bred by Compound Genetics - Tiger Cake is a potent cross of Layer Cake x The Menthol. Known for high THC content and large compact buds, this strain is ideal for users that are knowledgable in regards to their tolerance levels. This indica-dominant strain offers notes of sweet cream with hints of gas, petrol and menthol. Small batch, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Grown without the use of chemicals and non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Purple Sunset is known for sweet fruity notes, but also slight floral and sour aromas. Minty green buds with deep purple undertones.
Product Long Description: Bred by Ethos Genetics - Purple Sunset is known for sweet fruity notes, but also slight floral and sour aromas. Minty green buds with deep purple undertones, provide the backdrop for beautiful trichome coverage. Our product is grown without the use of any form of pesticides, and is non-irradiated. Small batch (under 700 sqft rooms), hang dried, hand trimmed, and hand packaged. Non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: The one and only Bacio Gelato. If you know, you know.
Product Long Description: The one and only Bacio Gelato. If you know, you know.

Product Short Description: Imagine sweet apple, with a subtle hints of mint and pine.
Product Long Description: This unique cross has gas! Dark hued buds with hints of olive green, caked sugar leaves, contrasting orange pistils, and frosted with a healthy coat of trichomes. Imagine sweet apple, with a subtle hints of mint and pine.

Product Short Description: This renowned OG strain packs a serious flavour punch and is not one to take lightly. Sweet, skunky and straight gas.
Product Long Description: Sweet, skunky and straight gas. This renowned OG strain packs a serious flavour punch and is not one to take lightly. Chunky and dense buds, with fiery red pistils that offer serious bag appeal.

Product Short Description: Queen SanG is reminiscent of a summer fruit salad, sharp oranges and lemons overwhelm your senses, followed by that signature diesel fuel aroma.
Product Long Description: Reminiscent of a summer fruit salad with sharp orange and lemon scents, Queen SanG fills the room with a delightfully fresh bouquet that invigorates your senses. The signature diesel aroma from the Royal Kush lineage confirms you’re experiencing an authentic, Northern Cali strain blessed with Mandelbrot’s golden touch. Queen Sangria is a sativa-leaning hybrid bred by California's Emerald Mountain Legacy and derived from a selected cross of Mimosa x Royal Kush. A rare limonene and pinene dominant cultivar, the Queen’s genetic pedigree is second to none and an experience you'll want to share.

Product Short Description: A cross of Mazar Kush and Oaxaca Highland, the pallet is rich and creamy with a burst of sweet floral flavours, citrus and fruit.
Product Long Description:
A cross of Mazar Kush (a strain named for the holy city in Afghanistan) and Oaxaca Highland (the Mexican region famous for its mole sauce).

The aroma evokes the woodland of Oaxaca, and the ancient spice trails of Afghanistan. The pallet is rich and creamy with a burst of sweet floral flavours, citrus and fruit. This indica has a dense bud structure that you come to expect from a premium Kush.

Product Short Description: WINK WINK brings you only the highest quality, small-batch flower from the best growers. No matter what's in your bag, quality is guaranteed.
Product Long Description:
We're letting you in on a little secret. WINK WINK is our way of bringing you only the highest quality, small-batch flower from the best micro-cultivators across the country. We're dropping the latest and greatest flower in real time, with different strains and lots for you to try. We’ve got nothing to hide, so we’re uploading all the specs online so you can learn more about what’s in your bag and the growers behind it. Visit winkcannabis.com to unlock more information about your flower. No matter what's in your bag, quality is guaranteed.

This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: This triple cross of Zkittlez and Gelato 33 x Orange Punch from legacy breeders TunaaaaRoom is craft-grown, slow-cured, hand-trimmed, and hang-dried.
Product Long Description:
WINK TUNAAAAROOM RNTZ MUFFINS (Zkittlez x Gelato 33 x Orange Punch) is a delicious treat for anyone looking to experience a burst of fruity flavours with citrus, creamy, and sweet flavour notes. Bred by the best at TunaaaaRoom, the bud is dense and frosty and has been indoor-grown, hang-dried, hand-trimmed, and slow-cured to protect trichomes, preserve terpenes, and retain bud moisture. Grown in Alberta by Noble Growth Corp. Dominant terpenes include caryophyllene, myrcene, and farnesene. 

This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: Full of mouth-watering blueberry and citrus flavours, this cross of Blue Cookies x Sunset Sherbet is hang-dried, hand-trimmed, and flushed for 14 days.
Product Long Description:
WINK CRAFT BLUE SHERBET (Blue Cookies x Sunset Sherbet) delivers a punch of mouth-watering blueberry and citrus flavours. Known for its beautiful lime green and purple hued buds, the flower is hang-dried, hand-trimmed, and flushed for 14 days for pure white ash. CRAFT BLUE SHERBET was bred by The Plug Seedbank and grown in Ontario.
This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: WINK DAIRY CREAM (ICC x Kush Mints #11) is BC grown, featuring a mix of creamy-vanilla and funk flavours.
Product Long Description:
WINK DAIRY CREAM (ICC x Kush Mints #11), also known as Dairy Queen, is one strain you don’t want to miss out on. Bred by Seed Junky Genetics, and pheno hunted to perfection, this flower carries a powerful gassy and creamy-vanilla flavour , with a heavy funk from Kush Mints. Just like the name suggests, these buds are caked with frosty trichomes. Dominant terpenes include limonene, caryophyllene, and linalool. DAIRY CREAM is indoor-grown, hand-groomed, hang-dried and grown by Dunesberry Farms in Kamloops BC by a Master Grower with over 35 years of experience.

This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description: A grower-exclusive phenotype of Face Off OG x Animal Mints x GSC with high total terps. Tastes like a bowl of your favourite fruity cereals.
Product Long Description:
WINK CRAFT ANIMAL FACE COOKIES is a unique, grower-exclusive phenotype of Face Off OG x Animal Mints x GSC. Believe us when we say this one’s got high terps. These beautiful, dense buds are covered in a healthy dose of milky-white trichomes, and smells and tastes like a bowl of your favourite fruity cereals! Our partners at Paper Craft Cannabis have a combined 25 years of growing experience and grow in a state-of-the-art hydroponic indoor facility where they hand-trim, hang-dry, and jar-cure all their flower. Dominant terps include caryophyllene, myrcene, and limonene.  

This bud is sustainably packaged in 30% post-consumer recycled packaging and includes a humidity pack for freshness. WINK donates 10% of profits to homelessness and Plastic Bank.

Product Short Description:
This cultivar smells like a freshly-iced blackberry strudel - fruit-forward, with undertones
of fuel, Canadian maple, and mulled spice.
Product Long Description: Our Blackberry Gelato pre-roll smells like a freshly-iced blackberry strudel - fruit-forward, with undertones of fuel, Canadian maple, and mulled spices. A crowd favorite with a caryophyllene-dominant terpene profile to add a hint of black pepper and spice. Limonene, farnesene, and linalool exaggerate the light-but-fruity overall flavour, rounded out with myrcene. The ripe flowers are round, very dense, and sticky - especially once cured. Visually, they're a West Coast Rainforest-green, with hints of dark purple throughout, contributing to the cultivar's name. This in-house bred cultivar is the result of a cross between a Jordan Of The Islands Blackberry Kush & Jet Fuel Gelato, and an ensuing pheno-hunt to curate the ideal flower for the pre-roll market.

Product Short Description: Vivid and beautiful dense buds, that are glittering with frosty trichomes.
Product Long Description: True to its name, ICS produces vivid and beautiful dense buds, that are glittering with frosty trichomes. Enjoy a deliciously sweet, cotton candy-like aroma with an exhale that is creamy and slightly floral.

Product Short Description: Daily Special’s Gasberry Pie is dried flower at a low price. Its medium-sized, lime-green buds carry rich notes of berries, gasoline, and wood.
Product Long Description: Daily Special’s Gasberry Pie is dried flower at a low price. Distinguished by medium-sized, lime-green buds with purple streaks and high trichome density. Bred from Wedding Cake and Jet Fuel genetics, Gasberry Pie carries very rich and distinct notes of berries, gasoline, and wood. All our dried flower is grown under the highest quality standards.

Product Short Description: Daily Special’s Gasberry Pie is dried flower at a low price. Its medium-sized, lime-green buds carry rich notes of berries, gasoline, and wood.
Product Long Description: Daily Special’s Gasberry Pie is dried flower at a low price. Distinguished by medium-sized, lime-green buds with purple streaks and high trichome density. Bred from Wedding Cake and Jet Fuel genetics, Gasberry Pie carries very rich and distinct notes of berries, gasoline, and wood. All our dried flower is grown under the highest quality standards.

Product Short Description: Cyber Fuel OG is bred from OG Kush and Wedding Cake. This hybrid has notes of orange cream soda, gasoline, and garlic.
Product Long Description: Cyber Fuel OG is bred from OG Kush and Wedding Cake genetics. This hybrid strain is characterized by large, dark green, and deep purple flowers with high trichome density. As for its flavour profile, Cyber Fuel OG carries very unique and aromatic notes of orange cream soda, gas, and garlic – derived from its primary terpenes, limonene, beta-myrcene, and trans-caryophyllene. Cyber Fuel OG is grown and cultivated under the highest quality standards.

Product Short Description: Alien Cake 3030 is bred from Miracle Alien Cookies with notes of citrus, cake, pine, and ammonia.
Product Long Description: Alien Cake 3030 is a sativa hybrid strain from Drift, bred from MAC (Miracle Alien Cookies) genetics. Distinguished by medium-sized, light-green buds with purple streaks and high trichome density, Alien Cake 3030 carries a very strong aroma of lemon, citrus, cake, cream cheese, pine, and ammonia – derived from its primary terpenes, trans-caryophyllene, terpinolene, and limonene.  Alien Cake 3030 is grown and cultivated under the highest quality standards.

Product Short Description: Lemon Mech OG is a hybrid strain that carries a very complex aroma of lemon, sour tangerines, cheese, and vanilla notes.
Product Long Description: Lemon Mech OG is a hybrid from Drift, bred from Lemon OG genetics. This strain is characterized by medium-sized, dark green and orange conical buds covered in a dense layer of trichomes. Lemon Mech OG’s flavour profile consists of lemon, sour tangerines, cheese, and vanilla notes – derived from its primary terpenes, trans-caryophyllene, limonene, and alpha-humulene. Lemon Mech OG is grown and cultivated under the highest quality standards.

Product Short Description: A sativa-dominant cultivar with a refreshingly spicy scent, subtle hints of lemon grass, freshly cut pine and Thai basil.
Product Long Description:
A sativa-dominant cultivar consisting of Stardog and Arise, has an unmistakable bouquet with a refreshingly spicy scent and subtle hints of lemon grass, freshly cut pine and Thai basil.
Pheno hunted and selected by MSIKU.  Hang dried and hand trimmed to preserve aroma and flavours.

Product Short Description: A highly sought after genetic from the Swamp Boys with notes of gas and earthy undertones. Be sure to check this one off your bucket list!
Product Long Description: This powerful cultivar from the acclaimed Swamp Boys is a modern take on a classic genetic consisting of Chem 91, Star Fighter and White 91. This award-winning strain produces a flavorful smoke with warming gassy notes and earthy undertones. Be sure to check this one off your bucket list!

Product Short Description: Greenman Acres Grand Daddy Purple (GDP) is a sun-drenched indica dominant strain with a lemon and fresh fruit nose.
Product Long Description: GDP is a sun-drenched indica dominant strain. It has been slowly dried, cured for a minimum of 21 days and lovingly hand-finished. Possesses a lemon and fresh fruit nose, boasting a rich terpene mix of alpha-pinene, myrcene, caryophyllene, limonene and beta-pinene.  Greenman Acres is family owned and operated.  We share a passion for cannabis and strive to produce some of best  cannabis available.  We take an enormous amount of care when growing and caring for our plants. If it's not good enough for our table, it won't make it to yours. Passion. Craft. Quality. Greenman Acres.

Product Short Description: LowKey Haze by MTL cannabis is a complex sativa-dominant hybrid with a vibrant citrusy earthy aroma and a sweet exhale.
Product Long Description: LowKey Amnesia Haze is a complex sativa-dominant hybrid, a cross of Haze, Southeast Asian, Hawaiian and Jamaican landrace strains. Small batch, indoor grown, and hang dried this cultivar packs a citrusy, fruity, and earthy punch, with a slightly sweet exhale.

Product Short Description: Stay frosty with the icy frozen glow of Cryo Chronic. An indica strain that’s a gleaming glacier with powerful spicy, pepper and earthy aromas.
Product Long Description: Stay frosty with the icy frozen glow of Cryo Chronic. An indica strain that’s a gleaming glacier with remarkably unique light green buds, and hits of purple and blue that are absolutely blanketed in white and golden trichomes. The structure of these buds will give you chills, with super dense yet fox tailed buds reminiscent of a snowcap. Powerful spicy, pepper and earthy aromas await within this snowstorm of a strain…

Product Short Description: Cuban Linx is a sativa hybrid strain with a refreshing lemony aroma that is accentuated by hints of gassy diesel and a touch of spiciness.
Product Long Description: The diverse richness of exotic terpenes found in Cuban Linx give these buds an invigorating lemony aroma that is accentuated by hints of gassy diesel and a touch of spiciness. A truly refreshing strain, Cuban Linx was bred by crossing TK Skunk and Trigerian. The result is a huge bud with a shape that resembles corn on the cob.

Product Short Description: This indica hybrid is known to pack a punch. A cross of the popular Blue Sherbert with GMO, this strain is one that is hard to forget after trying.
Product Long Description:
Sherbert (Sunset Sherbert x Blue Cookies) mixed with the uber popular GMO (Garlic Cookies)
strain is one that is hard to forget after trying. The onion and garlic terpenes come out heavily during grinding and leave a slight floral aroma in the air afterwards. Upon consumption, you can taste the aroma of the garlic on the back of your tongue.

As are all our products, this strain is non-irradiated and pesticide-free. Using only handpicked
medium to large crown buds with no shake or trim. This flavourful product is flushed for 14
days, hang dried and hand trimmed for the finest of care and quality. Cured to craft standards,
in small batches, for highest terpenes.

This strain was grown in craft rooms less than 1000 sq ft. and is provided in a matte black glass jars using only crown buds. This elusive strain will quickly become your favourite once you’ve had a chance to take it in.

Product Short Description: Sweet with hints of vanilla, this cultivar presents with dark green flowers and purple hues.
Product Long Description: The aromatics on this wonderful cultivar are true to its Gelato #33 and Tropicana Cookies lineage. Extremely sweet and almost candy like, with a hint of vanilla coming through. The aesthetic presents dark green flowers with purple hues. Between the aromatics and the colours, this may be the most beautiful genetic we have grown. Hang-dried and hand-trimmed to preserve aroma and flavours.

Product Short Description: Tweed GG#4 is a hybrid strain that some associate with earthy, woody, and citrus flavours.
Product Long Description: Tweed GG#4 is a hybrid strain is a cross of Chem Sister, Sour dubb, and Chocolate Diesel. Its buds are fluffy and covered in dense trichome coverage. Some associate earthy, woody, and citrus flavours with the Tweed GG#4 strain.

Product Short Description: A potent whole flower indica, GG#4 is known for its pungent earthy and diesel aroma, and potency. Comes with a humidity device for lasting freshness.
Product Long Description: This potent whole flower indica strain contains high THC levels and produces a strong, skunky perfume when burned. It’s known for its earthy and pungent attributes, and its heavy resin content. Packed with a humidity device to extend for lasting freshness. Quality cannabis, everyday fares.

Product Short Description: A potent whole flower indica, GG#4 is known for its pungent earthy and diesel aroma, and potency. Comes with a humidity device for lasting freshness.
Product Long Description: This potent whole flower indica strain contains high THC levels and produces a strong, skunky perfume when burned. It’s known for its earthy and pungent attributes, and its heavy resin content. Packed with a humidity device to extend for lasting freshness. Quality cannabis, everyday fares.

Product Short Description: Dense, elongated buds with funky aromas of spice and garlic thanks a cross of GMO and Mendo Breath.
Product Long Description: Available for only a limited time, Doja GMO Garlic Breath is an indica dominant strain created by crossing Mendo Breath with GMO. This strain features a powerful aroma and overall savory flavour, featuring spicy undertones and an unmistakably funky, garlic-like aroma. Expect dense and elongated buds covered in trichomes, with an overall light green colour.

Product Short Description: Go Chill Sour OG Cheese is an indica-dominant strain with a pungent earthy cheese flavour and a potent diesel aftertaste.
Product Long Description: Go Chill Sour OG Cheese is an indica-dominant strain with a pungent earthy cheese flavour and a potent diesel aftertaste. Complementing the sharp taste, the strain offers a gentle floral aroma. The plant is a grower’s dream, light green in colour, packed with dense buds, and covered in orange pistils and tons of trichomes. FIGR dried flower products are hand selected to ensure dense, high-quality buds are in every package.

Product Short Description: A potent sativa-leaning strain with spade-shaped buds and burnt orange pistils. Expect a sweet citrus aroma with hints of diesel and spice.
Product Long Description: Big Buds. Big Terps. Big Bag. Not all flower is worthy of an ounce, except Big Bag. Lemon Margy’s parents (lineage) Lemon Jack x Frozen Margy have come together to create a bright citrus aroma thanks to a unique bushel of terps: terpinolene, limonene, β-ocimene, myrcene, β-pinene. Expect to experience a sweet citrus trifecta of lemon, lime and grapefruit with an undercurrent of diesel and faint finishing notes of spice. Lemon Margy is a sativa-leaning strain with dense spade-shaped buds, featuring burnt orange pistils and a healthy coat of trichomes. Just imagine, all those citrusy terps just waiting for you in that Big Bag…

Product Short Description: Sativa-dominant Lemon Z is a delight for the nose and taste buds, with a veritable rainbow of zesty citrus and subtle, sweet herbal flavours.
Product Long Description:
A classically sativa-dominant cross of Las Vegas Skunk and Zktlz, this cultivar expresses a veritable rainbow of zesty citrus and subtle, sweet herbal flavours. The bright green, crystal covered buds delight the nose and taste buds with highest terpene concentrations of caryophyllene, myrcene, and limonene - especially noticeable after a trip through your grinder.

Lemon Z UP20™ flower is indoor-grown in our Atholville, New Brunswick facility and promises to deliver 20% THC or higher. Every time.

Product Short Description:
Gelato x Sherb x (Gelato 41 x Animal Mints bx1). These buds are covered in a thick layer of
trichomes, with a  sweet nose and the flavours to match.
Product Long Description: Gelato x Sherb x (Gelato 41 x Animal Mints bx1). These buds are green and purple covered in a thick layer of trichomes. The buds pack a very strong sweet nose and the flavours to match. This is a premium variety hands down for those seeking quality with extraordinary colors, flavours and scents. These buds are very unique and the trichome density will surprise even the most experienced cannabis customers. This product was grown in a small batch craft cannabis system. These flowers were grown in sea of green, drip irrigation, hand harvested, hand trimmed and hand packed.

Product Short Description: Twd.28 Himalayan Kush is an indica dominant strain with high THC potential.
Product Long Description: Twd.28 Himalayan Kush is an indica dominant strain with high THC potential and minimal amounts of CBD. It originates in a mountain range in the Himalayan region. Its dense buds are covered in trichomes, giving off strong aromas of earth & pine.

Product Short Description: HWY 8 Golden Pineapple is a cross between Golden Goat and Pineapple Kush, and has a sweet, fruity smell and taste.
Product Long Description: HWY 8’s team has over 45 years of experience growing cannabis, with generations of skills and perspectives to pull from. With an exceptional genetic library of over 200 cultivars and 3,000 seeds, HWY 8 aims to change the industry by focusing on high-quality, high-potency strains. HWY 8 Golden Pineapple is a cross between Golden Goat and Pineapple Kush, and is grown in an indoor controlled environment to produce a clean, premium product. Each plant is grown in Pro Mix soil, then hang-dried in rooms that are both temperature and humidity controlled. The plants are then hand-trimmed to ensure the integrity of each bud is intact. Golden Pineapple has tight, light green buds with a hint of amber. They’re sticky and spongy to the touch, and with a sweet and fruity smell. Golden Pineapple's terpene profile includes ocimene, farnesene, and limonene.

Product Short Description: This indica dominant strain is highly potent with a sweet, creamy taste that will remind you exactly of its namesake.
Product Long Description: Ice Cream Cake is a cross between Wedding Cake and Gelato #33 -- hybrid strains that are already very popular on either side of the Atlantic. Inheriting the best traits from both of the parent strains, Ice Cream Cake is famous for high THC levels, flavours and tastes. This indica dominant strain is highly potent with a sweet, creamy taste that will remind you exactly of its namesake.

Product Short Description: From Canada's first 100% Indigenous Licensed Producer,  Island Cherry is a hybrid strain with sweet cherry flavour and strong THC and terpenes levels.
Product Long Description: Island Cherry (Mohawk translation: Kawehnoke Eri'ko:wa), brought to you by SEV7N, the first 100% indigenous owned and operated LP based on Cornwall Island in the Akwesasne Mohawk Territory, is an indica-dominant hybrid with strong cannabinoid and terpene levels. Bred by crossing Purple Punch and Black Cherry Pie, this dessert strain has a loud flavour profile full of mouthwatering sweet cherries and floral undertones.

Product Short Description: From Canada's first 100% Indigenous Licensed Producer,  Island Cherry is a hybrid strain with sweet cherry flavour and strong THC and terpenes levels.

Its naturally occurring terpenes underline an herbal aroma with sour tangerine overtones. The light green buds present a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

This rare, unique strain is packed with irresistible aromas of s’mores, accented by earthy tones

Product Long Description: Kush Mints is one of the most densely trichome covered buds the growers at Broken Coast have ever seen. The buds are exceptionally shaped with bright green and purple colouration, hidden under the thick covering of crystals. Expect a thick dusting of kief to form on everything that touches these buds. Rife with notes of mint, hash and a subtly fruity scent, you’ll want to experience this quality hybrid again and again. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang cured and hand trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Product Short Description: Dim MAC has the best of both genetics, the appearance is more MAC leaning with the density of Dark Helmet and hints of creamy citrus and cookie dough.
Product Long Description: A first release from Carmel’s in-house breeding program, Dim MAC was born by crossing Drew’s Dark Helmet with a MAC male. The result is a beautiful flower that delivers the best of both genetics. The appearance is more MAC leaning with the density and flavour profile of the Dark Helmet. Expect hints of creamy citrus and cookie dough.

Product Short Description: Distinguished by its mossy green buds, flecked with amber calyxes and coated in trichomes. A pungent earthy aroma and sweet floral funk on the finish.
Product Long Description: Do Si Dos is the offspring of OG Kush Breath (a GSC phenotype) and Face/Off OG. Distinguished by mossy green buds, flecked with amber calyxes, and coated in trichomes, this bud has a pungent earthy aroma and sweet, slightly floral funk on the finish. Nith & Grand flower is grown in small batches, hang dried, slow cured and hand trimmed.

Our most potent sativa carries a unique blend of strong floral aromas, notes of grape with hints of sugary and spiky greens. Nugz Early Lemon Berry is hang-dried, slow-cured in curing barrels and packaged in an air-tight pouch for ultimate freshness. Early Lemon Berry is a sativa-dominant strain of cannabis. The bud smells like a mix of sweet lemons, grapefruit and sugary sweet berries. The flavour is quite similar to the smell, but the taste of the exhale is what earned its popularity. The aroma produced by these flowers is strong but not pungent. Expect medium to large buds, dense and covered in trichomes.

Product Short Description: The genetic make-up of this strain contributes to what it’s best known for, its funk. Expect bright green buds with brilliant orange pistils.
Product Long Description: The Ghost Drops cut of First-Class Funk was bred by Compound Genetics, hunted by Cultivating Happiness and grown by several ultra-premium, hand selected, and vetted craft micro-producers.  The genetic make-up of this strain contributes to what it’s best known for, its funk. Bright green buds feature dark green undertones, highlighted by brilliant orange pistils and coated with dense diamond like trichomes. Its heavy nose smacks you in the face as you crack the jar, with a pungent funky, creamy, fragrance compounded by a dense scent of jet fuel, making for an undeniably dank aroma. The funk tastes as funky as it smells with notes of fermented anise and fennel coupled by gassy aftertaste as it rolls off the pallet. First Class Funk makes for a vibrant session. The 14 g format contains small buds.

The tightly-wound, smaller buds are frosted beneath a thick coat of silver trichomes, often with a purple hue, mixed with dusted orange pistils. Chem OG produces a strong, skunky perfume with undertones of rubber when burned.

Smoking it coats your mouth with floral, fresh flavours and a pleasantly confusing aftertaste. This craft flower is grown with zero pesticides, hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cured and hand packed in batches small enough to treat each plant like they’re family.

Product Long Description: Dense light green buds are spiked with orange and yellow hairs in this cross of Banana Kush and the Strawberry phenotype of Bubble Gum. With the fruit-forward aromas true to its namesakes, BC Strawnana hits with notes of banana and earthy undertones. This is a high THC indica-leaning hybrid.

Supplier Name: Trichome JWC Acquisition Corp. dba JWC
Product Short Description: An indica leaning hybrid strain with purple hues that contrast sharply with orange pistils and are balanced by different shades of green.
Product Long Description:
Purple hues contrast sharply with orange pistils and are balanced by different shades of green. A hybrid strain that leans slightly to the indica side of the spectrum and smokes with flavours of citrus, orange zest and earth.

WAGNERS believe in hard work and Well Made Weed. Our Blue Lime Pie strain is just that, Well Made.

Product Short Description: This high-CBD, low-THC hybrid strain has strong notes of citrus and pine, with some earthiness thanks to higher levels of myrcene.
Product Long Description: This high-CBD, low-THC hybrid strain has strong notes of citrus and pine, with some earthiness thanks to higher levels of myrcene.

Product Short Description: Cannatonic Blackberry Kush is a sativa dominant strain with an extra kick of CBD. A sweetly fruity smell and taste with notes of a woody background.
Product Long Description: Cannatonic Blackberry Kush is one title in the Maricann dried flower ‘library’ which can be judged under the cover of its name. The sativa-dominant balanced has an extra kick of CBD. Its exceptionally-beautiful inflorescent buds are dark green, orange-pigmented with hues of purple and are saturated with delicious white crystals. A sweetly fruity smell and taste with notes of berry and sugar mingled with a woody background reminiscent of fruit punch infused with lemon-lime soda. Its terpene profile is headlined by myrcene, found in mangoes; lavender and birch bark’s linalool; and the herbaceous pinene, present in rosemary, basil and parsley.

Product Short Description: BC-grown indica with aromas of sweet fruit, mint, and diesel.
Product Long Description: Smooth, with aromas of sweet fruit, mint, and diesel, Bubble Mints is a marriage made right here in BC. An indica-leaning cross of Wedding Cake and Wedding Crasher, this handpicked phenotype offers fruit-forward aromas and flavours from terpenes that include caryophyllene, limonene, and linalool. Grown in Pure Sunfarms’ modern greenhouse in BC’s Fraser Valley, its frosty flowers display an attractive range of greens with a hint of violet. Hand harvested and hand groomed.

Product Short Description: Chemdawg OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid cultivar that combines diesel aromas from parent Chemdawg with sour, piney notes from OG Kush.
Product Long Description: Chemdawg OG is a sativa-dominant hybrid cultivar that combines diesel aromas from parent Chemdawg with sour, piney notes from OG Kush. The result: a pungent and skunky strain that truly does justice to its esteemed lineage.

Product Short Description: Cherry Cheesecake offers consumers the delicious scent of sweet cherries and dark chocolate with a potently dank twist.
Product Long Description: Cherry Cheesecake offers consumers the delicious scent of sweet cherries and dark chocolate with a potently dank twist. RC Supply Co. is the name of the farmgate storefront on the site of Medz Cannabis Inc., a unique federally licensed, small batch, cannabis production and processing facility in the Greater Toronto Area. RC Supply Co. brings this offering of indoor-grown craft cannabis that is free of pesticides, non-irradiated, hand harvested and trimmed after a long cure time.

Product Short Description: Cherry Juice is an indica-dominant hybrid of Cherry AK and Kush Mints #11 with frosty dense buds, high potency and a loud terpene profile.
Product Long Description: Itopian brings an in-house Jamaican favourite to Canada. The name says it all with sharp notes of cherry and mint. This craft cultivar combines the best of both worlds, high THC and terpene content, along with dense buds covered in trichomes. Grown in coco under LED lights, hang-dried, cold cured and hand-trimmed in British Columbia.

Product Short Description: A triple cross of Chocolate Diesel, Chocolate Thai and Sour Dubb with flavours of chocolate, guava and a hint of sour and a gassy fruity aroma.
Product Long Description: Do the Chocolate Dubstep with this rare sativa. A fascinating triple cross of Chocolate Diesel, Chocolate Thai and Sour Dubb. The flavours of chocolate, guava and a hint of sour dance on your tongue while the gassy fruity aroma overtakes the dance floor.

Product Short Description: This aromatic, high-THC sativa kicks off with a splash of citrusy limonene, followed by a sweet myrcene undertone of a fully ripened mango on exhale.
Product Long Description: Citrus Skunk is a high-THC, terpene-rich sativa with delicious tropical fruit flavours and aromas. The sensory experience when consuming this aromatic, skunky, highly potent sativa kicks off with a bright splash of citrusy/sour limonene sunshine on inhale, subtly followed by the sweet, musky myrcene undertone of a fully ripened mango on exhale. Citrus Skunk’s sativa-typical effects come on quickly and powerfully. Citrus Skunk exemplifies GreenSeal’s commitment to the highest level of cannabis quality, with flowers displaying lime green, tightly knit, trichome-covered calyxes intertwined with fiery tendrils of bright orange hairs. Upon opening a bag and pulling out a chunky bud, the first impulse is to take a photo!

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: A sativa-dominant small-batch strain with very strong THC potency potential and fruity, sour, earthy and citrus flavour.
Product Long Description: Cobra Lips is a small-batch sativa from BZAM offering very strong THC potency potential. If the name isn't enough to spark your imagination, try sparking up this cross between Chemdawg and Appalachia and experience its fruity, sour, earthy and citrus flavours for yourself. Didn't think you'd get a chance to taste Cobra Lips in your lifetime, did you? Well pucker up. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better™.

Product Short Description: BC-grown hybrid with aromas of berry, sweet gas, and vanilla.
Product Long Description: Berry Cream Puff, a flavourful high-THC hybrid, is a proprietary cultivar created by the Pure Sunfarms growers. A Cake Crasher cross, Berry Cream Puff offers delicious notes of tropical berry, sweet gas, and vanilla from terpenes that include caryophyllene, limonene, and linalool. Grown in Pure Sunfarms’ modern greenhouse in BC’s Fraser Valley, its dense flowers appear brushed with strokes of purple, under a heavy frosting of trichomes. Hand harvested and hand groomed.

Product Short Description: BC-grown hybrid with aromas of berry, sweet gas, and vanilla.
Product Long Description: Berry Cream Puff, a flavourful high-THC hybrid, is a proprietary cultivar created by the Pure Sunfarms growers. A Cake Crasher cross, Berry Cream Puff offers delicious notes of tropical berry, sweet gas, and vanilla from terpenes that include caryophyllene, limonene, and linalool. Grown in Pure Sunfarms’ modern greenhouse in BC’s Fraser Valley, its dense flowers appear brushed with strokes of purple, under a heavy frosting of trichomes. Hand harvested and hand groomed.

Product Short Description: Bold fruit flavour from Blueberry backed by the potency of GG#4. Berry Smasher provides a satisfying smoke at an affordable price.
Product Long Description: Bold fruit flavour from Blueberry backed by the potency of GG#4. Berry Smasher provides a satisfying smoke at an affordable price.

Product Short Description: This rare cultivar possess a sweet, fruity flavour with notes of cookies and cake. With beautifully dense buds.
Product Long Description: Freedom Cannabis' Birthday Cake possess a sweet aroma while providing a sweet fruity flavour with notes of cookies and cake. This indica-dominant strain (Freedom's Latitude product line) is packaged in a Mylar bag.

Product Short Description: Black Diamond is a nearly pure indica known for producing highly potent flowers with dense conical shaped buds.
Product Long Description: Black Diamond is a nearly pure indica known for producing highly potent flowers with dense conical shaped buds. The genetic expression leans toward its Triangle Kush parent, which can be traced back to the legendary breeders of the Florida Everglades. The other parent is ‘88 G13 Hash Plant, which gives Black Triangle its frosted forest appearance, powerful Kush aroma and subtle vanilla overtones.

Product Short Description: Black Mamba by Ritual Green is a potent indica-dominant hybrid that provides a tangy yogurt, mango aroma when given a nice squeeze.
Product Long Description: Black Mamba by Ritual Green - a potent indica-dominant hybrid cultivar that is believed to be a cross of Granddaddy Purple and Black Domina strains. Black Mamba has dense, solid buds caked in trichomes that are purple and green in colour. This particular phenotype has a strong, unique aroma, reminiscent of over-ripe mangoes and creamy, tangy yogurt that intensify when given a light squeeze.

Product Short Description: Blueberry Fuego (Slurricane x Wedding Crasher) is a rare and unique cultivar bred by Seed Junky Genetics boasting heavy blueberry gas terpenes.
Product Long Description: What type of berry this strain smells like is widely debated but blueberry and blackberries come to mind first. Every waft of Blueberry Fuego feels like you're getting slapped in the face with a blueberry muffin. Consumers can expect smooth and creamy muffin terpenes at first with a strong berry aftertaste. This particular phenotype was selected by Noble Growth because of its heavy blueberry dessert terpenes. The strain was bred by Seed Junky Genetics crossing the infamous Slurricane with Symbiotic Genetics Wedding Crasher.

Product Short Description: King Kush is a high-THC, indica strain with big buds that have a tangy, spicy flavour with hints of woody lavender.
Product Long Description: King Kush is a high-THC, indica-dominant strain with big sticky buds that produce a tangy, spicy flavour with undercurrents of cedar and lavender from a terpene profile of beta-caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene. This legacy favourite has been parent to a host of undeniably classic genetics. This treasured strain is an exceptional indica. Grown by United Greeneries and distributed under the 18twelve banner.

Product Short Description: Animal Face takes the piney, gassy terpene profile and potency from Face Off OG and pairs it with the cookie flavoured smoothness of Animal Mints.
Product Long Description: Animal Face comes from a very distinct lineage combining Face Off OG and Animal Mints. The buds grow extremely dense and round. The bag appeal and nose if very distinct. This bud has a sweet sugary nutty flavour with hints of mint and earth upon exhale. The aroma is just as delicious, with a light hint of pine and diesel as the buds are burned. Animal Face buds have dense mossy green buds with dark orange hairs and a coating of bright amber crystal trichomes.

Product Short Description: Animal Sorbet is an indica dominant hybrid strain produced by crossing Animal Cookies and Sunset Sherbet. It has hints of spice and sour citrus.
Product Long Description: Everything micro producer Quadessence touches turns into a delectable treat and Animal Sorbet is no different. The curing is perfected, creating a nose that will blow your mind and make you want to keep the pouch open all day long. The aromas have a sweetness with gas and cream on the nose, plus a hint of spicy, sour citrus. Flavours include nutty cookies with a floral undertone. Each Pouch is hand-filled to ensure the quality of the flower is preserved and you get the flower you have waited for all day.

Product Short Description: Bold, large, and iced out buds deliver a sweet melon flavour.
Product Long Description: Avalanche was pheno-hunted off a cross of Lava Cake and Fleetwood Mac. These buds are bold, large, and completely stacked with icy trichomes, and produce a sweet melon flavour.

Product Short Description: B. Banner’s aroma is a mix of floral, earthy and sweet scents with a sweet, fruity, strawberry smoke that brings out those earthy kush flavours.
Product Long Description: B. Banner’s aroma is a mix of floral, earthy, and sweet scents. It has a sweet, fruity, strawberry smoke, and really brings out those earthy kush flavours which originate from the many frosted trichomes encasing the buds. This high potency strain finishes with a boasting terpene profile of 3.9%. A sativa dominant strain which was formed when OG Kush was combined with Strawberry Diesel.

Product Short Description: Crafted for its world-renowned flavour. The sweet taste of honey combined with grape and berry aromas deliver a unique and balanced terpene profile.
Product Long Description: Bamboo Honey is a delightful strain crafted for its exceptional taste and packed with a world-renowned flavour that everyone enjoys. The sweet and sugary taste of honey combined with sweet grapes is creatively bred through the crossing of Do-Si-Dos, Platinum Cookies, and Purple Punch together. This genetic lineage produces a terpene profile and potency that is as strong and sweet as the name itself. These dense buds are magnificently covered in a glistening layer of frosted trichomes that makes it look as beautiful as it tastes.

Product Short Description: BC Mango Melon OG is a potent cross between Watermelon Zkittlez x Tahoe Hydro OG. Its flavour is like a warm cup of Earl Grey tea on a cool day.
Product Long Description: BC Mango Melon OG is a potent cross between Watermelon Zkittlez x Tahoe Hydro OG. Its dense and unique buds are visually stimulating. Dark and light green buds with pops of light purple through a blanket of frosty trichomes. BC Mango Melon OG pulls in a distinct nutty aroma, underscored by a warm lavender finish. Its flavour is like a warm cup of Earl Grey tea on a cool day.

Product Short Description: Citizen Stash Jungle Breath brings the expected Kush traits of gas and skunk notes with fruity and citrus flavours.
Product Long Description: Citizen Stash Jungle Breath brings the expected Kush traits of gas and skunk notes with fruity and citrus flavours.

Product Short Description: An indica dominant hybrid cross between Khalifa Kush x The Menthol with dense, light dark green buds, caked with trichomes, and bright hairs.
Product Long Description: Ghost Drops Khalifa Mints is an indica dominant hybrid cross between Khalifa Kush and The Menthol. Its hunted by Rockstar Canadian cultivators Headwater Cannabis and grown locally in a micro craft facility. Khalifa Mints is noticeable upon appearance due to its dense, light dark green buds, caked with trichomes, and highlighted by bright hairs. Its nose is heavy, fruity at first scent flowed by notes of pungent peppermint and its flavour is dominated by menthol with hints of citrus followed by a gassy aftertaste. Ghost Drops is thrilled to continue our relationship with Headwater Cannabis, holding true to our promise; “No Ghost left behind.”

Product Short Description: Sweet, woody aroma with undertones of lemon and spice. Hang dried, hand selected, hand portioned, hand packaged and nitrogen sealed. Indica.
Product Long Description: King Bubba Kush flower should be considered royalty, for this high THC indica strain provides a majestic aroma and flavour profile that holds true to the characteristics of its lineage. These light green buds feature a large calyx, beautiful orange pistils and glowing trichomes to provide traditional Bubba Kush traits, such as the distinctly sweet, woody aroma with undertones of lemon and spice. You don’t need a castle to put your feet up and chill to experience the earthy and sweet flavours of this high THC flower. Hang dried, hand selected, hand portioned and hand packaged and finally sealed in nitrogen to preserve quality, humidity, freshness and terpenes to ensure Mood Ring King Bubba Kush arrives in the customer’s hands just as it was when it was selected by our award-winning cannabis sommelier. All hail the King!

Product Short Description: Grown by Krazy Krystal in Nicola Valley, BC. A cross of Biscotti Sundae and Wedding Cake. Expect a nose of creamy vanilla, ending in notes of fuel.
Product Long Description: Biscotti Cake is a heavy indica bred by Cannarado and grown by Krazy Krystal. This boutique micro is located in the Nicola Valley of BC. This cultivar is a cross of Biscotti Sundae and Wedding Cake and expresses itself with a nose of creamy vanilla, ending with sharp notes of fuel. This flower is stunningly coloured with basil and lilac foliage and bright tangerine pistils. The dense buds burst with flavour which will be sure to entice the most experienced connoisseurs.

Product Short Description: A potent indica-leaning hybrid known for its aroma with crisp concentrated hints of cool mint flavour funkiness and robust notes of sweet vanilla.
Product Long Description: Flint & Embers' Kush Cake (Wedding Cake x Kush Mints) is a highly potent indica-leaning hybrid known for its pleasant aroma. This strain has crisp concentrated hints of cool mint flavour funkiness while harbouring robust sweet vanilla undertones. Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in – Kush Cake is hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and then carefully sorted and packed to capture the best bud. This is a beautiful bud with deep greens and a layer of white trichomes caked into every crevice.

Product Short Description: Highly revered. Highly Potent. Savoury herbs & spicy earth with undertones of citrus & musk.
Product Long Description: You’ll whisper its name in reverential tones after this bud passes your lips - “Kush Cookies.” Potent, terpene rich, with dense & sticky buds. A rare lineage of GMO Cookies X OZ Kush that delivers highly aromatic notes of savoury herbs & spicy earth, with undertones of citrus & base note of musk. Kush Cookies comes in at a heavenly 4.4% terps with a high THC range –delivering potency without sacrificing taste. The top terpenes are caryophyllene, myrcene, limonene, and linalool. Righteously grown in the sun and rain watered; both promote better and more varied terpenes (meaning more flavour and entourage for you), as well as being a much more environmentally sustainable way of growing. Of course, the flower is hand harvested & hang dried to protect those hard-won trichomes, and given a slow, steady cure for a deeper, richer smoking experience.  What’s not to revere? Whisper that name again…” Kush Cookies.” HAIL MARY JANE.

Product Short Description: Tweed Kush Mints is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD.
Product Long Description: Tweed Kush Mints is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD. Kush Mints comes from a cross of Animal Mints and Bubba Kush. Its buds are known to be dense and dark green with hits of lime. Some associate minty, earthy and pine flavours with the Tweed Kush Mints strain.

Product Short Description: An indica leaning cultivar with a terpene profile dominant in beta-myrcene, limonene and trans-caryophyllene giving it a distinctive palette.
Product Long Description: Layer Cake is an indica leaning cultivar developed from some of the worlds most sought-after genetics crossing Wedding Cake x GMO x Triangle Kush x Skunk. Grown by craft cultivator Origin Coast, in their purpose built facility on Cape Breton Island in Nova Scotia, it has a terpene profile dominant in beta-myrcene, limonene and trans-caryophyllene. A light vanilla scent adds some sweetness to the strong skunky aromas while the caryophyllene gives it a spicy flavour that turns cheesy, with a hint of diesel as it burns. Layer Cake is grown indoors in small craft batches and is hang dried, hand trimmed and cured for one month ensuring a rich dynamic experience and clean white ash.

Product Short Description: Tweed Lemon Kush is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD.
Product Long Description: Tweed Lemon Kush is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD. Lemon Kush comes from a cross of Master Kush and Lemon Joy. Its buds are known to be dark green with hints of orange hairs. Some associate citrusy, sour and spicy flavours with the Tweed Lemon Kush strain.

Product Short Description: The baron of bliss. The prince of pep. The sultan of swag. Lemon Royale is a potent cultivar that will forever reign supreme over citrusy sativas.
Product Long Description: The baron of bliss. The prince of pep. The sultan of swag. Lemon Royale holds many titles, but this citrusy sativa will forever reign supreme. Bursting with fruity lemon-lime and diesel flavour and aromas, this strain is adorned from head to toe in crystals. All hail the king of zest! Find Lemon Royale packed bright orange jar with an air-tight freshness seal and humidity pack included. Palmetto is grown by cannabis lovers for cannabis lovers, found somewhere deep in the mystic shadows of the majestic Rocky Mountains of Alberta.

Product Short Description: Lemon Sour Diesel is a sativa strain that has a sour taste of lemon with a diesel aftertaste. It tastes like sour lemons with a hint of spice.
Product Long Description: Lemon Sour Diesel is a sativa strain that has a sour taste of lemon with a diesel aftertaste. It tastes like sour lemons with a hint of spice. Lemon Sour Diesel is a sativa dominant hybrid (80% sativa/20% indica) strain that was created by breeders at Green Lantern Seeds. This dank bud is a cross between California Sour and Lost Coast OG. Lemon Sour Diesel has an intensely sour taste of lemon with a diesel aftertaste upon exhale and an aroma of sour lemon diesel with a hint of spice. This bud has dense spade-shaped neon green buds with rich amber and gold undertones, a massive covering of furry fiery orange hairs and dark olive green leaves.

Product Short Description: Liberty Haze is a citrusy, sweet sativa dominant strain made from a beautiful cross between G13 and Chewdawg that produces vibrant lime green buds.
Product Long Description: Liberty Haze is the citrusy, sweet sativa dominant strain you have been looking for! A beautiful cross between G13 and Chewdawg that produces vibrant lime green buds covered with a frosty coating of crystals and beautiful little delicate red hairs. Expect a pungent bouquet of skunky lime and fresh citrus. The product is hand harvested, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packed. This is sativa craft cannabis at its finest.

Product Short Description: This sweet berry gas flavour with a hint of diesel was created by crossing London Pound Cake #75 with Kush Mints #11 by Seed Junky Genetics.
Product Long Description: Seed Junky Genetics has taken the mysterious London Pound Cake and crossed it with something quite special. London Pound Cake was crossed using Sunset Sherbet and an unknown indica cultivar which lends heavy grape, berries and gas aromas. Add Kush Mints #11 to the mix and experience the unique flavour profile as your taste buds are alerted to sweet, floral, berry and diesel notes. Taking lineage from two of the biggest breeders in the industry, Cookies and Seed Junky Genetics, this indica dominant hybrid offers a deep, potent experience.

Product Short Description: MAC & Cheese is a rare sativa-leaning hybrid of the popular MAC (Miracle Alien Cookies) crossed with Alien Cheese.
Product Long Description: MAC & Cheese by Truro Cannabis is a rare sativa-leaning hybrid of the popular MAC (Miracle Alien Cookies) crossed with Alien Cheese. Flavour profile is hints of cheese and citrus, but not an overpowering cheese profile. All Truro Cannabis dried flower is hang-dried, hand-trimmed, slow-cured and hand-packed for the ultimate craft cannabis experience. MAC & Cheese is packaged in recyclable nitrogen-filled aluminum cans, which use a purge of liquid nitrogen and hermetic seal to preserve the dried flower quality and terpene profile.

Product Short Description: A citrus-forward hybrid with balanced notes of earth and gas.?
Product Long Description: This smooth hybrid is a cross between the iconic strains Alien Cookies F2 and Miracle 15. Bulk bags with round buds covered in frosty trichomes and sugar leaves, MAC 1 is a balanced flower with citrusy, earthy and lightly gassy notes. Each bag is filled with quality bud, greenhouse grown in BC’s Fraser Valley.

Product Short Description: MAC 1 Cap’s Cut is a potent indica/sativa hybrid.
Product Long Description: MAC 1 Cap’s Cut is a potent indica/sativa hybrid. This potent strain originated from clones that came directly from the breeder, Capulator. It can be traced back to the original plant, which is a cross of Miracle 15 -- a Colombian X Starfighter cross named for the fact that only 15 seeds from this particular cross existed, they accidentally went through the washing machine, and only one seed germinated -- and Alien Cookies. The strain was supposed to be unavailable commercially, as it was originally given as a gift to only those growers deemed worthy of this special strain, as personally selected by Capulator. It’s a visually beautiful, high-THC strain with dark purple buds with orange pistils, caked in trichomes. It has dank, creamy, gassy and citrus aromas, and an orange-like flavour with floral, earthy undertones.

Product Short Description: Bursting with a fruity sweet aroma, Megaton Melon #4 is a bright sativa that we can only describe as a fruitsplosion of flavour!
Product Long Description: Bursting with a fruity sweet aroma, Megaton Melon #4 is a bright sativa that we can only describe as a fruitsplosion of flavour! Its chunky gooey buds will leave your fingers sticky like you just finished digging into a bowl of sweet, sliced watermelon. Our small batch buds are hang-dried and hand-trimmed to preserve trichomes and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to keep your bud fresher, longer.

Product Short Description: Mint Chip Gelato by Redecan is an indica sativa hybrid (50:50) carefully developed by crossing Green Cookies and Sinmint Cookies strains.
Product Long Description: Mint Chip Gelato is a perfect indica sativa hybrid (50:50) developed by crossing Green Cookies and Sinmint Cookies strains. The combined result is a very well-balanced genetic offspring with medium mini-pine-sized buds that are a firm dark olive green with furry orange hairs blanketed in a flurry of white trichomes. With modest THC levels, this hybrid carries a terpene profile that includes carene, camphene and caryophyllene which combine to deliver a rich earthy minted pine aroma mixed with sweeter floral notes and a spicy finish. Mint Chip Gelato by Redecan is improved through careful care and attention given through each stage of growth and harvested at its peak, expertly cured and hand trimmed  to ensure the highest level of quality.

Product Short Description: A rotating strain SKU from the incomparable growers at LOT420. Off Menu contains a host of classic genetics that were beloved in the legacy market.
Product Long Description: Lot420 and United Greeneries have teamed up again to bring you, Off Menu. This rotating strain product allows consumers to discover exclusive new strains in legacy market fashion. Each strain is associated with a specific lot number. Retailers and budtenders will be able to identify each specific lot number and inform the consumer on how to find the product description online. You will be able to obtain your strain specific product description through Lot420’s website and social media channels. Upcoming strains include: Apples & Bananas, Area41, Baklava and many other tantalizing legacy strains.

Product Short Description: Doja OG Deluxe is a hybrid strain bred with a lineage that involves backcrossing to create a plant heavy with OG characteristics.
Product Long Description: Doja OG Deluxe, also written as OGDlux, is a high THC hybrid strain bred from a unique lineage of OGKB x Triangle Kush crossed with Triangle Kush crossed with Josh D OG. This cultivar's terpene profile is highlighted by dominant amounts of terpinolene and caryophyllene. This strain emits a fruity, gassy and spicy aroma profile with heavy OG characteristics.

Product Short Description: Loud with a fruity, sweet, coffee profile, LOXL flower is indoor grown, hang dried, slow cured and hand trimmed to maintain its natural structure.
Product Long Description: LOXL OG Grape is loud and punchy right out of the bag! OG Grape has a complex layered flavour profile of fruity, sweet, coffee notes. LOXL selects only top tier flower grow in hydroponic indoor batches. Each harvest is hang dried, slow cured, and hand trimmed to maintain its beautiful structure and naturally loud presence.

Product Short Description: Palmetto OG Kush is an indica fan favourite and is considered the top dog grand daddy father figure to all other kushes out there.
Product Long Description: What’s there left to say about OG Kush? That it’s a fan favourite? That the hype is real? How about the fact that this is the kush all other kushes aspire to be? You already know the buds are dense and the flavour is bold, sweet and diesel-like. Palmetto jars always include a humidity pack. Palmetto is grown in the heartland of Alberta.

Product Short Description: Also known as OKC, Ethos Genetics bred Orange Kush Cake from the lineage ((Wedding Cake x Jilly Bean) x Triangle Kush) x Mandarin Cookies R2.

Product Long Description: This San Francisco strain is a hefty hybrid of OG Kush and Durban Poison, easily recognizable by its bold purple tone, sparkling frost and electric orange hairs. These pre-rolls offer a heady flavour of pepper with a sprinkle of nutty mint, sure to please the palate.

Product Short Description: Indica-dominant EastCann Dirty Banana is produced from premium whole flower of the popular EastCann Dirty Banana.
Product Long Description: Dirty Banana smells a bit like kiwi, which gives banana-adjacent in taste. That extra fruitiness is evidence of a luscious stash of terpenes and flavonoids. The aroma is really rather intoxicating — pleasantly tart and honey sweet. Remarkably, that banana flavour follows through into the smoke, amidst the citrusy terpenes and something reminiscent of chocolate. The bud is densely packed and each petal is crystal-covered, giving them a notably pale appearance, though they are rather lightly hued by themselves.

Product Short Description: Ethos Genetics' Ethos Glue is Original Glue crossed with Black Fire F1.
Product Long Description: Ethos Genetics' Ethos Glue is Original Glue crossed with Black Fire F1. The result is a plant with dense stacked flowers, presenting with a collage of light green colours. Expect a similar structure and aromas as Original Glue with pungent earthy, skunky, and sour notes.

Product Short Description: A selection of our top indoor grown flowers, strain selection available for a limited time.
Product Long Description: A selection of our top indoor grown flowers, strain selection available for a limited time.

Product Short Description: 10th planet is an indoor grown, calyx-heavy strain with chunky, dense flowers.
Product Long Description: 11th Planet is a calyx-heavy strain with chunky and dense flowers that have deep purple and light green calyx’s that explode with tall trichomes. Expect an aromatic fruit, gasoline, and grape fragrance that matches the visual appearance of this beautiful flower.

Product Short Description: Pink Petrol combines the legendary flavour of Pink Kush with the best that craft flower has to offer: small batches, hang dried slowly for maximum flavour.
Product Long Description: Pink Petrol combines the well-known flavour of BC Pink Kush with strong gas, sugar and floral undertones. We chose Pink Petrol after a long search to find the flavour and aroma that would please any legacy consumer while maintaining high THC.  We're excited to be adding Pink Petrol to our EVERYDAY GAS lineup of fresh, flavourful and fairly priced indica flower offerings.

Product Short Description: dosi-GMOsi #13 is shorter and bushier with a more garlicky aroma than its sister phenotype, dosi-GMOsi #6.
Product Long Description: dosi-GMOsi #13 brings some intense funk. The overall structure is shorter and bushier with chunky buds, leaning toward a more garlicky aroma than its sister phenotype, dosi-GMOsi #6. This indica-dominant cultivar is hand-trimmed with precision and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to help preserve trichomes and keep your buds fresher longer.

Product Long Description: dosi-GMOsi #13 brings some intense funk. The overall structure is shorter and bushier with chunky buds, leaning toward a more garlicky aroma than its sister phenotype, dosi-GMOsi #6. This indica-dominant cultivar is hand-trimmed with precision and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to help preserve trichomes and keep your buds fresher longer.
