Product Long Description: dosi-GMOsi #13 brings some intense funk. The overall structure is shorter and bushier with chunky buds, leaning toward a more garlicky aroma than its sister phenotype, dosi-GMOsi #6. This indica-dominant cultivar is hand-trimmed with precision and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to help preserve trichomes and keep your buds fresher longer.

Product Short Description: Bred by Capulator as a special release, Frozen Lemons is a unique sativa-dominant bud with high potency and a sweet lemon citrus aroma.
Product Long Description: Bred by Capulator, these seeds were only made available as a special release at the 2019 Emerald Cup. Edison’s Frozen Lemons is a special pheno run of Cap’s Frozen Lemons, a unique cross between Fruity Pebbles OG x Cap's Frozen Lemons. This sativa-dominant strain smells and tastes like sweet lemon. Its aroma has a bright lemon citrus smell, followed by light and subtle sweetness. The chunky spade-shaped buds are light green with a firm sponginess, rich amber pistils and frosty patches of shiny trichomes throughout. Be one of the few to try this rare strain bred by one of the best in the game.

Product Short Description: Zombie Kush is an indica-dominant hybrid strain with a sweet and fruity berry pine flavour and a delicate earthy lavender pine aroma to match.
Product Long Description: Zombie Kush is an 80% indica-dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Sideral x Bubba Kush strains. It has a multi-dimensional flavour profile with hints of berry and pine, and an earthy lavender aroma to match. This offering of indoor-grown craft cannabis is free of pesticides, non-irradiated, hand harvested and trimmed after a long cure time.

Product Short Description: Ghost OG is an indica-dominant hybrid with a colourful appearance, a pleasant and strong aroma with a hint of lemon and citrus flavours.
Product Long Description: This super-rare strain, is an indica-dominant hybrid (70% indica/30% sativa) with a colourful appearance that has a leafy exterior and contains numerous colours, including tones of green, yellow and purple. It has a pleasant and strong aroma with a hint of lemon and citrus flavours. This offering of indoor-grown craft cannabis is free of pesticides, non-irradiated, hand harvested and trimmed after a long cure time.

Product Short Description: Pura Vida Legacy Gorilla Cookies offers pungent earthy aromas mixed with sugary sweet flavour profiles.
Product Long Description: Pura Vida Legacy Gorilla Cookies offers pungent earthy aromas mixed with sugary sweet flavour profiles.

Product Short Description: Rosetta Stone’s vivid crystal trichomes drip with resin, bringing sweet flavours and slight sour citrus and spice overtones.
Product Long Description:
Rosetta Stone, a sativa-dominant child strain of Jack Herer, celebrates light, sweet, citrus flavours with a slightly sour citrus exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a peppery herbal overtone that sweetens as it burns, unlocking a slew of rich trichomes. As beautiful as their name suggests, Rosetta Stone buds are fluffy, spade-shaped, and bright neon green with thin light orange hairs coated in vivid crystal trichomes and dripping with resin.
Our dried flower offerings are hand-trimmed and protected within our optimally sized packaging which is not only reusable and recognized for its ability to retain terpenes, but also fully recyclable and engineered to degrade at an accelerated rate.

Product Short Description: Temple Kush has herbal aromas that complement mixed flavours of earth, liquorice and a touch of diesel.
Product Long Description:
Temple Kush, a popular child of Nepalese Hashplant and Hindu Kush, is a rare indica hybrid strain featuring elongated green and lavender buds with dark orange pistils, golden crystal trichomes, and a coating of sweet sticky resin. Its herbal aromas complement mixed flavours of earth, liquorice and a touch of diesel. 

Our dried flower offerings are hand-trimmed and protected within our optimally sized packaging which is not only reusable and recognized for its ability to retain terpenes, but also fully recyclable and engineered to degrade at an accelerated rate.

Tommy's Grape Galena is a high THC and CBG strain grown in the west, known for its silvery dense buds that resemble moon rocks. Hang-dried and hand-trimmed, this glistening indica brings with it notes of cherry, sour berries and grape candy, derived from myrcene, caryophyllene, humulene and limonene. What's more, our reusable and recyclable container will keep each dose fresh from the first pinch to the last, maintaining terpenes and locking in moisture. Enjoy this cross between OGKB, Lost Sailor and Platinum Kush.

Product Short Description: Dense and bright green flower with protruding bright orange hairs that show purple colours with a piney, lemon aroma reminiscent of diesel and skunk.
Product Long Description: Dense and bright green flower with protruding bright orange hairs that show purple colours with a piney, lemon aroma reminiscent of diesel and skunk.

Product Short Description: Dense and bright green flower with protruding bright orange hairs that show purple colours with a piney, lemon aroma reminiscent of diesel and skunk.
Product Long Description: Dense and bright green flower with protruding bright orange hairs that show purple colours with a piney, lemon aroma reminiscent of diesel and skunk.

Product Short Description: KWK fluffy, purple-hued buds release a musky diesel aroma reminiscent of the long line of Kush strains.
Product Long Description: KWK fluffy, purple-hued buds release a musky diesel aroma reminiscent of the long line of Kush strains.

Introducing JMO, the first official release from Gas Station. This indica-dominant hybrid is a cross of Jellybreath (Mendo Breath x Do-Si-Do) mixed with the uber-popular GMO (Garlic Cookies x ChemDawg) strain, and is a staple in smokers stash-boxes across the U.S. Cured to craft standards, in small batches, for highest terpenes this strain features the lip-smacking and throat-coating of jelly kush with a slight kick of spice flavours at the end. This strain was grown in craft rooms less than 1000 square feet then hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged for premium quality. This JMO will surely have you refuelling for more!

Product Short Description: 7ACRES’ newest core cultivar Lemon Zktlz is a high terpene hybrid with pungent aromas of bright citrus, sweet candy, fruit, and hints of cheese.
Product Long Description: 7ACRES’ newest core cultivar Lemon Zktlz is a high terpene hybrid with beautiful bag appeal, featuring light green colouration with pink pistils and dense structure. Pungent and complex aromas of bright citrus, sweet candy, fruity notes and hints of cheese that transfer to robust flavour for a super smooth smoking experience. Cross of Las Vegas Lemon Skunk x Zktlz. Indoor grown in Ontario, whole plant hang dry and hand polished.

Product Short Description: Have twice as much fun with Loop / Pool's Duo Gorilla Breath. This hybrid cross has strong notes of pine, fuel, chocolate and diesel.
Product Long Description: Have twice as much fun with Loop / Pool's Duo Gorilla Breath. This indoor grown hybrid cross between Original Glue and Kush Breath is high in resin with a strong OG aroma. You will sense notes of pine, fuel, chocolate and diesel.  Now available in 3.5g whole flower.

Product Short Description: Garlic Toast is an intense skunky indica dominant strain with aromas of herb and spice, deep amber undertones and frosty crystal trichomes.
Product Long Description: Garlic Toast is an intense skunky indica dominant strain with deep amber undertones and frosty crystal trichomes. This complex pungent strain is bred by combining GMO, TK Skunk, and Wedding Cake and has undertones of herb and spice.

Product Short Description: Tally Man, by Oni Seed Co., is a cross between Banana Dosi-do and Oni's flagship, Papaya. This cultivar drops the intense aromas of banana and coconut.
Product Long Description: When your genetics are this hyped, you have a lot to live up to. Tally Man, by Oni Seed Co., is a cross between Banana Dosi-do and Oni's flagship, Papaya. And trust us, it meets the hype. Our cut of this cultivar drops the intense aromas of banana and coconut, then hits you with a hint of suntan lotion. The light green buds with lilac-coloured accents offers great bag appeal. There's no doubt, Tally Man will leave you wanting more.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and fruity, sweet, tropical, woody and earthy flavours.
Product Long Description: West Coast Banana Skunk from -ness is an indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential. Its dominant terpenes include limonene, caryophyllene and myrcene, imparting banana-forward flavour that’s fruity, sweet, tropical, woody and earthy. With its lime green buds, frosty trichomes, orange pistils, and legendary lineage, West Coast Banana Skunk is ready to slide into your life. Explore Your -ness™.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and tropical fruit flavour and aroma.
Product Long Description: Golden Papaya from BZAM is an indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and unmistakable tropical fruit flavour and aroma from dominant terpenes myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. Its fluffy light green buds are covered in dense trichome crystals and golden pistils to match its tropical golden flavour. We wish you could experience the wall of papaya scent that greets you in the grow room, but alas, a package of this flower in your hands is the next best thing. Wham. Zing. Whoosh. Everything just got better™.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: A hybrid strain with very strong THC potency potential and sweet and nutty peanut butter flavour.
Product Long Description: Peanut Butter Mochi from Snackbar is a hybrid strain with very strong THC potency potential and sweet and nutty peanut butter flavour with notes of cream and spice from terpinolene, caryophyllene and farnesene. Its big, grape-shaped, minty green buds are covered in orange pistils and crystal trichome frosting. Whether you like it sweet or savoury, Peanut Butter Mochi is an all-star for your treat jar.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid with a sweet diesel aroma and citrus and earthy flavours.
Product Long Description: B.C. Valley Gas from Dunn Cannabis is an indica-dominant strain with strong THC potential and a sweet diesel aroma that evokes citrus and earthy flavours. Grown in a micro production facility in Abbotsford, the buds are hang dried for 21 days in a cold room to preserve their terpenes before hand trimming. Proudly handcrafted in the birthplace of B.C. bud, this strain is for those who truly appreciate the care and attention that goes into a micro-grow.

Supplier Name: BZAM MANAGEMENT INC. D.B.A. BZAM CANNABIS
Product Short Description: An indica-dominant hybrid strain with very strong THC potency potential and berry fruit flavour to match its pink-hued buds.
Product Long Description: Rozay from Dunn Cannabis is an indica-dominant hybrid with very strong THC potency potential and notable sweet berry flavour. It’s a frosty and colourful strain with lots of reds and pinks to match its fruit-forward flavour profile. The product of a limited release genetic with only 50 mother stock seeds, Rozay is a rare offering that must be experienced, if only just to see the strikingly rose-coloured buds for yourself.

Product Short Description: A cross of Sunshine State’s Triangle Kush and the dank, bubble hash-esque ‘88 G13 Hashplant. A sugary, earthy flavour with a gentle, spicy aroma.
Product Long Description: Go Steady Sunshine Bubble Kush is a balanced hybrid created by crossing the Sunshine State’s Triangle Kush with the dank, bubble hash-esque ‘88 G13 Hashplant. The strain has a sugary, earthy flavour with a gentle, spicy aroma of cloves and pine, followed by a citrusy perfume. The bud is compact and quite dense, with deep purple, almost black sugar leaves. It’s known for producing extremely potent flowers with potent THC levels. FIGR dried flower products are hand selected to ensure dense, high-quality buds are in every package.

Product Short Description: Get your hands sticky with sweet, supreme powerhouse strain Sherbert Glue.
Product Long Description: Sherbert Glue is an indica-dominant strain, bred from tSherbert Dab and GG #4. The chunky, trichome laden, resin-covered buds have a pungent, earthy aroma with a sweet, citrusy flavour profile. Get your hands sticky with this supreme powerhouse strain.

Product Short Description: OS.Haze is a single strain offering that features a rotating selection of quality flower from well-known haze strains.
Product Long Description: OS.Haze is a single strain offering that focuses on the characteristics of the haze family. Haze strains are known for tall, thin colas with dense trichomes that deliver dominant sweet and citrus aromas. This innovative product from Original Stash features a rotating selection of quality flower from well-known haze strains. We take special care during the plant’s growth to make sure only high-grade buds end up in each bag.

Product Short Description: OS.Kush is a single strain offering that features a rotating selection of quality flower from well-known Kush strains.
Product Long Description: OS.Kush is a single-strain offering that features a rotating selection of quality flower from well-known Kush strains. All Original Stash flower is grown with care to make sure only high-grade buds end up in each bag.

Product Short Description: We create something different for all the gas lovers! Working through our library of genetics, we release the best and gassiest lots as limited drops.
Product Long Description: We at Highland Grow decided to create something different for all the gas lovers out there! As we were working through our library of genetics, we decided to release the best and gassiest lots as limited drops. We’ve been working with rare cuts like Pink Octane, El Jefe, Pink Mink, El Muerte, Pre98 Bubba, Cold Snap, Platinum Bubba, Pink Coast, and many more for the sole focus: GAS! Expect that dank, spicy, citrusy scent with the undertones of anise and sweet apple that we all know and love, in every bag. Coupled with frosty, dense potent indica buds.

Product Short Description: Diamond breath is a well-balanced hybrid coated in a thick carpet of trichomes. Glistening like a layer of diamonds on each dense bud.
Product Long Description: Diamond breath is a well-balanced hybrid, taking qualities from both parents that evolve slowly through the smoke with a complex aroma and taste. Expect an earthy flavour balanced by an almost spicy note of sour fruit, that is smooth and full bodied. Each bud is a tapestry of greens, with emerald notes balanced by lime greens and even the occasional purple, coated in a thick carpet of trichomes. Glistening like a layer of diamonds on each dense bud.

Product Short Description: Our Caesar Salad blends pungent, citrus and garlicky strains for a tasty and memorable experience worthy of the world’s favourite salad.
Product Long Description: People have been making cannabis salads forever. At Salad Bar, we are stepping the salad up a notch by blending three or more thoughtfully selected cannabis cultivars in one bag. We work with different producers to bring together a unique mix of strains, creating collaboration within the industry, while allowing consumers to discover different complimentary flavours and effects. Our Caesar Salad blends whole-flower, pungent citrus- and garlicky strains for a tasty and memorable experience worthy of the world’s favourite salad. And at our value-driven price point, there’s no reason to ever skip a salad again.

Product Short Description: An indica-dominant flower with a pungent smell and flavour of diesel with sour earthy notes.
Product Long Description: An indica-dominant, OG #18 conveys a pungent smell and flavour of diesel with sour earthy notes. Top 5 terpenes are: beta-caryophyllene, alpha-humulene, beta-pinene, d-limonene, alpha-bisabolol.

Product Short Description: Billy's Pheno features the latest drop that was selected by our Flower Manager, for its unique terpene profile, bag appeal and cannabinoid profile.
Product Long Description:
At Carmel, incredible flower all starts with a pheno hunt, where we work through hundreds of seeds to find our unicorn. Billy's Pheno features the latest drop that was selected by our Flower Manager, for its unique terpene profile, bag appeal and cannabinoid profile. 
Because it’s just the right thing to do, all our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch that features a perfect airtight seal. Non irradiated, obviously.

Product Short Description: This flower is high in terps, providing an earthy aroma of hops and black pepper, with notes of pine and cedar.
Product Long Description: Our BR has been nicknamed Krussian. This flower is faithful to its aromatic lineage of earth, hops and black pepper, with notes of pine and cedar. Once sparked, expect a sweet tropical flavour with a hint of lychee on the finish.

Product Short Description: Electric Punch is a strain that definitely lives up to its name! Before grind, the aroma is pleasantly sweet with earthy and skunky undertones.
Product Long Description: Electric Punch is a strain that definitely lives up to its name! This exotic cultivar has a rich deep purple base color laced throughout with beautiful bright orange pistils, all covered by a thick blanket of white, frosty trichomes. The medium sized buds are dense with an excellent tight trim that makes sure you don't get any extra leaf in your buds. Before grind, the aroma is pleasantly sweet with earthy and skunky undertones that are only enhanced after being ground.

Product Short Description: Crazy Rntz is an exclusive indica-dominant strain of the highly sought after Rntz family combining the most flavourful, exotic strains available.
Product Long Description: Crazy Rntz is an exclusive indica-dominant strain of the Rntz family originated in Los Angeles combining the most flavourful and exotic strains available. Expect a flavourful, sugary explosion when you try Rntz. Its dense grape-shaped olive green buds are supplemented with thin orange hairs, dark purple undertones, and a coating of frosty tiny white, purple-tinted crystal trichomes. Smells and tastes of sour grape candy abounds with a creamy mild fuel undertone. This profile is an expertly balanced representation of both ends of the spectrum. Aromas of hops, vanilla icing and nostalgic fruity flavours over a dank herbal foundation based on the terpenes caryophyllene, linalool, limonene. Offering a little mystery with its lineage Crazy Rntz is a cross of Rntz x Bonkers x Unknown Hybrid.

Product Name: Stinky Greens Organic Platinum Jelly Indica
Product Short Description: Stinky Greens Platinum Jelly indica is a cross between Jelly Breath and Platinum strains. It has a high THC range and terpenes > 1%.
Product Long Description: In the heart of Simcoe County, Ontario you’ll find a 3.5-acre property with an indoor cultivation facility. That’s where Stinky Greens Organic grows their high-quality cannabis. Their dedication & care for each plant is what makes their cannabis stand out. Platinum Jelly is grown in coco soil to allow sufficient air flow and water circulation. Grown using the sea of green method, Platinum Jelly is hand-watered then hang dried and cold-cured for 14 days. The buds are dry trimmed, then finished by hand to keep the integrity and the trichomes intact. Stinky Greens Platinum Jelly Indica is a cross between Jelly Breath and Platinum strains. Its olive green buds sport thick, orange hairs and a coating of tiny frosty white crystal trichomes. Platinum Jelly has a creamy, sugary, and fruity taste with hints of spice and flowers upon exhaling. The aroma is earthy and herbal with notes of grapes. Stinky Greens Platinum Jelly has a high THC range and terpenes >1%.

Product Name: Kolab Project x Safari Flower Co. Dark Shadow Haze
Kolab Project x Lotus Cannabis Co. Tranquil Elephantizer
Product Short Description: We have once again partnered with Lotus Cannabis Co. to launch Tranquil Elephantizer, a Bodhi Seeds cross between 88 G-13 Hashplant and Snow Lotus.
Product Long Description: In an effort to build community, profile our partners, and offer transparency to consumers, Kolab Project launched the Growers Series. We are committed to showcasing the quality, the consistency, and the difference it makes when cannabis is grown in small batches, hand-tended, and hand-picked by dedicated growers. As part of this Growers Series release, we have once again partnered with Lotus Cannabis Co. to launch Tranquil Elephantizer, a Bodhi Seeds cross between 88 G-13 Hashplant and Snow Lotus. This indica has high THC potencies and a pungent earthy herb aroma that has a hint of sweetness. With terp content of up to 2.7%, top terpenes are limonene, caryophyllene, myrcene, farnesene and humulene.

Product Name: Kolab Project x Safari Flower Co. Sticky Monkey
Product Short Description: We have once again partnered with Safari Flower Co. to bring you Sticky Monkey. This indica from Seedstockers genetics comes from original GG#4.
Product Long Description: In an effort to build community, profile our partners, and offer transparency to consumers, Kolab Project launched the Growers Series. We are committed to showcasing the quality, the consistency, and the difference it makes when cannabis is grown in small batches, hand-tended, and hand-picked by dedicated growers. As part of this Growers Series release, we have once again partnered with Safari Flower Co. to bring you Sticky Monkey. This indica from Seedstockers genetics comes from original GG#4 genetics and it has a unique blend of diesel and earthy aromas with notes of myrcene, caryophyllene, limonene, humulene and the not often seen fenchol.

Product Short Description: The indica-dominant Ethos Glue is a perfect combo of flavour and appearance. The plant produces massive light green flowers with purple calyxes.
Product Long Description: The indica-dominant Ethos Glue is a perfect combo of flavour and appearance. The plant produces massive light green flowers with purple calyxes. There are spicy, earthy flavours with a noticeable sour finish – a pure refined delight.

Product Short Description: Chocolate Marshmallows is an exotic, limited edition 50/50 hybrid of the legendary highly potent Gorilla Glue #4 crossed with Mint Chocolate Chip.
Product Long Description: Chocolate Marshmallows is an exotic, limited edition 50/50 hybrid of the legendary highly potent Gorilla Glue #4 crossed with Mint Chocolate Chip. Its large dense brownish green buds look like Christmas trees covered in snow crystals highlighting dark evergreen shaded sugar leaves that are curved like crab claws with small dots of sapphire. Super sweet flavour of cocoa and toasted marshmallows with a earthy tinged finish. Chocolate Marshmallow's terpene profile is comprised of limonene (found in citrus fruit peels, such as lemon, orange, and lime), caryophyllene (often in black pepper and cinnamon), and camphene (reminiscent of needles and damp earth).

Product Short Description: Peanut Butter Breath crosses Mendobreath and Do-Si-Dos by renowned breeder ThugPug to create a violet flower coated in trichomes.
Product Long Description: Peanut Butter Breath from Jonny Chronic is an indica-dominant strain that produces violet buds with orange pistils. Containing caryophyllene, linalool, fenchol, and humulene terpenes, this strain has an aroma of kush and sugar. Peanut Butter Breath’s lineage consists of Do-Si-Dos and Mendobreath with every bud hang-dried and cured before it is hand-packaged by our team in Thorndale, ON.

Product Short Description: An indica-dominant strain created by combining Alien Cookies #1 with a backcross of Stardawg crossed with Jelly Breath. Hang dried and hand trimmed.
Product Long Description: Bred by In-House Genetics, Jellien is an indica-dominant strain created by combining Alien Cookies #1 with a backcross of Stardawg, which was then crossed with Jelly Breath. At Joi we hang dry, hand trim and cure in stainless steel containers for at least 14 days to ensure a quality finish. Glass jars are filled by hand and include humidity packs inside to maintain optimal freshness. Enjoi!

Product Short Description: Proudly cultivated by BC Legacy OGs at Smoker Farms! Master Kush Ultra is a cross between G-13 and OG Kush, and is a legacy strain dating back 15 years.
Product Long Description: Proudly cultivated by BC Legacy OGs at Smoker Farms! Master Kush Ultra is a cross between G-13 and OG Kush, and is a legacy strain dating back 15 years. Its tightly packed buds are dark green in colour and the nose is woody and peppery with hints of orange or citrus. This indica strain is grown hydroponically with flood tables and rockwool cubes and each plant is fed by Dosatron nutrient delivery system. It's flowers are meticulously trimmed and hung to dry before being hand-finished and packed in nitrogen for optimal freshness. Expect a one-of-a-kind taste and a smoke that is absolutely loaded with THC.

Product Short Description: Hawaiian Pineapple is a Dole Whip x Cookies and Cream sativa cross. This sativa is known for its tropical aromas and creamy taste of pineapple.
Product Long Description: Hawaiian Pineapple is a Dole Whip x Cookies and Cream sativa cross. This sativa is known for its tropical aromas and creamy taste of pineapple. Hawaiian Pineapple brings a 1.4% CBG score in addition to its high potency. Expect buds in sativa structure, with pink hues and coated in trichomes.

Product Short Description: This sativa-dominant strain pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A Cookies strain x Mandarin Sunset cross.
Product Long Description: Life's a little sweeter in the back forty and you won't want to wait for dessert to give our Mandarin Cookies a try! This sativa-dominant strain pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A cross of the classic Cookies strain and Mandarin Sunset, with some major limonene.

Product Short Description: This sativa-dominant strain pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A Cookies strain x Mandarin Sunset cross.
Product Long Description: Life's a little sweeter in the back forty and you won't want to wait for dessert to give our Mandarin Cookies a try! This sativa-dominant strain pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A cross of the classic Cookies strain and Mandarin Sunset, with some major limonene.

Product Short Description: A cross between Pineapple Haze and Nuken, this hybrid is a fave for its fluffy, round buds and exotic terp profile.
Product Long Description: A cross between Pineapple Haze and Nuken, this hybrid is a fave for its fluffy, round buds and exotic terp profile. A sweet fruity aroma with earthy undertones thanks to its exotic terp profile high in ocimene,  farnesene, and caryophyllene.

Product Short Description: Heat Wave is a sativa cross of Grape Ape x Nevilles Wreck with a grape and berry flavour blast complete with deep purple buds and orange pistils.
Product Long Description: Start the summer off right with Heat Wave! Cruuzy’s newest strain, Heat Wave, is a cross of Grape Ape x Nevilles Wreck with a grape and berry flavour blast that hits just like a cannonball into the pool. Its deep purple buds are sun-kissed by bright orange pistils, bringing you an uplifting ray of light. But don’t wait too long—the sun will set on this Limited-Edition sativa. Ride the Heat Wave while ya can!

Product Short Description: High CBD flower
Product Long Description: High CBD flower with myrcene, pinene and farnesene terpenes.

Product Short Description: Haven St. No 417 Indigo Daze greets you with pungent aromas of sweet citrus accompanied by herbal notes, and black pepper.
Product Long Description: Haven St. No 417 Indigo Daze greets you with pungent lemon, accompanied by sweet and earthy aromas. Black pepper notes may also linger through the nose. The Indica dominant strain has dense green buds covered in crystal trichomes. High levels of the terpene Myrcene are present, giving the flower its sweet yet earthy aroma, as well as the terpene Limonene, for its citrus aromas.

Product Short Description: Haven St. No 417 Indigo Daze greets you with pungent aromas of sweet citrus accompanied by herbal notes, and black pepper.
Product Long Description: Haven St. No 417 Indigo Daze greets you with pungent lemon, accompanied by sweet and earthy aromas. Black pepper notes may also linger through the nose. The Indica dominant strain has dense green buds covered in crystal trichomes. High levels of the terpene Myrcene are present, giving the flower its sweet yet earthy aroma, as well as the terpene Limonene, for its citrus aromas.

Product Short Description: OS.RESERVE is a very strong THC potency indica flower blend.

Gabriola, like all Broken Coast strains, is grown indoors in small batches in strain specific rooms then slow cured and hand trimmed.

Grown in state of the art hybridized, greenhouses, our flowers and tops are dried naturally to preserve the integrity of our plants and hand finished to exact standards.

Our product is grown locally in Strathroy, Ontario just West of the city of London. It has a sour aroma, but features a light, bitter taste with earthy, woodsy notes of sweetness. This strain has desirable colours of green, orange and purple bud, and medium THC potency. It's available in various sizes of dried flower and pre-rolls.

The buds are hand-trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil, using organic methods, and the strain has a very potent floral aroma, with subtle notes of grape and melon created by a terpene profile that includes terpinolene (also found in apples, cumin, lilac, tea tree oil and conifers), caryophyllene (found in black pepper, cloves and balsam) and guaiol (also in cypress pine). THC Sativa has very strong THC potency potential and comes in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g of dried flower.

These premium buds are dominated by a covering of deep amber hairs but also showcase a variety of dark greens and yellows, and specks of brown. The buds are hand-trimmed from plants grown naturally in soil, using organic methods, and the strain has a very spicy and warm aroma, with hints of clove and delicate floral notes created by a terpene profile that includes myrcene (also found in mango, lemon grass, hops and thyme), terpinolene (also in apples, cumin, lilac, tea tree oil and conifers) and ocimene (in mint, parsley, pepper, basil, mango and orchids). CBD Indica comes in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g of dried flower.

Product Short Description: A powerful strain with a, earthy floral scent and a hint of citrus. Well suited for those with an elevated tolerance.
Product Long Description: Enjoy our high THC MAC1, the latest entry in the Citizen Stash organic small batch series. Pesticide free, hand harvested and trimmed, MAC1 is a powerful strain with an earthy floral scent and a hint of citrus. Well suited for those with an elevated tolerance.

Product Short Description: Sage and Sour has a sweet herby sage taste with a hint of sour earth upon exhale and an aroma of sour herby sage.
Product Long Description: Sage 'N Sour is a sativa dominant hybrid (75% sativa/25% indica). A potent cross between the hugely popular Sour Diesel X SAGE. Sage and Sour has a sweet herby sage taste with a hint of sour earth upon exhale and an aroma of sour herby sage. The buds have dense fluffy dark olive green nugs with rich purple leaves and undertones and a spattering of light thin twisty amber hairs. These nugs are dusted with a fine layer of almost translucent trichomes and sweet sticky resin. The buds are pesticide free, hand-harvested and hand-trimmed.

Product Short Description: A very potent indica-hybrid that can reach THC levels over 20%, Nuken's terp profile is sweet with fat and dense buds.
Product Long Description: Some people stay close to home, others prefer to sing among the stars. Nuken doesn't discriminate and thinks being in both places at the same time is just fine. A very potent indica-hybrid that can reach THC levels over 20%, Nuken's terp profile is sweet with buds fat and dense enough to have their own gravitational pull, but if you're floating in a most peculiar way, don't worry—Nuken knows which way is up. Palmetto is weed for people who like weed, grown in the heartland of Alberta so you're always good to go.

Product Long Description: Blue Nova is a sativa-dominant hybrid with a sweet berry aroma and sugary flavour. The bud is dense, sticky and rich with trichomes, with THC levels reaching up to 20%.

Product Long Description: Our version of this sativa-dominant strain uses only FVOPA Organic Certified whole flower. It’s exceptionally aromatic, giving off a strong blueberry aroma with a warm and peppery terpene profile. It’s grown in living soil, hang-dried for 14 days and cold-cured.

Product Long Description:
Mirage Plus by SKOSHA is an indica-dominant strain. This bud is lightly trimmed and handled carefully throughout the harvest process to protect trichomes and terpenes. Expect a strong earthy aroma with hints of spice and citrus within the large dense flower. 
It’s available in various dried flower sizes and pre-rolls. This flower produced by SKOSHA is packaged in a moisture-locking bag and is non-irradiated.

Product Short Description: Pungent aromas of spice, earth, diesel, hops, and creamy coffee.
Product Long Description: Created in Vancouver, D. Bubba is a well-known BC strain. A pungent cross of D. Star and Bubba Kush, Pure Sunfarms’ phenotype is grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley. Each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. The buds are dense and lightly feathered, with dark green leaves almost completely concealed by a heavy icing of trichomes. D. Bubba presents flavours and aromas reminiscent of spicy earth (caryophyllene), gassy hops (humulene), and creamy coffee (bisabolol).

Product Short Description: This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential.
Product Long Description: Pure Sunfarms’ cut of Pink Kush from BC’s Vancouver Island is a coastal relative of the legendary OG Kush. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth, and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

Product Short Description: This unique strain offers a musky, berry aroma with an earthy flavour and a soft and sweet berry finish.
Product Long Description: A potent Indica-Dominant Hybrid that is a cross between Cherry All Kush 47 and Purple Punch. This unique strain offers a musky, berry aroma with an earthy flavour and a soft and sweet berry finish.

Product Short Description: A potent sativa-dominant strain from JC Green, Cherry Bomb produces dense, elegant buds with a sweet earthy aroma.
Product Long Description: Cherry Bomb from JC Green is an exceptionally high THC potency sativa-dominant hybrid strain that produces dense, light green buds with golden-orange pistils and a thick frosting of trichomes. Cherry Bomb delivers a refreshing earthy aroma of sweet flowers derived from a diverse terpene palette of beta-caryophyllene, beta-pinene, d-limonene, nerolidol and linalool. Cherry Bomb’s lineage is complex and features popular parents like OG Kush, Tangerine Dream, Head Hunter and a Hawaiian Sativa Landrace strain. Cherry Bomb plants are grown with the utmost care in small batches before they are hang-dried, slow-cured, and delicately hand-trimmed and then packaged fresh to preserve their true elegance.

Product Long Description: Skip across the sour patch to this irresistible Sour Kush. Welcome to the adults’ table – sour powered flower with some diesel stank. Thank you for coming to our Sour Kush talk.

Product Short Description: A unique Indica-Dominant hybrid of True OG and Kush Mints 11 with an earthy, sweet, and citrus aroma with frosty bright green buds.
Product Long Description: Truro True OG is a unique Indica-Dominant hybrid of True OG and Kush Mints 11. This combination results in an earthy, sweet, and citrus aroma with frosty bright green buds.  True OG was proudly grown on the east coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in their state-of-the-art production facility.  Each bud has been carefully dried, cured, trimmed and packaged to the high-quality specifications of their elite grow team.

Product Short Description: Truro Wedding Mint is an indica dominant hybrid of Wedding Cake and Kush Mints 11. It has a sweet, earthy and peppery flavour profile.
Product Long Description: Truro Wedding Mint is a unique and potent indica-dominant hybrid of Wedding Cake and Kush Mints 11. This combination displays a sweet, earthy and peppery flavour profile with beautiful frosty dark green and purple buds. Truro Wedding Mint is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our state-of-the-art production facilities, where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang-dried, hand-trimmed, slow-cured and hand-packaged for a craft cannabis experience. Truro Cannabis is proud to use recyclable nitrogen-filled packaging for our dried flower. Nitrotin packaging uses a purge of liquid nitrogen and hermetic seal to preserve the dried flower quality and terpene profile.

Product Short Description: This Indica dominant strain provides a sweet apple citrus aroma. Ancestry: God Bud x Apple Jack
Product Long Description:
Royal City’s Royal Goddess was selected for its unique sweet apple aroma, Indica dominant structure and frosty fresh green colours. 

The RC Royal Goddess pairs high THC potency with a pungent (>1.6% terpene) spicy apple citrus sweetness. The RC Royal Goddess is grown indoor to maturity, hang dried and hand processed to ensure the passion of our growers translates into high grade flowers for our customers. Following a multi-week cure they are packaged by hand with a humidity pack to preserve our desired moisture content. 

The RC Royal Goddess comes from a God Bud x Apple Jack cross and expresses fresh apple citrus flavour (Fernaesene-2, Limonene, Linalool) with notes of sweet woody spice (Beta-Myrcene, trans-Caryophyllene)

Royal City Cannabis Co. is an independent employee owned craft producer. Our roots run deep, and our standards are high. We hope you enjoy our flower as much as we enjoy growing it.

Because it’s just the right thing to do, all our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch that features a perfect airtight seal.

Product Short Description: Hang dried and hand-trimmed, this strain boasts medium-dense flowers with a unique aroma of melon and spearmint.
Product Long Description: Hang dried and hand-trimmed, this strain boasts medium-dense flowers with a unique aroma of melon and spearmint. This cultivar presents deep purples, fall oranges, and is coated with crystals.

Product Short Description: California Dreaming contains our highest grown level of THC. This flower is hand groomed from seed-to-sale.
Product Long Description: California Dreaming contains our highest grown level of THC. This flower is hand groomed, from seed-to-sale, and grown under natural sunlight with the assistance of LED lights. This indica-dominant flower is derived from flowers known as Hash Plant and Northern Lights. The earthy combination of alpha pinene and beta pinene brings you the sweet smell of pine trees. While pinene is the most widely encountered terpene in nature, underneath the earthy aroma is a hint of spice brought on by beta caryophyllene. California Dreaming is grown in the heart of Niagara's world renown grape and wine country. At Dykstra Greenhouses we take great care in hand grooming our flower to bring you our best product.

Product Short Description: Our product has significant levels of myrcene which give off spicy, woody, and ripe flavours.
Product Long Description: This indica flower has a consistently high potential of THC potency. This narrow-leafed, full of flower plant has an overabundance of trichomes from its flowery center carrying on throughout its trim and leaves. The amount of snow-like substance found on the flower is reminiscent of a winter wonderland. Our product has significant levels of myrcene which give off spicy, woody, and ripe flavours. Lemon Pepper Spice gives off the aroma of cantaloupe and melon which are accented by the spiciness (ocimene). Overall, the flower has a sweet and herb like flavour (guaiol). Our product as identified in its name, is home grown and hand nurtured at our greenhouse facility, steps from the Niagara Escarpment. The Niagara Region is one of the oldest parts of Canada so it links well with the older of the terpenes guaiol, which can be traced back to the 16th century.

Product Short Description: The famous purple strain is best known for its loud purple leaves, glimmering trichomes, and dense buds.
Product Long Description: The famous purple strain is best known for its loud purple leaves, glimmering trichomes, and dense buds. Master Kush and the now believed extinct Red River Delta were crossed to create Purple Aya. These ultra-rare crosses explain its stunning appearance. In addition, it has a loud blend of papaya, sour, and earthy aromas and is craft grown indoors under full spectrum lighting. Purple Aya is hung dried, hand manicured, and cured for 21 days to ensure consistency in quality.

Product Short Description: DOJA C99 is a THC potent sativa dominant strain with dense buds that deliver a combination of pine and citrus aromas and flavours.
Product Long Description: DOJA C99 is a THC potent sativa dominant strain with dense buds that deliver a combination of pine and citrus aromas and flavours. This flower is hang dried and hand-finished using techniques found in British Columbia's Okanagan Valley. The effects of this product can be felt within seconds to minutes and can last for up to 6 hours. Some effects could last as long as 24 hours.

Product Short Description: Redecan Black Cherry Punch is a potent indica-dominant hybrid, widely known for its bold cherry, yet light skunky flavour profile.
Product Long Description: Redecan Black Cherry Punch is a potent indica dominant hybrid, widely known for its bold cherry, yet light skunky flavour profile. The signature aroma comes from a diverse collection of terpenes such as fruit, wood, spice, and pine. With dark green buds, purple specks, and gold trichomes, Black Cherry Punch comes from the classic strains Black Cherry Pie and Purple Punch. Redecan’s BCP is a smash of delicious flavours – fruity and potent, and expected to be a classic in no time. Just as with any Redecan Evergreen strain,our Black Cherry Punch is carefully harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, hand-trimmed, and inspected.

Product Short Description: A sativa-dominant hybrid strain, named for its beautiful appearance and especially unique flavour profile.
Product Long Description: Redecan Lilac Diesel is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain, named for its beautiful appearance and especially unique flavour profile. Lilac Diesel crosses classic genetics like Silver Lemon Haze, Forbidden Fruit, Citral Glue, and NYC Cherry Pie to create a lightly flavoured, yet complex strain. With a terpene profile featuring notes of berries, pine, spice and citrus fruits, this bud has small, dense nugs with lilac undertones and light-purple crystal trichomes. With THC levels between 19-24%, Redecan’s Lilac Diesel is the perfect choice for hybrid and sativa lovers alike. Just as with any Redecan Evergreen strain, our Lilac Diesel is carefully harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, hand-trimmed, and inspected.

Product Long Description: Garlic Cookies is a cross between Chemdog and GSC, sometimes referred to as GMO cookies. This gorgeous strain has a dank gassy smell along with tones of citrus; a natural genetic fox tailing feature, and fiery orange hairs. This is part of our craft collection and will be a limited edition; grown indoors under ideal conditions for the best results, hung dried, fully hand trimmed to retain its trichome structure, and cured for 28 days.

Spicy, woodsy and a little nutty to taste, it’s an indica-dominant hybrid known to produce tightly-packed, trichome-coated buds that emit a lush forest fragrance with subtle hints of honey and delicate florals.

Product Long Description: Acapulco Gold from Jonny Chronic is a potent sativa strain that produces big beautiful buds that glisten with trichome-covered leaves and copper-orange pistils. Acapulco Golds is a Landrace that originates from Central America and is dominant in terpinene, caryophyllene, myrcene. Acapulco Gold plants are grown with the utmost care in small batches before they are hang-dried, slow-cured, and delicately hand-trimmed and then packaged fresh to preserve their true elegance.

Product Long Description: Mule Fuel is a prominent example of a terpene-rich Sugarbud exclusive cultivar phenotyped from our genetic library. With a strain lineage of GMO x Lurch, this myrcene dominant terpene profile is high in limonene, pinene and caryophyllene. Full dense buds with sticky sugary green and orange hues. Earthy and spicy with notes of meadow flowers and grass, citrus and pronounced fuel aromas. Hang dried and cold barrel cured for 28 days, meticulously hand-finished and packaged with care into glass jars.

Product Short Description: Flint & Embers’ GSC Kush (GSC x Conspiracy Kush) is robust and refined, immersing you in sweet notes of savoury chocolate, coffee, and crushed pepper.
Product Long Description: Flint & Embers’ GSC Kush (GSC x Conspiracy Kush) is a full-flavoured hybrid. Robust and refined, this cultivar immerses you in sweet notes of savoury chocolate and coffee with lingering aromas of crushed pepper. Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in - GSC Kush is hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and then carefully sorted and packed to capture the best bud. These chunky buds are deep olive-green and powdered in a thick layer of silvery-white crystals.

CBD Runtz contains a 2:1 CBD to THC ratio with a high terpene percentage that offers a fruity and sweet aroma and candy-like flavour.

Packed with a humidity device to extend freshness.

Product Long Description: Hot out of the OGEN oven, Freshly Baked #76 finds its roots in the cake family. This bud’s aroma is a complex mix of gas, warm creamy sweetness, and finishes with hints of spice. With dense nugs that are covered in trichomes, this cultivar really takes the cake! Our small batch buds are hand-trimmed to preserve trichomes and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to keep your bud fresher, longer.

Product Short Description: MAC-1 is a hybrid cultivar that is THC potent. Its colourful buds are trichome-rich and are bursting with citrus, diesel and spicy aromas.
Product Long Description: MAC-1 (a cross of Miracle 15 x Alien Cookies) is a legendary hybrid cultivar with a history as robust and colourful as the bud itself. THC potent, Edison’s MAC-1 has super dense and firm buds composed of two-tone light and dark greens, with the occasional punch of light purple colouring. The trichomes covering this bud envelop every nook and cranny of the flower. An abundance of fiery copper pistils permeates throughout completing the rich and colourful mosaic. The aroma has an upfront citrus flavour, which then gives in to a mid-range gassy diesel smell and finishes with a hint of spice to complete this stellar sensory bouquet.

Product Short Description: Have your cake and smoke it too with this smooth yet strong indica.
Product Long Description: Top Leaf LA Kush Cake is proof that sometimes you can have your cake and smoke it too. Simultaneously smooth and surprisingly strong, treat yourself to LA Kush Cake’s sweet vanilla scent and indulge in its earthy mint flavour. This indica-hybrid is very potent, which you might expect when you mix the mighty Kush Mints with tasty Wedding Cake. Both easy smoking and delightfully powerful, this indica really does take the cake. Top Leaf prides itself on carefully crafted cannabis—cultivars with rich, full-bodied flavour and complex terpene profiles—grown to exacting standards and cured for 28 days in the heartland of Alberta.

Product Short Description: THC potent, GMO Cookies have dark green buds that are matched only by their powerful pungent and DANK aroma.
Product Long Description: GMO Cookies (a cross between Chemdog x GSC) is a potent and palate-provoking indica strain. Pungent and powerful, this flower’s potency is matched only by the strength of its aroma. Opening a jar of GMO Cookies is like opening the doors of a shuttered cottage after a long winter – DANK, damp, musty and full of fond memories. The crown-shaped buds are dark green in colour (though the thick layer of trichomes makes the green look a few shades lighter), with dark purple flecks throughout and bright orange pistils protrude from the top contour of each chunky crown.

Product Short Description: A combination of pre-shredded whole-flower with pungent and skunky aromas, THC potent and a humidity pack included.
Product Long Description: We've captured the essence of real dank nugs with skunky, gas and earthy aromas that bring the funk. A combination of sweet skunk, funky cheese and pungent diesel notes. Get down and get dank with Funk Master.

Product Short Description: The tartness of Meyer lemon meets the diesel and pungent notes from the cultivar’s kush undertones.
Product Long Description: Big Buds. Big Terps. Big Bag. Not all flower is worthy of an ounce, except Big Bag. If terpinolene and limonene had a lovechild it’d be Ultra Sour. The tartness of Meyer lemon meets the diesel and pungent notes from the cultivar’s kush undertones. A sativa-leaning sour with outcroppings of orange pistils from deep green, crystal-rich nugs. This bag is a medley of fresh terps that are sweet and fruity on the nose and herbal upon exhale.

Product Short Description: An indica-dominant strain with a dank earthy sweetness. Expect chai spice to start, followed by sage, clove and astringent simple syrup.
Product Long Description: Our Ice Cream Cake maintains that dank earthy sweetness every cake-lover expects from this indica-dominant, cookies-based varietal with a twist. The onset of Germacrene-B in our terps gives this cake a matcha-like quality. Expect chai spice to start, followed by sage, clove and astringent simple syrup once you break open these evergreen, trichome rich buds.

Product Short Description: Papaya is an indica dominant hybrid known for its highly pungent sweet and fruity aromatic notes.
Product Long Description: Papaya is an indica dominant hybrid known for its highly pungent sweet and fruity aromatic notes. A cross of Citral #3 and Ice #2, Papaya produces beautiful light green buds densely coated with milky white trichomes. Originally bred by Nirvana Seeds as their take on Mango, you can expect a complex aromatic profile of fresh papaya, mango, guava and citrus combined with hints of earthy spice.

Product Short Description: This unique indoor-grown strain has crystal covered buds and expansive flavours of spice, berry and earth.
Product Long Description: Where’s My Bike boasts big, dense buds covered in a thick layer of frosty white crystals. A cross between Amnesia Haze and Biker Kush, this indoor grown, sativa-dominant hybrid has over 2.6% terpenes and expansive flavours of spice, berry and earth.

Dark Helmet gives off earthy aromas with undertones of sweet, buttery baked goods. The smoke itself is smooth, full flavoured and reminds us of lemons and spearmint. This is a classic indica dominant hybrid in both effect and appearance.

When consumed, the rich mix of terpenes gives off a subtle earthy and spicy flavour beneath the unmistakably sweet berry overtones.

Product Short Description: Sweet and citrusy, Gelato #33 is an indica hybrid.
Product Long Description: With sweet and citrusy flavours, Gelato #33 (crossing is Sunset Sherbert x Thin Mint GSC) is an indica hybrid. LOT420 is a licensed cannabis producer located in southeast of Montreal in Quebec's Eastern Townships, focused on producing hand-crafted, select batch, high-grade flower. Using proven methods developed in-house, every batch is thoughtfully cultivated, hang-dried, cured and hand-trimmed to give consumers the highest grade product on the market.

Product Short Description: Wedding Poop is an indica dominant hybrid that features a rich and flavourful flavour profile with undertones of vanilla cake.
Product Long Description: This cultivar comes from Unicorn Poop x Wedding Cake. This variety grows big dense buds that are absolutely caked in trichomes. This is a very terpy variety which is no surprise as Unicorn Poop and Wedding Cake are very impressive cultivars. The most dominant terpenes are myrcene, caryophyllene, humulene and limonene. The aroma and flavour are quite similar as the buds smell strongly like vanilla cake. This is an indica dominant hybrid. These plants are grown in a sea of green to maximize top bud production and to create a premium product. The plants are hand harvested, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged to ensure the upmost quality.

Product Short Description: Known for its potent gassy smell, GP20 buds have minty green nugs with bright orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.
Product Long Description: GP20 is a coveted hybrid strain collab between Cookies and Powerzzz Genetics combining the strains Y-Griega and Snowman. This strain is known for having a very potent gassy smell. GP20 buds have minty green nugs with bright orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

Product Short Description: With a pungent fresh peach cobbler aroma, Georgia Pie buds have striking orange hairs with trichomes that are tinted purple, orange and green.
Product Long Description: Georgia Pie is a potent hybrid strain bred by Seed Junky Genetics and is a cross between Gellati and Kush Mints. This strain is known for having a pungent aroma that smells like a fresh peach cobbler. Georgia Pie buds have striking orange hairs with trichomes that are tinted purple, orange and green.

Product Short Description: Big Dip is a potent Indica-Dominant strain boasting sweet, fresh earthy aromas.
Product Long Description: On warm summer evenings in Canada, the Big Dipper shines bright in the night sky. Cruuzy Big Dip was inspired by this transfixing sight. This limited release, highly potent indica-dominant strain boasts sweet, fresh earthy aromas. Big Dip is a unique Banana Punch.

Product Short Description: Pink Krush is a relative of OG Kush.  Expect gassy aromas in addition to citrus and earthy notes.
Product Long Description: Favours is an emerging cannabis brand that always has a good time through small acts of kindness and joyful gestures.  We proudly introduce Favours and the first product Pink Krush. This popular strain is a relative of OG Kush and has a flavour-rich strong, gassy aroma with citrus and earthy notes from a terpene profile that includes beta-caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and linalool. The dense and sticky green buds dance in the sunlight with sparkling trichomes throughout.

Product Short Description: An intense pungent Kush-like smell with an undertone that is sweet and spicy.  Mild hints of diesel and vanilla that leaves a peppery aftertaste.
Product Long Description: An intense pungent Kush-like smell with an undertone that is sweet and spicy.  Mild hints of diesel and vanilla that leaves a peppery aftertaste.

Product Long Description: Our Sour Kush is super smelly. High in terpenes, it's an assertive flower with a terrifically tart and ultra-pungent aroma. Known for its dense buds peppered with orange pistils and coated in sparkling trichomes that hit the nose with a combination of sour lemon and invigorating pine. Its powerful flavour profile is just as tangy, balanced with hints of earth, wood, and diesel.

Product Long Description: Introducing Liiv Orange Monkey, a new strain carefully curated with the Liiv consumer in mind. A terpene content of over 4.5% provides a sensory experience we know our consumers are looking for. It features very high levels of limonene, myrcene, and caryophyllene, giving it a very strong citrus aroma. The buds show distinct orange hairs and a frosty coating of amber crystal trichomes.

And, it smells positively bananas, owing its sweet aroma to its unique terpene profile dominated by terpinolene and rounded out by myrcene and beta-caryophyllene. Its large spearhead shaped buds boast a tight, dense structure flecked with copper calyxes, while its flavour is a blend of sweet citrus with earthy hints of pine.

Royal City Cannabis Co. is proud to partner with passionate craft growers like 7Green to keep bringing exciting craft flower to Ontario. Our roots run deep, and our standards are high.

Cherry Head has a flowering period of approximately eight to nine weeks to maturity.
Yield: High
THC: 5–8%
CBD: 5–8%
Flower Period: 8–9 weeks
Feminized: Yes

With a higher difficulty to grow, you can be rewarded with very high THC percentages and incredible terpene profiles. This earthy, and subtle tropical mix is a treat for the nose and produces amazing effects. Product Short Description: Bubba Kush is an indica heavy, and high THC producing genetic
Product Long Description:
Bubba Kush is an Indica heavy, and high THC producing genetic. This plant will produce dark green flowers, with purple pigments in late flower with an incredibly pungent and classic aroma and flavour. The higher stretch rate will complement the larger yields, but should considered when growing either indoors/outdoors. Bubba Kush is a beginner friendly cultivar and is resistant to mould and pests, which makes it a great candidate for all growing types. Colder temperatures and environments should be avoided.

Product Long Description:

It grows fast and stretches during both the vegetative and flowering stages, producing a tall plant with large buds. These 100% feminized seeds have been bred in greenhouse conditions and are suitable for indoor and outdoor cultivation across Canada. Charlotte’s Diesel has a flowering period of approximately nine to 12 weeks to maturity.

Product Long Description:
Wedding Cake, a hybrid of Cherry Pie and GSC, features a rich and tangy flavour profile with undertones of earthy pepper. Wedding Cake grows short and sturdy, allowing growers to cultivate it in various environments. At harvest, it produces dense buds that look close to solid. These 100% feminized seeds have been bred in greenhouse conditions and are suitable for indoor and outdoor cultivation across Canada. Wedding Cake has a flowering period of approximately seven to eight weeks to maturity.
  • Yield: Very high
  • THC: 16-25%
  • CBD: <1%
  • Species: Indica dominant
  • Flower period: 7-8 weeks
  • Lineage: Cherry Pie x GSC
  • Feminized: Yes

Product Short Description: This unique feminized pheno is a true kush, with bright autumn colours at the end of the flowering cycle. Tested at  8–14% CBD to 6–10% THC.
Product Long Description: Violator Kush is a high-quality strain from India, where Malana Cream hashish finds its origin. This particular pheno is a rare balanced cultivar; coming in at 8–12%+ CBD and 7–10%+ THC. For those who prefer the "body high" of an indica, Violator Kush delivers a very pleasing physical sensation of complete relaxation. With only 20% sativa genetics, this is definitely an indica-dominant variety. The strain has a pungent odour with strong earthy aromas and a musky taste. Violator Kush is a small plant and rarely grows over 90 cm in height. Violator Kush is best suited to mild climates. Indoors, Violator Kush should respond well to both soil and hydroponics. Flowering time is 8–9 weeks, yielding roughly 650g/m² indoors."

Product Short Description: With fruity, musky cheese aromas, this classic cultivar is suited to the outdoors, and is sea of green and hydroponic system friendly.
Product Long Description: With fruity, musky cheese aromas, this classic blueberry and cheese favourite gets a pungent boost from OG. Suited to the outdoors, this cultivar does need a bit more trimming but rewards with a high yield and dense, trichome rich buds. This plant is sea of green & hydroponic system friendly.

Product Short Description: Bred from old school genetics, OG Haze is a sativa hybrid and is ideal for indoor or outdoor cultivation. Feminized seeds, 5 per pack.
Product Long Description: Bred by ABIDE from old school genetics and adapted to Ontario, OG Haze is a sativa hybrid strain producing medium to tall, bushy, high yielding plants. OG Haze has dense medium to dark green flowers with a flowering time of approximately 8 weeks. 5 feminized seeds are packaged in a plastic vial within a zip pouch.

Product Short Description: Feminized autoflower seeds. Flavour powerhouse with 4 to 5% terpenes, finishing in late August to early September outdoors. Compostable packaging.
Product Long Description: Get ready to hear “I can’t believe it’s not indoor!” A truly new school meets old school variety of feminized autoflower seeds. With 4 to 5% terpenes and terpinolene dominance, this unique strain is a powerhouse of flavour. Hints of lime and pine round out the aroma nicely. Finishing time outdoors in late August to early September, under natural lighting in southern Canada. Can be high yielding with resistance to pests, mold and powdery mildew. Smaller pots can encourage faster yield, where larger pots can give bigger yields. Packaged in 100% compostable packaging with an insert to keep your seeds safe and protected.

Product Short Description: These feminized seeds are a Purple Papaya cross. Terpene rich with earthy hops, citrusy pine and a warm hint of cinnamon. Finish in early September.
Product Long Description: With a sweet and fruity fragrance, these feminized hybrid seeds are a Purple Papaya cross. Very vigorous and healthy growth makes this strain great for both outdoor growing or greenhouses. This strain is a pleasure to grow and smoke. Terpene rich, smooth aromatic flavours include earthy hops, fresh citrusy pine and a warm hint of cinnamon drawn from myrcene, pinene and humulene dominance. Finishing time outdoors in mid-September. Packaged in 100% compostable packaging with an insert to keep your seeds safe and protected.

Product Short Description: A new collaboration between BC and Ontario nurseries brings the Garlic Chem feminized seeds to market. Pungent terpene profile with gassy aromas.
Product Long Description: A new collaboration between BC and Ontario nurseries brings the Garlic Chem feminized seeds to market. Grown by Apollo Green, Garlic Chem is a powerful cross of the world-renowned GMO (aka Garlic Cookies) with a powerhouse backcross of the rare, clone-only Chem91 Skunk VA from Chemdog. A robust plant that can provide above average yields and resistance to powdery mildew. Dense flowers with an extremely pungent terpene profile and excessive gassy aromas that will impress any connoisseur. Dominant terpenes include myrcene, caryophyllene, selinadiene and limonene. Garlic Chem is suitable for indoor, greenhouse or outdoor growing with 7.5 to 8 week flowering time. Packaged in 100% compostable packaging with an insert to keep your seeds safe and protected.

Product Short Description: This heavy-yielding seed is great for the new grower or the professional.
Product Long Description: Parkland Flower’s Northern Lights contains Auto Blue Cheese hybridized with Northern Lights to mix the best of both worlds. The Northern Lights lineage presents earthy flavours, while the Cheese lineage sweetens the taste, intensifying the organoleptic qualities of NL x Cheese cross. Bred for Canadian climates, this cultivar is pest and bud rot-resistant. Plant outside after the last frost and expect 100 days from germination to harvest.

Product Name: E V E R E 5 T Seeds (Regular)
Product Short Description: E V E R E 5 T is an indoor indica-dominant strain for the home grower, producing a great yield with thick buds and an eight-week flowering period.
Product Long Description: E V E R E 5 T, the fifth release of our M O U N T A I N series, is an indoor indica-dominant strain that is sure to be a classic. With genetic heritage from Mendo Purps and OG Kush, this F3 cross has pedigree for greatness. The nose is a familiar cannabis skunk aroma, as the terpene profile includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, and ocimene. This traditional indica-dominant strain will yield large sticky flowers with potent THC frosted peaks in eight weeks of 12-hour light.

Product Short Description: This strain is an early finisher that’s light green in colour, with frosty buds and a sweet fruity fragrance.
Product Long Description:
One of BC’s most legendary strains, Apricot Kush is known for its consistency. Best for outdoor and greenhouse cultivation, plants will grow to a medium height with a flowering period of 8 weeks to maturity. From first-time growers to experts, Apricot Kush is an easy-to-grow plant with great yield and bud density. This strain is ready to grow in your backyard or on your balcony! This incredibly tasty and flavourful cannabis strain will reach a THC concentration of 14-18% and will allow you to undergo a potent but balanced sativa-indica effect.
Apricot Kush buds are very resinous with an intoxicating aroma. A superb yielder with good mold resistance, the Apricot is great outdoors, in greenhouses or indoors. An uplifting and euphoric high compliment the intense aroma. Enjoy the experience of harvesting and trimming but fair warning -- these buds will gum up your scissors and fingers with resin. This strain will finish in mid-September so you’re able to harvest your crop before the cold.

Product Name: D 3 N A L I Seeds (Regular)
Product Short Description: The third release of our M O U N T A I N series is an indoor sativa that is easy to grow.
Product Long Description: The third release of our M O U N T A I N series is an indoor sativa that is easy to grow. Averaging about 3 feet in height and resistant to botrytis, our D 3 N A L I seed line is great for the home grower, flowering within 56-65 days. The genetic heritage of this seed line is from Super Silver Haze and Lemon Skunk. With a fragrant lemon pepper aroma from limonene and caryophyllene terpenes and average THC percentage of 20%, D 3 N A L I is sure to be a favourite in your garden. Plan for ways to support your crop of D 3 N A L I, as the yield can sometimes become too heavy for the plant.

Product Short Description: Pest resistant, can grow to 5 feet outdoors and very resinous. It’s an ideal cultivar for extraction, with buds dripping in resin producing trichomes.

It’s an ideal cultivar for extractions, with buds dripping in resin producing trichomes.  THC levels of greater than 20%, with a flowering time of eight to nine weeks.

Lemon Rocket is bred from Cake and Fuel genetics and carries a strong aroma of gas with fresh lemon undertones. Driftwood Diesel is crossbred from GMO and Fuel strains, giving it a uniquely pungent aroma of gas and chem with a sour taste. Each pre-roll is packed with milled whole bud, and never shake. Every “Mixed Greens Sampler” comes in a sleek, reusable tin package and includes a humidity pack, so your pre-rolls stay fresher for longer.

Product Name: Pineapple Infused with Congolese Live Resin Soft Chews
Product Short Description: Sweet pineapple-flavoured soft chews infused with sativa-dominant Congolese live resin. Made without animal products.
Product Long Description: Exotic fruit flavours are accented by the earthy, incense-forward fragrance from the classic sativa strain Congolese. Lost Farm soft chews are made without animal products. They are strain-specific and infused with live resin. At the time of harvest, cannabis flower is flash-frozen to preserve the rich flavours, complex aromas and broad terpene profiles typically lost in most edibles. From there, the flower is delicately extracted to create live resin, which is infused to create an edible with unparalleled flavour. Lost Farm is where past and future, nature and technology merge. Where the ambition of master cultivators meets the vision of edible engineers. Here, we make the freshest, most mouth-watering fruit-flavoured edibles featuring some of the most exciting cannabis strains for the most sophisticated consumers.

"Blüm's cannabis infused beverage is expertly composed with the natural flavours of strawberry, mint, and lime. Enjoy the classic taste of the islands without sugar or sweeteners and only 10 calories. Blüm is not your typical sparkling water, with unexpectedly bold flavours you’ll have to taste to believe. For the ultimate experience, Blüm is best served chilled over ice and garnished with a wedge of lime. From the pleasant fruity aroma to the cooling mint finish, Blüm offers a refreshing new way to 'get bubbly'. 

Blüm Beverage Co. originates in Southwestern Ontario and is comprised of a team that has been immersed in the cannabis industry since 2015. Our formulation is complete and our product is production-ready."

As they harvest, the crop is flash-frozen to seal in the cannabinoids and terpenes until they are ready to be extracted through their hydrocarbon process, resulting in highly aromatic and flavourful concentrates.

Kish is an Ontario original, a brilliant outdoor grower with outstanding terp levels and bulging trichomes, this strain is a renegade mix of DJ Short, Blueberry and Afghani.

Once the top colas of the 2019 outdoor-grown Kish hit 19.5% THC and a terpene content of over 5% in the field, they topped those trees and immediately froze them to lock it all in.

Kish Terp Slush gives off notes of raspberry, mango, and pine, with a strong hit of sweet Orange at the finish. Greybeard Live Resin Terp Slush also has a wonderfully granular consistency that makes it a breeze to use in dab rigs and pens.

Product Name: Sauce Rosin Labs Mimosa Live Rosin
Product Short Description: Sauce Rosin Mimosa Live Rosin is made using hand-washed, hang-dried Mimosa flower grown indoors. The non-taffy extract goes straight from the press to the jar to preserve terpenes. 73% THC, >1% CBD.
Product Long Description:
Sauce Rosin Mimosa Live Rosin is a water-based, solventless extract made using Mimosa whole, fresh, 
frozen flower, which is a cross between Clementine and Purple Punch. The plants are hand-washed and 
then frozen before undergoing an agitation process to gently remove the trichome heads. This creates 
Ice Water Hash, which is graded into a premium spectrum (73µ-159µ) and pressed at 170°F. The pressing 
process creates the first-press live rosin, which is immediately moved from the press to a jar to avoid 
turning to taffy. Sauce Rosin Mimosa Live Rosin has a flavour profile similar to fresh pressed oranges, 
flower bouquets, and hints of grape, with terpenes including limonene and humulene. It has a bright 
white-gold colour with a wet badder consistency, and it melts clean on the banger with no residue. Sauce 
Rosin Mimosa Live Rosin is a sativa extract with 70-75% THC, >6% terpenes, and <1% CBD.

Product Short Description: Apricot Kush has a taste of earthy and sweet apricots. This BC outdoor grown cultivar by Dunesberry Farms is processed as WPFF material.
Product Long Description: Apricot Kush has a taste of earthy and sweet apricots. This BC outdoor grown cultivar by Dunesberry Farms is processed as WPFF (whole plant fresh frozen) material. It is then submerged in an ice water bath to manually separate the trichome heads from the plant biomass. The separated and isolated trichome heads are then referred to as hash, are collected and freeze dried to remove all moisture content. The dried hash is then put into mesh bags and pressed between heated plates to separate the oil from the hash creating a product known as “rosin.” Rosin is able to be vapourized, free from impurities and any foreign chemicals.

Nugz Fresh Frozen Hash Rosin (FFHR) is derived from our single source indoor-grown genetics, frozen at harvest to preserve the flowers’ natural terpene profile, flavours and aromas. Coffee Cream is an indica-dominant cultivar that descends from the base OG Kush that’s twisted with the South African sativa, Durban Poison. It offers complex, robust coffee and dried berry flavours with top terpenes of myrcene, limonene, nerolidol and linalool. This flower is hand-harvested, then immediately fresh frozen. It’s then washed in ice water to separate the trichome heads from the plant material and freeze dried to remove the water. Once fully dried, the oils are squeezed out using a rosin press. A narrow spectrum of 90-120u micron filter bags are used to sift out the most premium trichome heads that are used for squishing on the rosin press. Smaller yield, biggest flavour.

Product Short Description: ?This solventless extract is made from sun-grown whole plant fresh-frozen trichomes that are separated in ice water and gently pressed into rosin.

Outlaw’s terpene content comes in at 9-12%, with high levels of caryophyllene, farnesene and limonene. We hand harvest our sun-grown cannabis plants and immediately freeze them (called Whole Plant Fresh Frozen, or WPFF). Trichomes are separated in ice water using a careful agitation process, and the water hash is gently pressed into rosin through 37u bags. Avana hand packages our rosin in square glass pods sealed with an industry-leading airtight FEP anti-stick liner and multi-shot TPE gasket. We recommend storing Avana Select Live Rosin in the fridge and removing it a minimum of 30 minutes before opening to reduce condensation and bring the rosin to its truest representation at room temperature. We recommend dabbing Avana Select Live Rosin between 450°F and 500°F.
